context:
{
  "id": "line:0ecb64f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Tavern"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89623",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] Is it just me,[p/] or does this hallway look similar to the one in your family's tavern?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2082",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Well,[p/] most taverns use the same architecture.[p/] So, I don't think it's [i]that[/i] strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0cece",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: No,[p/] but it looks [i]exactly[/i] like the McCoy Tavern.[p/] It's uncanny."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8b991",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's as if whoever made this tavern decided to just reuse the same design."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a57052",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] making unique designs is difficult, Tyrion.[p/] [i]And[/i] it costs money."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bc693",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you really think developers should be spending resources on a location that you'll only see once?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0573b35",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know...[p/] It just seems kind of lazy."
}

{
  "id": "line:019e442",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, if it bothers you so much,[p/][s/] why don't [i]you[/i] pay for the assets required to make a new one?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3ff9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "I decided to drop the matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93d07",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Player: End Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0350852",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this your room, Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a7ec",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Aster: Yes,[p/] it's quite cozy."
}

{
  "id": "line:023938a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Aster: I'm very pleased with how much personality the craftsmanship has."
}

{
  "id": "line:0543601",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Aster: It's nothing like any of the resorts I've stayed at.[p/] It's far more rustic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5c51",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bc84d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0722c17",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Aster de Wyverngarde"
}

{
  "id": "line:091d365",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, Your Highness—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0186355",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Please, there's no need for that.[p/] Just call me \"Aster\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9316",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "He couldn't be serious, could he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0173120",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "After I got a good look at him,[p/] he looked sincere—[p/]a little [i]too[/i] sincere."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b7be2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "He carried himself with the poise of a royal,[p/] but there was also a warm kindness and humility in his eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9c749",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "He sounded too good to be true,[p/] but maybe I was just too jaded by the other aristocrats I'd met."
}

{
  "id": "line:049aaa1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is the Crown Prince doing in a tavern like this, anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0413320",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] the Kingsguard were being far too overbearing."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f2c89",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: They were insistent that I return to the capital,[p/] but I'd been planning this trip to Aurinax for days."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8f7e",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I found an opportunity to sneak away from them and hired a guide to show me around the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ebbad",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you talking about Noah Morrison?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deeaae",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Ah, yes.[p/] Mr. Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38899",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: He told me quite a lot about the industrial complexities of Aurinax[p/] and even more about the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:052e1fc",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is it really okay for you to disappear like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060d0dd",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: The Kingsguard are probably freaking out over losing track of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e8396",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] they worry far too much.[p/] I can take care of myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd46c2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I may not look it,[p/] but I'm one of the most powerful mages in this kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:056b645",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That sounds awfully cocky,[p/] don't you think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d66e7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Hm...[p/] You think so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084d455",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "There was so much optimism behind those eyes.[p/] How sheltered was this guy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba11f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: What did you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dcfd0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] Mr. Morrison told us you were present when the accident occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:010c5c0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Ah, it was quite dreadful what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9acd5",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We only have one witness who actually saw Justin fall into that vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8f3c2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was wondering if you saw anything she didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f83f2f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I didn't see much, I'm afraid.[p/] It all happened very quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f15c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: If he weren't yelling at that animal,[p/] I might not have even noticed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06782a7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There was an animal up on the catwalk, too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cfdde",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: It looked to be some kind of hairless rodent,[p/] but it was abnormally large."
}

{
  "id": "line:02532ce",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I think he may have been trying to catch it.[p/] He even grabbed it at one point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0428eac",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Was he facing towards Dracogen's office when he was yelling at this rodent?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb3c61",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I think so.[p/] Noah pointed out the office window earlier.[p/] It allowed Stefanic to oversee the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b49491",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see anyone else up on the catwalk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb53bb",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: No,[p/] my view of the catwalk was limited by my position."
}

{
  "id": "line:03542e5",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] This whole time,[p/] I thought Justin had been yelling at the Phantom,[p/] but it turned out he was just yelling at a rat."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b4547",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "It seemed that the only person who spotted the thief that day was Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59773",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Accident"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5852e",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see the moment that Justin fell in?[p/] Was he pushed off the catwalk by a spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1a40",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I'm not quite sure,[p/] but I definitely saw something magical."
}

{
  "id": "line:0805939",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: There was a flash of magical light centered on his position."
}

{
  "id": "line:097242c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: The magical energy took the shape of a prism before blowing apart the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0778670",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Justin lost his balance afterward and fell into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:05643c9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see what the spell looked like?[p/] Do you think you could identify it for us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff3714",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: The problem is that I'm almost sure that it [i]wasn't[/i] a spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f87f87",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: It was the effect of some sort of artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:03af993",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How can you be so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b760",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: It's difficult for someone who's not a mage to understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0865b0a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: When a mage casts a spell,[p/] they draw and harness the aether from within their own body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43775",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Artificery, on the other hand,[p/] draws aether from the natural ley lines that run through the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52456",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I am someone who has practiced arcane magic for my entire life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0464cc7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I've slowly learned how to sense how aether moves around me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd7fbb",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You can do that, too?[p/] I thought I was the only one."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef56a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Oh,[p/] that talent is quite a rarity—[p/]even among the royal family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6f3f8",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I suppose I shouldn't expect anything less from the Crimson Demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b68af8",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Stop calling me that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f40394",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: What spell was cast on Justin?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0079d94",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you could feel the aether was moving towards the source of that spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:080e641",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Yes,[p/] it was quite distinct because of how high up he was."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3d5d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I could sense the aether rising out of the ground to his position on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0133cb3",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: So the guardrail was broken apart by this artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d5ec",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Is that why there weren't any traces of magic up there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e227f9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Artificery simply replicates the effects of an arcane spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0143541",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They leave traces of magic,[p/] just like spells cast by a mage do."
}

{
  "id": "line:029f9bb",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That also means our culprit wasn't necessarily a mage.[p/] [i]Anyone[/i] could have used a device like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a00d2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: ...Not necessarily."
}

{
  "id": "line:0637f4c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a561d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: The amount of aether being drawn was considerable.[p/] It was of a much a higher quantity than what most artificery devices are capable of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d834dd",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Whatever that device was,[p/] it was quite advanced and dangerous.[p/] Something like that wouldn't be commonly available to the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9f17",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "The military would definitely have access to a weapon like that, too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0258b95",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "It pointed to Lucio Steelwind,[p/] but that just made his actions during the trial all the more bizarre."
}

{
  "id": "line:058ec22",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Lucio Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:007c193",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What can you tell me about Grand General Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b99c04",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: The Grand General is a difficult man to speak of."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d0dae",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: In recent days,[p/] his name alone carries the weight of thousands of slaughtered innocents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb028",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I take it you don't care much for him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0441aae",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Not many do.[p/] Even the most heartless monster would see little sense in his bloody conquest in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0478c07",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I was surprised when he took the stand at the trial yesterday,[p/] but I'm sure it's just another plot to undermine the other pillar families."
}

{
  "id": "line:0118eac",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I had really hoped my arranged marriage to Lady Steelwind would sate his thirst for power,[p/] but it seems to have just made it worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e12d4d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] What did you just say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07dfa2f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] of course.[p/] I suppose most outside of the nobility wouldn't be aware of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e87ce",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: My father and the Grand General have arranged for me to marry Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab9652",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] She never told me she was engaged to the [i]Crown Prince[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0934b32",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I wouldn't blame her.[p/] She's not exactly pleased with our arrangement."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d988",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: That woman despises me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee606",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0450ef0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: Our marriage is purely political—[p/]a way to unify the royal family with the upper brass of the military."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc46f7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: I admire her desire to bring prosperity to the commonfolk,[p/] but I unfortunately seem to represent everything she hates about this kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bda098",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: She can't even stand speaking to me.[p/] Every time I'm around her,[p/] she can barely contain her contempt."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c8c3",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh no..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0413f50",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: But I've made my peace with that.[p/] She's always cared more about her duty than anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:033a7b2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: When I take the throne,[p/] I will build her a compassionate kingdom that she can take pride in."
}

{
  "id": "line:034b132",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "...I really wanted to believe him,[p/] but I knew better than to trust empty promises like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07747d1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "I guess only time would tell what kind of ruler he would be."
}

{
  "id": "line:089dd8d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Stolen Item"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8834c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Talk",
  "text": "Player: BACK"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4fc33",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster, I've been hearing an awful lot about how the serial robber stole that item from your ship."
}

{
  "id": "line:063512e",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: Ah, that.[p/] The Kingsguard have been scrambling around trying to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c4a0e",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would you be able to tell me what they stole?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e53641",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: Hm...[p/] I don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:095003b",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been having a lot of trouble pinning down what the thief was after."
}

{
  "id": "line:010a375",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: If they infiltrated your ship,[p/] they were taking a gigantic risk.[p/] They wouldn't have done that without a good reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e18282",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068bbf3",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: They stole several high-capacity arcane crystals attuned to the school of [b]evocation[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeabdf",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: Arcane crystals are pretty common, aren't they?[p/][s/] They're what draw and provide power to artificery devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3834",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: The problem is that they're attuned to [b]evocation[/b]:[p/] the most raw and destructive school of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e8b34",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: Artificery that uses [b]evocation[/b] is heavily supervised by the kingdom,[p/] and most devices that use them are extremely weak."
}

{
  "id": "line:043e3b6",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: Those crystals were a shipment addressed to Von Sanctus Industries.[p/] They were meant to be received at port and used to construct weapons for use by the military."
}

{
  "id": "line:011e7bc",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are these crystals really that valuable?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00943cf",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: They have a large capacity to channel [b]evocation[/b] magic.[p/] They're extremely potent at unleashing energy,"
}

{
  "id": "line:0727049",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Aster: In the wrong hands,[p/] they could produce an explosion with the power to level an entire block of this city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac778c",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And there have been mass reports of insurrection here, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f60ee7",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "Whether those reports were true or not,[p/] my teeth clenched at the thought of what someone might do with those crystals."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fb8f3",
  "node": "AsterConvStoleItem",
  "text": "It was even worse to think about what the Grand General might do to stop that from happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0432d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Runestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4b4e4",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3f99",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04edcc7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: It's proof that you're a certified attorney!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5bb9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I've never seen one of these up close before!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b13b4",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?[p/] I thought the Crown Prince would be the first person to have a Runestone like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4f1e1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I have a Runestone,[p/][s/] but it's not an [i]Attorney's[/i] Runestone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0973855",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Finally![p/][s/] Someone that understands the difference!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cb584",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36c1a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc5fc6",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I can't believe I'm meeting Tyrion Cuthbert!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1e3e3",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I appreciate the admiration,[p/] but I don't see what's so special about me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0243aef",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Well, I've been an admirer of Ruby Tymora for a while,[p/] but your story is far more inspiring!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09079c1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...You rose above the tragedy that befell your mother,[p/] and became a force against the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fbe77",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How do you know about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0248a61",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I read about your story in the paper—[p/]a grieving child,[p/] who walked into the woods in despair."
}

{
  "id": "line:038b3f5",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: That story made quite an impression on me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0c980",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: When I saw the story of Ms. McCoy's trial,[p/] I recognized you immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b41f9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I'm so glad that you survived."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c586a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2d11",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d56b9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d054c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I never imagined that I'd meet the Crimson Demon of the Eastern Kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:042da5f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay,[p/] how the hell did you find out about that nickname?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e49f52",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ba154",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: My position as the Crown Prince makes me privy to stories like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a05ad1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What is the \"Crimson Demon\", anyways?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0012b3a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I don't want to talk about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5f3b",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "I decided to drop the subject."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b45cc8",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c25879",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] Lady Steelwind.[p/] I'm glad to see my fiancée is growing into her role."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e1667",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5c2c",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Is Ruby Tymora here as well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcc7fc",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I was wondering if you could put in a good word for me.[p/] I've been wanting her autograph."
}

{
  "id": "line:027fd44",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]You're[/i] the Crown Prince.[p/] Couldn't you just ask her yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae1172",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I-[p/][s/]I've tried,[p/] but the last time I saw her,[p/] she had very[p/] [i]strong[/i] words for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:014253f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "That [i]did[/i] make sense.[p/] She had more animosity towards the aristocracy than [i]I[/i] did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed5d5a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Lloyd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08fda",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I heard about your chess match with the Duke of Commerce."
}

{
  "id": "line:091a6c9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I wish I could have seen it myself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0913593",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: There wasn't much to see.[p/] For all his arrogance,[p/] The Duke was a pushover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b67d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] That just makes me regret it more.[p/] I would've loved to see that weasel put in his place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0538be1",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Isn't he one of the kingdom's dukes?[p/] I'd thought you two would be more amicable."
}

{
  "id": "line:072ec73",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: No one knows more about the oppression of the Four Pillars than I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:077af97",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099653a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Coraline"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3d74",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Coraline Sibyl:[p/] the Minister of Justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:050ba65",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It doesn't sound like you have a high opinion of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aab8e3",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: She's the most powerful of the Four Pillar Lords,[p/] but she's also the most apathetic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c6a7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Our system of governance is broken.[p/] She has the power to change it,[p/] yet she and her House of Lords do nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd91a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you care so much,[p/] [i]you[/i] have the ability to change it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b858bb",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're a part of the royal family, for crying out loud."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e113a0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: One [i]would[/i] think that, wouldn't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0479802",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Lucio"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b44b18",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...I would appreciate it if you didn't speak of the Grand General unless necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f42b0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I take it you don't care for him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9751d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...How could I?[p/] My heart aches for the innocent people he's slaughtered."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a95cd",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: All because of these supposed \"insurrections\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:00846ae",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you really feel that strongly about it,[p/] why hasn't the royal family done anything to stop him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29489",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: House Steelwind controls the only military force equipped to maintain order in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:009d40a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I can't say more,[p/] but their mages are also the only thing standing between us and war with the other kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a0ba0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: They are our greatest asset,[p/] while also being our greatest failure."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c140a",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aster"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e652b",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've read a lot of stories about the Crown Prince in the paper,[p/] but they never mention you by name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c968c8",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...That's intentional.[p/] I prefer not to have my name associated with my title."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eeee4",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You've done a lot of charity work for the less fortunate, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67e32",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Yes,[p/] we've hosted so [i]many[/i] fundraisers for them."
}

{
  "id": "line:027d756",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're not a fan of fundraisers."
}

{
  "id": "line:013a40f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I'm not a fan of aristocrats who think they can alleviate their guilt by giving me their spare gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2495e",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: UnionTensions"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed05fb",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Hm...[p/] I'm sad to say that tensions such as these are rampant throughout the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd01e0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: It's just the same conflict between the commoners and the aristocrats that I've always seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ccee",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Dracogen isn't exactly an aristocrat.[p/] He's just a merchant."
}

{
  "id": "line:030b1b0",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: In the eyes of the commonfolk,[p/] there's very little difference.[p/] He has wealth and power,[p/] while they do not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0039230",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I think he [i]is[/i] trying to help them.[p/] I'm fairly certain these \"tensions\" are just fabricated stories."
}

{
  "id": "line:073e24d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0416c5d",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Even so,[p/] I think the damage is already done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0241830",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I can only hope Mr. Dracogen's intentions are as noble as you claim they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d7911",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: ShipRep|Blockade"
}

{
  "id": "line:082de78",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Treason"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe1f6",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: ...I can certainly sympathize with the insurrectionists' displeasure with the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0863b0f",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: With what the Grand General has been doing in the countryside,[p/] this was inevitable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0367d75",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you sympathize with them so much,[p/] why hasn't anything been done?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c7db9",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I won't blame you for saying that,[p/] but there's only so much I can do."
}

{
  "id": "line:020eecc",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: I hate to say it,[p/] but the royal family has a lot less influence than you'd think,[p/] especially when it comes to the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb9535",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: My family holds the crown,[p/] but the dukes and duchesses hold everything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d02c7",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "...Was that really true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044c429",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: RikaTest2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0087ce4",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: A mysterious, magical explosion pushed Mr. Waye off that catwalk..."
}

{
  "id": "line:098ba94",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: There aren't any magical traces there either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b49c55",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: It's quite the mystery, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0998f71",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: Although,[p/] I have no doubts that you'll be able to solve it, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e516ac",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Hopefully,[p/] I could live up to his expectations."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d2be",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Player: Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:05729f2",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster, what can you tell me about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ada272",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Present",
  "text": "Aster: My apologies...[p/] I don't think I can help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:00526b6",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, I think that answers all of my questions.[p/] Thank you, Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a983ab",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Check",
  "text": "Aster: Of course![p/][s/] I'm just happy to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:058c0b3",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Check",
  "text": "I was hoping that the Crown Prince had spotted the thief,[p/] but all he saw was some hairless rodent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e707",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Check",
  "text": "I would just need to look into my other leads and hope that would lead somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:042661e",
  "node": "AurUpstairs_Check",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d1655",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Card"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b86f84",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's some kind of tarot card."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6c0ac",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: A customer must have accidentally left it here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd739",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"The Magician...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d48bcd",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: The Magician is associated with the power of transformation and manifestation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b061f0",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: And it's in its upright position,[p/] which is associated with the resourcefulness to harness one's inner potential."
}

{
  "id": "line:04405d2",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: It often symbolizes a person who possesses great skill,[p/] creativity,[p/] and mastery over their craft."
}

{
  "id": "line:04068ca",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: …I never knew you knew about these things."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dd653",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ha![p/][s/] Of course, I do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55ced",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: The power of the magician is the power to shape reality through the power of will!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d1cbc",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: Doesn't [i]that[/i] remind you of someone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0856835",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Not really."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6b292",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: Hey!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08398fb",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Barrels"
}

{
  "id": "line:0038e2a",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are some barrels stacked in the corner here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df9651",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder what's inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d765f",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] Rika.[p/] You wouldn't happen to have Lotus Juice, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddd393",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: \"Lotus Juice\"? [p/] What's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1ec1d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Never mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:071ba09",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: What happened to the Lotus Juice that you \"received\" from Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5a72",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I drank all of it…"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ae97b",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Already...?[p/] She'd only had it for a month."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dad09",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Table"
}

{
  "id": "line:0537689",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: This table looks [i]really[/i] well-made."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7eb33",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: You like it?[p/] I commissioned a local carpenter to have my tables custom-made."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d19c",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: It was probably worth it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8def2",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: They fit with the rustic vibe you've got going on here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac683d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Plant"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c63fdb",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Rika seemed to have decorated the entire café with several plants and flowers."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c45a6",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "The green added a fresh and earthy look to the restaurant."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9484",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Lantern"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b85d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "There were artificery lights hanging from the ceiling."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ff770",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your business must be doing pretty well if you can afford artificery like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97bd8",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's just one of the benefits I get from working with the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:04924ba",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Mosourika: Most of the merchants connect to the artificery ley line."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0df0",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Shelf"
}

{
  "id": "line:055bd0d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "There was a shelf full of drinks,[p/] mugs,[p/] and sugar behind the restaurant counter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0111792",
  "node": "Cafe1_Examine",
  "text": "It must've been where Rika's employees prepared coffee to be served."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aca0d7",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Court Case"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c81419",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright,[p/] let's get to work."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ae440",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that you saw someone cast a spell that pushed Justin into the vats."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3f67",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me exactly what you saw?[p/] I need every detail you can remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c72b5",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It was kind of hard to see.[p/] I was on the ground level,[p/] and he was up on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fae76",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I think I saw him yelling at someone from up there."
}

{
  "id": "line:02748be",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...That's when I saw a flash of light."
}

{
  "id": "line:00439c3",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: There was a short burst of magical energy that ripped the guardrail apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0539bc7",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Justin happened to be standing right next to the top of a nearby vat.[p/] He fell right into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce0c20",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I told one of the workers what I saw,[p/] and they went to try to pull him out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7b056",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: But I guess it was too late.[p/] Those chemicals must have been really toxic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbb017",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "They weren't just toxic.[p/] They were strong enough to completely melt down his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:096d496",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...There's actually something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0712cfe",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I saw Justin drop something from his hands before he fell into that vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0230bab",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: After they pulled him out,[p/] I tried looking for it and cast [b]Detect Magic[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22cda",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's when I found [i]this[/i] on the ground below the walkway."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ac27b",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: A leather strap?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0934a22",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "I looked at the strap more closely."
}

{
  "id": "line:027ec06",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "It had a buckle on it,[p/] but nothing to connect it with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeba31",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": ":The numerals: \"VI\",[p/] were engraved on it.[p/] I was really confused as to what the purpose of this was."
}

{
  "id": "line:00782fd",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I saw a blue glow when I looked at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0979d94",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It was cyan?[p/] That's the color of [b]conjuration[b/] traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a28ef",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I tried to give it to the investigators,[p/] but they didn't think it was important."
}

{
  "id": "line:01190ac",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "I guess that made sense.[p/] They were considering this an accident,[p/] not a murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac868",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Why were you there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058645e",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why [i]were[/i] you at the refinery anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e570c5",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't work there, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d36b9",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I was delivering Justin's breakfast."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a7440",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: He always skips it.[p/] It really annoys me,[p/] so I started bringing some of my pastries over every morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:085803a",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] Breakfast is the most important meal of the day!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089d944",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So important that you ate it multiple times yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c5ecd",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I have a high metabolism, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6ca2c",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Anyways,[p/] isn't it kind of dangerous to let a civilian walk around a factory like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0154b46",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ha![p/][s/] I am no ordinary civilian!"
}

{
  "id": "line:070fbb1",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: No one there would dare to bar my visit to the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0574658",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which means that you don't usually visit the Refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:030053a",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Yeah,[p/] I usually just meet Justin in the freight area."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6da1",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: But he didn't show up that day,[p/] so I got worried and went looking around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f703d4",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: The people who work there recognized me and let me in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0883cbc",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...That's when I saw him fall into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be88dd",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Spell"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4a52f",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you recognize the spell Justin was hit with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058cc76",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I [i]am[/i] a mage,[p/] but I've never seen a spell like that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f833ba",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It happened instantly,[p/] and it didn't look like an explosion or anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0649550",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It kind of looked more like...[p/] an expanding prism."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aee46d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...A prism?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04de3c6",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does that match with any spells that [i]you're[/i] familiar with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02eca72",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I specialize in [b]transmutation[/b] spells,[p/] but any of the spells I know that could create a cube wouldn't expand instantly like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:096702c",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The problem is that the Inquisition didn't find [i]any[/i] traces of magic on the walkway..."
}

{
  "id": "line:086f7df",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It couldn't have been an [b]evocation[/b] spell or a [b]transmutation[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0034b75",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I actually wanted to ask you about that.[p/] Why would an explosive [b]evocation[/b] spell leave traces of magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c272ea",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Magical traces are only left on the objects they are targeting.[p/] Something like a [b]fireball[/b] spell isn't technically targeting anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92b8b",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's correct,[p/] but every [b]evocation[/b] spell produces some kind of residue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0284f35",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: In the case of [b]fireball[/b],[p/] its magical traces would be left on whatever it had burned or melted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a51dd9",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If someone used an [b]evocation[/b] spell powerful enough to rip the guardrail apart,[p/] they would've found traces of [b]evocation[/b] there."
}

{
  "id": "line:06920c3",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Wow,[p/] I never knew how technical these things were."
}

{
  "id": "line:04deb2a",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're lucky they are.[p/] Otherwise,[p/] I'd have a lot less evidence to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0395393",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...If what you're saying is true,[p/] was I wrong about what I saw?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08476ff",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wouldn't say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0040e56",
  "node": "Cafe1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been doing this long enough to know that there's always an explanation for oddities like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a1205",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: A gem with strange carvings?[p/] Is it cursed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c582",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce1b8d",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s fitted with artificery.[p/][s/] I can use it to take pictures of evidence and crime scenes."
}

{
  "id": "line:04432dc",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb5189",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Do you know where I can get one of those?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004e5ea",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have to be an attorney to have one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0818950",
  "node": "Rika1RuneConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] People use Runestones for things other than practicing law."
}

{
  "id": "line:000314c",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'm sorry I had to drag you into this.[p/] I didn't know who else to turn to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbc552",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry about it.[p/] You've saved me more times than I can count."
}

{
  "id": "line:092279f",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Wait...[p/] When did I save you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c54d9",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did you forget?[p/] It's how we met."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c464e",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Celeste: What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09faf49",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was always getting harassed by some of the older kids by the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0303153",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: One day,[p/] they tried to steal the allowance my mother gave me."
}

{
  "id": "line:062ddce",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: You stepped in and stopped them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed11d",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ah,[p/] I remember those cretins now."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f535",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: They had no choice but to flee from the weight of my majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acfb5c",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: She basically knew how to scream in the most alarming way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe3fb",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It sounded like something between a rabid fox and a screeching baby."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a8097",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: A-[p/][s/]Ah, yes.[p/] My battle cry alone was enough to end battles before they started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6a652",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...It drew the attention of law enforcement.[p/] They thought a monster had broken into the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:086c68c",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think that's when I became your \"apprentice\".[p/] We'd always go on adventures together through the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b37c61",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yes,[p/] and look how much you've grown![p/] I'm glad I put you on the path to greatness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08234c4",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c76659",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I really miss those days."
}

{
  "id": "line:0333341",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Me too."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e7af6",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...After all this is over,[p/] let's go on another adventure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0702d6c",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: You should come with us, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:007daee",
  "node": "Rika1TyrConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah![p/][s/] I'm always up for an adventure!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0095b2e",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Celeste,[p/] I love your sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b1a7",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Is that [i]bone[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f6a2",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah![p/][s/] How did you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f57d",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: I could tell by the texture.[p/] I've held some really exotic blades being sold by some of the travelling merchants here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dff0a",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] it was carved from the bones of a Purple Worm.[p/] It's unbreakable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b476d8",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I want one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dadfad",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sure you can find your own sword from those travelling merchants."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ab0e8",
  "node": "Rika1CelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I said I [i]held[/i] those blades.[p/] Affording them is another matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b400dd",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...How [i]was[/i] living with Ruby Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a943c7",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: From the way the papers wrote about her,[p/] she doesn't sound like the kind of person that could raise a ten-year-old."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9fe82",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Those are just baseless rumors being spread by the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5a76",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're just trying to discredit her in the public eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e9925",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh, okay.[p/] That makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caaada",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: They made her sound like some ruthless maniac who'll do whatever it takes to win."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4d03f",
  "node": "Rika1RubyConv",
  "text": "...I wanted to deny that,[p/] so why didn't I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f69b",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this ring?[p/] Justin was wearing it on the day of the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0262c9c",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Really?[p/] I don't remember ever seeing him wear a ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0497c42",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not that noticeable.[p/] Maybe you just didn't notice it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f81de2",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: No...[p/] I was seeing him every day.[p/] I feel like I would've noticed something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:042400a",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's strange...[p/] There's something special about this ring, too.[p/] It wasn't damaged by the chemicals at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a4fa5",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Is that really so important?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbf5f5",
  "node": "Rika1RingConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Insignificant details like this tend to be relevant more often than you'd think."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5837",
  "node": "Rika1StrapConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: What [i]is[/i] this strap?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d89303",
  "node": "Rika1StrapConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...It might just be nothing.[p/] Maybe he found it on the street or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f98dbf",
  "node": "Rika1StrapConv",
  "text": "It [i]was[/i] dirty and reeked of grass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3975e",
  "node": "Rika1StrapConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll have to keep it in mind just in case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0834b78",
  "node": "Rika1StrapConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]has[/i] to be a reason why Justin was holding this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0666af4",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Mosourika"
}

{
  "id": "line:0115be4",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've really grown up.[p/] I can't believe it's been ten whole years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8565d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I kind of feel like not much has changed, though,[p/] and I mean that in a good way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26a23",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'm glad you never lost your spirit, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b75f8",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: You're taking on nobles now![p/] I should be [i]your[/i] apprentice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0425e37",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can make sure no one else ever loses their life to injustice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a950d0",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh...[p/] That's good..."
}

{
  "id": "line:091b03e",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bba7b",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's nothing. [h=\"Is he doing this|because of his mom?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b42035",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Justin|Autopsy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdf457",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm really sorry about what happened to Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:003b795",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It just seems so unfair.[p/] He just got his freedom back a few months ago. [h=\"Something happened to him|when he was locked up...\" e=\"\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2621",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] was Justin convicted of a crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0880d2d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/] Forget I said that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc1bb2",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: If he has a criminal history,[p/] that may point to who may have done this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beac21",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...He doesn't have a criminal history.[p/] He just made a mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3e29",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a139bd",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion.[p/] I [i]don't[/i] want to talk about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9b6ff",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "I paused.[p/] That seemed like a sore subject for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a65d14",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "It might be best to drop it for now and take her word for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ded61",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Ring"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd8b49",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Phantom"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6539",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you know about the \"Mistweaving Phantom\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a596f",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Oh,[p/] it's just some urban myth."
}

{
  "id": "line:001639e",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] Because it sounds like a name you'd come up with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f967be",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Well,[p/] a [i]lot[/i] of my names catch on.[p/] I can't always remember which ones came from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a67ab",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Strap"
}

{
  "id": "line:0312b60",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Player: RikaTest"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4968c",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember anything at all about the person who cast that spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03eca1f",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: No,[p/] with the angle I was at,[p/] it was impossible to see them."
}

{
  "id": "line:037345a",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "We really needed a lead on the murderer,[p/] but it didn't seem like anyone even saw them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bafe92",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Rika?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03642c7",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Hmph...[p/] Something like that speaks for itself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00840b6",
  "node": "Cafe1_Present",
  "text": "In other words,[p/] she had nothing to say about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0595a47",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ah, Lord of the Radiant Flame.[p/] You've returned!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49863",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: Did you get a chance to talk to Mr. Dracogen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cdbcb",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just missed him, apparently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7cc03",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I did talk to the prosecutor, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c6367",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...You mean Lady Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba41e9",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: She's not that bad once you get to know her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0762f6f",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] I learned a bit more about what happened,[p/] but I think your testimony doesn't really fit in with the reports."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe019d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about what you saw?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088a0a1",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Okay.[p/] I'll do whatever I can to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6ad8b",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "If what Rika saw was accurate,[p/] what kind of spell was Justin hit with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb679d",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "It was strong enough to rip the guardrails apart,[p/] but it didn't leave any traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b8a31",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c72fc5",
  "node": "Cafe1_Check",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] I'd learned everything I could from her.[p/] It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0579cff",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Trial"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0a89f",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Mosourika's Past (ARGUMENT)"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db92c5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Truth"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6748",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Mistweaving Phantom"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00ddf",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] but from your story it sounds like—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e36e82",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I think Justin is—[p/][i]was[/i][p/] the thief that everyone's talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:08504ea",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I told you, didn't I?[p/] The thief who broke into Mr. Dracogen's office didn't attack Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0311c88",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: He [i]was[/i] Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:040fa99",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But then,[p/] who attacked him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afe912",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I don't know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0474892",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "The [i]victim[/i] was the Mistweaving Phantom this entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a8f1a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "That was the only lead I had to identify the murderer..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c36794",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "But if Justin was the one who robbed the office that morning,[p/] why would someone attack him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0755615",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Who else would be up on that catwalk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096bffc",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I got him that job, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e29215",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: All those years ago,[p/] one of our heists didn't go as planned,[p/] and we were all arrested."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be51ea",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Justin told me to take a plea deal by letting him take the fall."
}

{
  "id": "line:083278f",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I was scared of losing everything,[p/] so I agreed."
}

{
  "id": "line:051ca65",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: When he finally got released from the dungeons,[p/] I begged Mr. Dracogen to hire him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3dafc",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I thought I could make it up to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06551da",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: But then I started hearing about all the robberies happening in the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6a5c5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It matched so closely to the reports back then,[p/] but I really didn't want to believe it was him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0245df2",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: He had his job at the refinery.[p/] He didn't have to steal to survive anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:031eafb",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...But I guess he just couldn't help himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:029f9ad",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were just trying to help him."
}

{
  "id": "line:073ab77",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...And now he's dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f639c",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: False Reports"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b8ce",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: But if Justin was the serial robber,[p/] why was he robbing the union offices?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ab613",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e0020",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00edd7a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069fb9a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Justin wasn't just robbing the merchant ships this time.[p/] He also stole administrative documents from the union offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cf98d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Why would he do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e2180",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I assumed that the Mistweaving Phantom was part of a larger plot,[p/] and that could still be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ba195",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Justin wasn't working alone.[p/] He must have been stealing those documents for someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:082be37",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: And whoever that person was,[p/] [i]they've[/i] been filing these false reports of insurrection."
}

{
  "id": "line:08385ae",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe his accomplice betrayed him to keep him quiet.[p/] He'd just robbed an imperial ship that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b77b3",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] do you know who he was working for?[p/] Did he say anything to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0833bcc",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...He didn't,[p/] but I know some people he might've talked to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0283dbe",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It was some other kids from the orphanage we used to run our robberies with.[p/] They always hang around the beach area."
}

{
  "id": "line:0639dca",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...They like playing around the abandoned house there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccf2b8",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "...An abandoned house on the coastline."
}

{
  "id": "line:031d44c",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Are you going to be okay?[p/] I can go there with you if you'd like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6da55",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] It's okay.[p/] You've done more than enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:000d95a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Just be careful around them.[p/] They can get in your face sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:06741a0",
  "node": "Cafe2_Talk",
  "text": "I looked at my bodyguard.[p/] I wasn't too worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0185ba0",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry about what happened during the trial.[p/] I didn't know Steelwind would pull your record like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:038400e",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I came to help you and Mr. Dracogen.[p/] I would have done it again if I had to."
}

{
  "id": "line:01354c8",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm really sorry about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f24b24",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know it's really none of my business,[p/] but I need to know this for the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba02da",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was what Steelwind said about you true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0961432",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] I think the Mistweaving Phantom is the person who hit Justin with that spell yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc30a",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: And it could be someone you used to...[p/] [i]work[/i] with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b36f39",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...That's impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:045a14d",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you be so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f63ba",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's just [i]not[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0164486",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:071e8f1",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion![p/][s/] I'm not going to talk about this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0386b18",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "...I couldn't blame her for being so defensive.[p/] I'd be a hypocrite if I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e09380",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "But I needed to know more about these thieves she used to run with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0566e07",
  "node": "Rika2TrialConv",
  "text": "I would need to PERSUADE her to tell me the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1e67",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Stories started spreading around after you went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd3de",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: People heard about how a single mother was executed while the City Watch forced her child to watch."
}

{
  "id": "line:03acc3b",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03652b1",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Things already weren't great here,[p/] but I think that was the tipping point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0309f30",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: No one trusted the City Watch after that,[p/] and the crime in the city slowly got worse and worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d141c",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Merchants were constantly getting robbed and attacked.[p/] One by one,[p/] they started pulling out of the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:09307fa",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: It wasn't long before the only person who could do business here was the Duke of Commerce:[p/] the one merchant with enough armed forces to protect his goods."
}

{
  "id": "line:0576b39",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Jobs became scarce,[p/] and the ones that existed had terrible conditions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1678b",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: A lot of people turned to crime to survive.[p/] So a bunch of us at the orphanage decided we might as well ride the wave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f82561",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: You started robbing von Sanctus's ships."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd122",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Honestly,[p/] it was all Justin.[p/] I was just the distraction."
}

{
  "id": "line:066827f",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: With some help from the other orphans,[p/] I'd use my [b]evocation[/b] magic and put on an act to spook the guards."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d821fb",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: While they were chasing us around,[p/] Justin would slip onto the merchant ships to take what we needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:03baa42",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: At first,[p/] we only took the food and clothes we needed to survive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0125a72",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: But we realized we could actually make a lot of gold by stealing von Sanctus's goods and selling them on the black market."
}

{
  "id": "line:005c011",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Justin had a real talent for breaking into the more guarded ships."
}

{
  "id": "line:0251dae",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: He'd learned a lot about artificery from some of the books we stole,[p/] and he learned how to bypass von Sanctus's security."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a6d1",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: He'd slip in and out of the ships without being seen or triggering any alarms."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aae68",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: They called him the Mistweaving Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d41ea5",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did [i]they[/i] call him that or just you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46cc2",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Hey,[p/] the titles I come up with are catchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01641eb",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Do you remember that name I came up with when we were kids?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed717c",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yeah,[p/] I remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:067cd05",
  "node": "Rika2TruthConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: \"Naught can remain concealed from the Eye of Horus.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8da03",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: You really know how to command a presence in the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d5944",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I kind of have to if I want to get anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b09c7",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Each session starts with the entire room convinced that the defendant is guilty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0381857",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'm glad there are people out there who will do what it takes to deliver justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:05140cb",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I think you and Mr. Dracogen have something in common there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0463aad",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know anything about the Duke of Commerce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd8f64",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Not anything outside of the papers.[p/] We've never even met."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ca88f",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: All I know is that I'm paying him a [i]lot[/i] of taxes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b36d1a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Noah"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b597",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I hope Noah is okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b53708",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] those knights were a little rough with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:026fae0",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is he okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fc999",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] he's just a little shaken up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab14c1",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...He's been trying to get the Kingsguard to reveal where his friends were taken."
}

{
  "id": "line:09deed0",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I suppose Lucio Steelwind is the [i]last[/i] person I'd trust with my friends' lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f1e7",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Stefanic"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cecba",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I really owe a lot to Mr. Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d7f52",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: He invested in you despite your brushes with the law."
}

{
  "id": "line:013b978",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must have a lot of faith in you."
}

{
  "id": "line:003ea13",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...You think so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c28df",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, your cooking [i]is[/i] amazing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0134d6a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I [i]love[/i] your breakfast wraps!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089ecae",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] I'm really proud of how those turned out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbbf9e",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I really hope he gets out of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01315ef",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Autopsy|Justin"
}

{
  "id": "line:096b1a4",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...He's really gone, isn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04991f2",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry,[p/] I shouldn't have—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d5abf",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's okay.[p/] I know you're doing your best to help Mr. Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:043ca79",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's just hard to accept, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4a37",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: A part of me wishes this really was all an accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f304b2",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: But someone attacked,[p/] and I don't even know why."
}

{
  "id": "line:0894f33",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe [i]Justin[/i] was the Phantom this entire time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6e495",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Which means he also robbed Mr. Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc64d5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry, Rika..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cddba",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's for the best...[p/] I think I've been trying so hard to ignore the truth,[p/] but it was sitting right in front of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abfec1",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It feels like there's a small weight off my shoulders at least."
}

{
  "id": "line:034cb0d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "She knew [i]something[/i] about the Mistweaving Phantom,[p/] but she obviously wasn't keen on sharing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0791782",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "I'd need to persuade her in an ARGUMENT if I wanted to get anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:071b094",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Mosourika|RikaPast"
}

{
  "id": "line:073f13a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks for telling me about what happened, Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5775f",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know that must've been difficult."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad23c5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] I really [i]do[/i] hope it helps."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2d2a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: It would've been nice if you told us you were safe in Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f82ab",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry.[p/] I was too focused on getting revenge on the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:074db1d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: And after a while,[p/] it just felt like too much time had passed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b1bbf",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah, well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d01b2c",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: You're here now.[p/] We should make the most of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5208b",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I'm holding you two to that adventure after all this is over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7541d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Sorry,[p/] I can't say much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4acae",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "I arrived at Rika's café and found it completely empty.[p/] The entrance was locked too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0068ed5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "There was a note on the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0957195",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "\"I am on a hunt to slay a fearsome demon! The café will be open later today unless I am tragically slain in my quest! &gt;_&lt;\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0fca8ba",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "...It sounded like I would need to return later."
}

{
  "id": "line:09034a5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "I stepped through the doors of the café and found it completely empty."
}

{
  "id": "line:048de15",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Rika was sitting near the kitchen,[p/] somberly looking out the window."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e522e2",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Hi, Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efb0e5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh...[p/] Hey, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:050fcf0",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?[p/] No grand declarations from the Dark Lord of Aurinax?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e14c2a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I'm not really in the mood for that today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0636826",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "I scratched my head and scanned the empty restaurant.[p/] I never knew what to say in these situations."
}

{
  "id": "line:021c58d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can we talk?[p/] I still need help with the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70a3b",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0168d12",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks for being honest with me, Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c18090",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Mosourika: Just don't push yourself too hard, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1f05",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey, is what she said true?[p/] Did the City Watch really—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3115d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Did all of that really happen to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a19cd6",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yeah."
}

{
  "id": "line:016483e",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I know I've been really pushy lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:065f22a",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...![p/] You've been nothing but kind and patient with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de64c8",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm really sorry I snapped at you yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd813",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were looking out for me.[p/] You didn't deserve that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceef5b",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I've just never seen you like this before.[p/] I've been really worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b32e77",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I really thought I moved past all of this,[p/] but it's like everything that happened is replaying in my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:022e986",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you want to talk about it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f198d",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think I just want to focus on the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc3f84",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion, you're [i]not[/i] okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d808b",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but I have a job to do.[p/] I can't afford to fall apart now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0648445",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can talk about everything once this is all over.[p/] I can handle this until then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df9077",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:017b826",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: But I'm always here if you need to talk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0464ee5",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0168d2c",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm really glad I get to work with you.[p/] These cases wouldn't be nearly as bearable if you weren't here with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8c6d9",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49668",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I love doing this job with you.[p/] I really hope you know that."
}

{
  "id": "line:030396c",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "For the first time in the last few days,[p/] I cracked a smile."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c8db1",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, let's get going."
}

{
  "id": "line:0844054",
  "node": "Cafe2_Check",
  "text": "...It was time to MOVE to the old abandoned house."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e4e0b",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Celeste McCoy"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0cc0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion Cuthbert"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e9a9b",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Rika's Café"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6d6a6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you the owner of this café, Rika?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a502b",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You always dreamed of opening one up when we were kids."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbcf89",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: The source of my strength is the everlasting financial support of the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:0832e17",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Its owner was rendered powerless when he tried confections.[p/] He had no choice but to fund my war path."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b158a9",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Dracogen Trading Company\"?[p/] I don't think I've heard of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae646f",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: They're pretty small.[p/] They're only operating in Aurinax right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a09caa",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: But I hear that they're planning to expand their operations throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:043631a",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm surprised the Duke of Commerce is letting that slide."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e43f2",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Isn't he the guy you beat in the chess tournament this morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0925c91",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Wait...[p/][s/] That was you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:079eeba",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: House von Sanctus is one of the Four Pillar families.[p/] They manage mercantile operations throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f46a",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: So House Steelwind controls the military,[p/] and House von Sanctus controls the businesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccc75f",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: House Frega controls the banking houses and the exchange of currency."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1e362",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And House Sibyl controls the judicial and legislative branches of our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e50ca5",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Aurinax City"
}

{
  "id": "line:055e79b",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it just me,[p/] or does the city look a lot cleaner than before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4147",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh, right.[p/] You left [i]before[/i] all those new merchants appeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:01779c3",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"New merchants\"?[p/] Did they come from a merchants' guild?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed4ec",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Not exactly.[p/] The Dracogen Trading Company was one of the first merchants that came."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9c019",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: They bought some of the Arcane Manufacturies a few years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaf364",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: They transformed it into the heart of artificery production within Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:025830a",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Other merchants felt the way of the wind and followed them here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a889c",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Being based in a port city would definitely give them an edge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2d7f0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: And Aurinax is one of the few trading hubs that sends and receives exports from the other kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0150f24",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "I just looked at her, surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:091bb1f",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hey,[p/] I'm a businesswoman.[p/] I [i]know[/i] about economics."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1cdcf",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Their presence lit a flame in the city's economy."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a1a8e",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: They aren't owned by the nobility,[p/] [i]and[/i] they pay their employees a lot more than von Sanctus does."
}

{
  "id": "line:070d378",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's really opened a lot more opportunities for the people here."
}

{
  "id": "line:094fd2b",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I doubt the Duke appreciates the competition, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a55fa3",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: They're even talking about forming employee-run unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:070a150",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh...[p/] the Duke definitely won't appreciate [i]that[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:09821b7",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Chess Tournament"
}

{
  "id": "line:0144eea",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: So...[p/] You still play chess?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f842e6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] I'm nationally ranked too."
}

{
  "id": "line:081ef58",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I heard that some \"upstart commoner\" defeated von Sanctus at a tournament this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:011b101",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I should have known it was the Lightsworn Monarch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1562e",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"U-[p/]Upstart commoner\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e37ce",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Lightsworn Monarch\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06953b6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Hey,[p/] do you still do that thing when you play?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d32a11",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...No."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da82e6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What \"thing\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01239d7",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nothing...[p/] She's not talking about anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b64ab2",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Wait...[p/] You're [i]actually[/i] embarrassed about it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9947",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: When we were kids,[p/] you did it even more than [i]I[/i] did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b778f5",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] What did he use to do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2970d",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Why don't you show her, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6caf5",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I refuse."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b5366",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/][s/] Show us, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2654",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The \"Thing\""
}

{
  "id": "line:040feac",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think I'm a little too old for this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f791f",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: I am [i]insulted[/i] that you think age has anything to do with it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0614ca6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: You need to feed it, Tyrion—[p/]lest your radiant light be smothered into a flickering ember!"
}

{
  "id": "line:063a737",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do it, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081539c",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah![p/][s/] Do it, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc78e",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "The two of them began chanting,[p/] drawing the attention of the other patrons in the café."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e1ef3",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "I took in a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f9d89",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those who stand in the shadows![p/][s/] Those who fear the light of divinity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c96a0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your imperials will fall,[p/] and your armies will perish!"
}

{
  "id": "line:006821c",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Kneel and cower before the divine gaze of the Eye of Horus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d28fa1",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am Tyrion Cuthbert: [p/][s/]Emperor of Light and the sworn enemy of Darkness itself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0094d69",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Pffft..."
}

{
  "id": "line:099d2b3",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: [i]*snicker*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b87874",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "They were trying really hard to contain their laughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9a07c",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: …W-[p/]Well,[p/][s/] [i]that's[/i] why I don't do it anymore!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0631d4c",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/]No...[p/] T-[p/]That was...[p/] great.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0443699",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It was [i]really[/i] cool, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbeb19",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Her poorly contained laughs puffed out between each word."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e941f5",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: And why are [i]you[/i] laughing?![p/][s/] You were [i]just[/i] doing it a moment ago!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0958135",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] but she owns it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0140ddf",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7c952",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: You used to say something else...[p/] What was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0023",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh, yeah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0184ec5",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: \"It doesn't matter who stands in my way—\""
}

{
  "id": "line:00c8d3e",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Man,[p/] king,[p/] or god?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba75dd",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah![p/] [i]That's[/i] it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da422a",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: He still says that sometimes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b34f99",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Your...[p/] bodyguard really eats a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e58011",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Celeste looked up from her plate,[p/] making eye contact with the two of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:008d6d7",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "She paused for a moment before going back to her meals."
}

{
  "id": "line:06460f7",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's really good at her job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0112830",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "She must've been burning all those calories somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:036d510",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I heard you've been fighting the nobility.[p/] Is that why you need her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0a7b3",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076ef4a",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: The papers won't stop talking about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03227c9",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: I couldn't believe it when I saw your picture in the Aurinax Post after all these years."
}

{
  "id": "line:073373a",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e9a44",
  "node": "RikaCelConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'm just glad you're safe, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cbd15",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Look at you.[p/] I never expected the Lightsworn Monarch to start wearing a suit."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f301e",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Celeste: What's this Lightsworn Monarch I keep hearing about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0009a70",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] It's something I used to call myself when I was a kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513c20",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait, really?![p/][s/] That's adorable!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0253ce9",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: It pales in comparison to the \"Ashen Lord of Aurinax\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acfd48",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: But just as I'd expect from my apprentice![p/][s/] You're practically famous now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c693",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Not even the headmaster of the Imperial Academy could stand against you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff0080",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "I winced at being reminded about Redmond.[p/] I still didn't feel great about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:008f690",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083ada8",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Theodore Redmond wasn't a bad person.[p/] He just made a really terrible mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0471ccc",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not happy about indicting him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b03b3a",
  "node": "RikaTyrConv",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9f7e9",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: A gem with a strange carvings?[p/] Is it cursed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03778c9",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I want one."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c6a5a",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have to be an attorney to receive one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed0f8f",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've really made a life for yourself here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0806fef",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad that you were able to realize your dreams and open a café."
}

{
  "id": "line:0889bf6",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Hehe.[p/] But of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f82539",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: Once the Dark Lord sets her sights on a quarry,[p/] it's only a matter of time before she obtains it."
}

{
  "id": "line:062fda3",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I've grown up since you last saw me."
}

{
  "id": "line:007d0c0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Let's not go [i]that[/i] far."
}

{
  "id": "line:042b131",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: What's [i]that[/i] supposed to mean?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b7d31",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: The scary lady...[p/] She's your mother now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068b3df",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: …She's my guardian, yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daa7b0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Is she nice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038c420",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Nice\" isn't the [i]first[/i] word I'd use to describe Ms. Tymora,[p/] but she's always taken care of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:074ddc0",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She taught me everything I know about being a defense attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d72ee2",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think I'd be the person that I am today without her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9c403",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f311dc",
  "node": "CafeIntro_Present",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'm just glad that she treats you well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0589b9c",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well…[p/] It's been nice catching up with you, Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca43f",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But, I think it's time for us to get going."
}

{
  "id": "line:0473047",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] But we just got here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:024c9cf",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: Hmph...[p/] I'll let you go this time, Lightsworn Monarch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0409bd2",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: But by partaking of the food within my realm,[p/] you've fallen under its curse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faaf00",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Curse?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac4f0e",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: You are now bound to my domain for eternity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf8e24",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: But I'm a benevolent lord.[p/] Your only charge as my servant is to write to me at least once a fortnight!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93ee5",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Celeste: ...How long is a fortnight again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5d37",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Tyrion: Two weeks."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bfd9b",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll stay in touch, Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:0138ae0",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: You'd better."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0cc31",
  "node": "AfterCafe",
  "text": "Mosourika: Don't just disappear like last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ca0f2",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "We left the café and made our way to the local merchant's guild to rent a carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4d80f",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "The city streets seemed a bit more crowded than before.[p/] There must have been some kind of event going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f72fc0",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6455f",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yeah?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052b825",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Celeste: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db9f9b",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "She fidgeted with her hands and seemed unable to make eye contact with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:047875b",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "She looked like she wanted to say something,[p/] but she couldn't find the right words."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d1506",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Never mind,[p/] it's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:09133c9",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d86106",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "We made our way to the merchant's guild in silence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4af01",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "With each step,[p/] we found the streets becoming more and more crowded."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c8f74",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "I really hoped that this traffic wouldn't interfere with the ride home."
}

{
  "id": "line:04466ec",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hi,[p/] could we rent a carriage for travel to Ratholme?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccda64",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Peasant: Sorry,[p/] but travel outside of the city is temporarily closed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f9cc",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?[p/] Why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a19b5",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Peasant: Haven't you heard?[p/] Steelwind's soldiers have locked down the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0571fad",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Peasant: They set up a blockade and everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0239092",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "A chill ran up my spine."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eac4a",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027d452",
  "node": "AfterCafe2",
  "text": "Peasant: Check the city gates if you don't believe me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bf7b6",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "We arrived at the city gates.[p/] Like the man had said,[p/] there was a division of knights blockading the exit to the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0f4f1",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "There was an entire legion of them.[p/] Their flags bore the colours of the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:079675a",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Celeste: What are [i]they[/i] doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e306f1",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "The Kingsguard was a military force that responded to matters of national importance."
}

{
  "id": "line:002155f",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "...They worked directly under Grand General Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0364682",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "The townsfolk kept their distance,[p/] but several aristocrats were making their objections known."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf2e23",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Nobleman: This is outrageous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a925ba",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Noblewoman: How long do you plan on keeping us here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01168ca",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Knight: Sorry,[p/] but we have our orders."
}

{
  "id": "line:00966e8",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Knight: We can't let [i]anyone[/i] outside of the city until our investigation is complete."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e025",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "An \"investigation\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3a402",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should keep our distance.[p/] I wouldn't want to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:028f7d2",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, screw that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05670ea",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Before I knew what was going on,[p/] Celeste marched towards the knight stationed there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aab7e6",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09be659",
  "node": "AfterCafe3",
  "text": "Celeste: At least tell us what's going on?[p/] Why is the entire city being blockaded?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e411e9",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: Sorry, ma'am.[p/] We're not allowed to release that information."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ffad2",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: You'll just have to make other arrangements while we sort this out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dce9ca",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: ...Actually,[p/] I haven't seen you two around before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2c3a9",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: I'll need to take down your names and occupations for our records."
}

{
  "id": "line:0111440",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/][s/] Why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f8f38",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]It's fine, Celeste...[p/] We're better off just cooperating with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5fc7e",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "We needed to avoid any kind of conflict with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0113542",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm Tyrion Cuthbert.[p/] I'm a defense attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701acd",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0040c5d",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm Celeste McCoy:[p/] bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b64814",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df74a9",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Knight: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0059458",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "He suddenly recognized us.[p/] Our reputation did more harm than good most of the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2530",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "I looked over to the other knights.[p/] They seemed to be taking notes of the people here, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83d8a",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "They seemed to be compiling a list of everyone inside the city,[p/] but for what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0286d09",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Nobleman: I have an important engagement tomorrow!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4de95",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Nobleman: What am I supposed to do now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8f7de",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "Noblewoman: This can't possibly be legal![p/][s/] The Minister of Justice [i]will[/i] be hearing of this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:020a93b",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "The nobles continued shouting at the knights.[p/] It was clear they wouldn't be budging any time soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e31d",
  "node": "AfterCafe4",
  "text": "As soon as the knights were finished speaking to us,[p/] I quickly backed away.[p/] Celeste followed closely behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46195",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01428ce",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "She said that,[p/] but it took very little effort for her to keep pace with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c42fff",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "My breathing was getting faster,[p/] and my head was aching."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c71a3",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord...[p/] It's happening here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c7178",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e61a1",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's exactly like what's been happening in the countryside!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bac3c",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio Steelwind sent his men to \"keep the peace\" here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087cce0",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, [i]that's[/i] why you're so freaked out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af80e1",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Tyrion: How are you so calm right now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10aff",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'd probably win if they tried to attack us."
}

{
  "id": "line:01397a2",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, [i]I'm[/i] not some super-warrior who can fight a legion of knights by myself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf601",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion, relax.[p/] They said they're just investigating something."
}

{
  "id": "line:022227d",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: There are no riots going on here,[p/] and we're in the heart of the Duke of Commerce's territory."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1372",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you seriously think von Sanctus would let another Pillar Family march onto his land and kill his people?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04724da",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "She had a point,[p/] but this uneasiness wasn't going away."
}

{
  "id": "line:046a6c7",
  "node": "AfterCafe5",
  "text": "Celeste: It'll be fine.[p/] Let's just find a place to stay the night and wait for all of this to blow over."
}

{
  "id": "line:08be8a1",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "We walked to a nearby tavern and found it absolutely crowded with patrons."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c012",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Everyone else had the same idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec687d",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: Hey,[p/] welcome to the Aegwyn Tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faf873",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: What can I do for you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0683218",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could we get two rooms for the night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072ec24",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: ...Sorry,[p/] we're fully booked with the blockade and all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe0902",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] Let me take care of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ffe6d",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Celeste took out a large pouch of gold and dropped it on the innkeeper's desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfb979",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a39161",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: Well, would you look at that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2439a",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: One of our rooms just opened up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031295e",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Only one?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000731b",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: The entire city's locked down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fec56d",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Peasant: Even [i]with[/i] this gratuity,[p/] that's the best I can do for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ffff3",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] Embarrassed to share a room with me, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035c7ae",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] I just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6d4c8",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "I briefly glanced at the innkeeper.[p/] He chuckled at my reaction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b784c4",
  "node": "AfterCafe6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Fine...[p/] Let's just go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfe91b",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "We walked into the room they had prepared for us."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bcad2",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "...There was one bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07827",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]So...[p/][s/] How should we—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a65231",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh.[p/] I was just kidding before."
}

{
  "id": "line:072b29f",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: You can have the bed.[p/] I'll just sleep on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:023e2fc",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] I can't just let you—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2f9d",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: Please,[p/] we're both commoners,[p/] but [i]you[/i] live a cushy life in the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:061b460",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm a mercenary.[p/] I've lived on the road for years."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0fcd",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: I've slept like this plenty of times."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f074ba",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "I couldn't argue against that,[p/] but I still felt uneasy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c85212",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright...[p/] Just let me know if you change your mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd522c",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e780e6",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "I let myself fall onto the bed.[p/] Celeste started checking the room for anything suspicious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d91d64",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "I tried to relax,[p/] but Lucio Steelwind was in my hometown.[p/] I just took deep breaths."
}

{
  "id": "line:09118af",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Celeste was right.[p/] The Grand General wasn't insane enough to try anything in the heart of Lloyd von Sanctus's territory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1c642",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "...I really hoped that was true."
}

{
  "id": "line:038f5f3",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Lloyd: We had an arrangement![p/][s/] What are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09237cc",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Justin: I don't know.[p/] I guess I'm goin' back to do my actual job."
}

{
  "id": "line:03440bd",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Lloyd: You little rat![p/][s/] Do you think you can get away with crossing [i]me[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008eaaa",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Lloyd: You've already come this far![p/][s/] You are far from blameless!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2f7c",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Lloyd: Now get back in that office and activate the device!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13ca9",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Justin: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c626fd",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Justin: I thought you wanted me to rob the place."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c7335",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Justin: What's so special about this thing,[p/] and why the office?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cb7fe",
  "node": "AfterCafe7",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fad03f",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: How about I activate it right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b968a2",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: D-[p/][s/]Do [i]not[/i] do that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056a382",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: I knew it.[p/] There's been something more to these jobs, ain't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0dc5",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: This ain't just robbery.[p/] You're using me for something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f24591",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: As if [i]you[/i] ever cared."
}

{
  "id": "line:09397ae",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: I know about your debts![p/][s/] You [i]need[/i] me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b4db4",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: You know what?[p/] I'm done with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0668ead",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: I quit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b61eb0",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: What do you think this is?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5a08",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Cat: [i]*MROOOOOOOW*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0862e9f",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: You got cotton in your ears or something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e59670",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: I said.[p/] I.[p/] QUIT."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a40d72",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: Consider this my resignation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88581",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: Wait![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccc8d5",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: W-[p/][s/]Wha—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0067db8",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Justin: AGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3dc56",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Damn it all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d9447",
  "node": "AfterCafe7b",
  "text": "Lloyd: Violetta![p/][s/] Get out of there now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7ac5a",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "As the night went on,[p/] I found myself falling into a terrible nightmare."
}

{
  "id": "line:022674d",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "...How long had I been walking through this forest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc107b",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "It had probably been days at this point.[p/] I was getting tired."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d92635",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "But I had to get to Ratholme.[p/] I had to find Ms. Tymora again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a010af",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I needed to find her.[p/] I needed her to teach me.[p/] I needed [i]revenge[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eacd9",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I needed..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5cf79",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I [i]really[/i] needed some food.[p/] I'd already gone through all of the dried fish that I'd packed for the journey."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edc827",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "The compass told me that I was still heading west,[p/] but I didn't realize how long it would take to get to Ratholme on foot."
}

{
  "id": "line:00186f1",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I suddenly heard the sound of a distant carriage coming from behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dea1e",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "It wasn't long before the cart passed by me.[p/] The carriage driver glanced at me before doing a double take and yanking at the reins."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b5547",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: Hey...[p/] What are you doing all the way out here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02eac71",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I said nothing.[p/] I just stared blankly at him."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a3d5",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: ...Are you okay?[p/] Where are your parents?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02404f1",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...They're gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0699a32",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "The man scratched his head and scanned the surrounding forest."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e25f",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I need to go to Ratholme.[p/] I need to find Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a7a5a",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: Wait,[p/] that criminal lawyer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78c1b",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's my family's lawyer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2a69a",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: Oh...[p/] Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08cca3c",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: I'm going to be passing by Ratholme.[p/] You should probably come with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cdd0b",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: We can get you to the City Watch.[p/] They probably know how to help a kid like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01023bf",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "I wasn't interested in meeting more knights,[p/] but at this rate,[p/] I was going to starve."
}

{
  "id": "line:0420477",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Without a word,[p/] I climbed into the back of his carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:022feb3",
  "node": "AfterCafe8",
  "text": "Peasant: Kid looks like he's half dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:095bea7",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "I was startled awake.[p/] My face was covered in sweat."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b97a2",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "It took me a while before I realized that it had just been a nightmare."
}

{
  "id": "line:0535f83",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "I rubbed my eyes.[p/] There were dried tears crusted into them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee2a59",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Damn it all..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bbb3b",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "It had been a long time since I'd stopped having those nightmares."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c21d5",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Being in this city was digging up memories that I'd moved on from.[p/] All the more reason to leave as soon as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:075b1c4",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] are you up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad6053",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Celeste: H-[p/][s/]Huh?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b892b5",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "She'd been wistfully staring outside the tavern window,[p/] but her body twitched the moment I called out to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4c6db",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a50b1",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ebfc3",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Celeste: You just startled me... [h=\"He wasn't awake.|...Was he?\" e=\"hf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0426c",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "There was clearly something else,[p/] but she didn't seem keen on sharing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b692d3",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you know if the city is still on lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09060ec",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/]I haven't checked yet.[p/] I was waiting for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c7617",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "We arrived at the city gates.[p/] It was still being blocked by the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5cf86",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "If anything,[p/] it looked like they'd doubled the number of knights there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6a761",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "I really didn't like where this was going..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6396",
  "node": "AfterCafe9",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Do you want to head to the Café again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b3965",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] We'll just have to wait this out."
}

{
  "id": "line:087723f",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "...And just as we turned around,[p/] we saw Rika running towards us from a block away."
}

{
  "id": "line:075b632",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06229ae",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "She broke out into a sprint,[p/] nearly tripping over as she slipped on the wet city streets."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bfc3d",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "She looked exhausted,[p/] and her clothes were drenched.[p/] She'd been out in the rain for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2b13",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion![p/][s/] It's terrible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e0b27",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: T-[p/][s/]There was an accident at the Arcane Refinery last night!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f53cba",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: One of my friends who worked there...[p/] He fell into a vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:053d71d",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: He's...[p/] dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:067121a",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, Rika...[p/] I'm so sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b73b",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Tyrion: If there's anything I can do—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7889b",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: The Duke is blaming the Dracogen Trading Company!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e062d5",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: He's trying to charge the owner with criminal negligence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b62782",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "As the lord of this region,[p/] it was House von Sanctus's responsibility to carry out the law."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a5207",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "But the Duke was obviously just taking this opportunity to attack one of his rivals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c31536",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion...[p/] You're a famous lawyer, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0726ff6",
  "node": "AfterCafe10",
  "text": "Mosourika: Can you help them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff9dce",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] don't think I can."
}

{
  "id": "line:095cbb5",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/] B-[p/]But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:061c848",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] I specialize in homicides,[p/] and most of my clients are [i]mages[/i] who've been charged with murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5a383",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: There isn't any magic involved in what happened.[p/] There isn't even a killer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0814c1e",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: T-[p/][s/]That's not true![p/][s/] I saw it happen!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd111f",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: I didn't see who did it,[p/] but I saw someone cast a spell at him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f3e16",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: It pushed him into the vat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4980",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Celeste: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039229b",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How sure are you of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a37ed",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: I-[p/][s/]I don't know...[p/] It all happened really fast."
}

{
  "id": "line:020f948",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "I took a deep breath.[p/] Even [i]she[/i] didn't seem that sure of what she saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:02245ad",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know what kind of spell it was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0605424",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: I-[p/][s/]I don't know![p/][s/] But it was powerful enough to break everything around it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b70d85",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "That definitely sounded too distinct.[p/] She must have seen [i]something[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:064a0e0",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay.[p/] I'll head to the refinery and see what I can do."
}

{
  "id": "line:055b8d3=",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b8c73",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Tyrion: But don't get your hopes up.[p/] I don't have a lot of information to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0200874",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's fine![p/][s/] I'll let Dracogen know that you're on your way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f96df4",
  "node": "AfterCafe11",
  "text": "...This week was just getting worse by the minute."
}

{
  "id": "line:06595e2",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika, are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0062621",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ha![p/][s/] Do you even need to ask?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8a512",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Mosourika: Of course I'm not okay!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022eb97",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Mosourika: This place is crawling with knights and nobles!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cb2bd",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand your reservations,[p/] but there's nothing to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f30877",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're just here to watch the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d339",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Stefanic: I really appreciate you coming to testify, Ms. Tudor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44371",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Stefanic: I can imagine it's difficult for you to return here again."
}

{
  "id": "line:006bdf6",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Stefanic: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9a9b6",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Stefanic: My apologies.[p/] Perhaps I've said too much."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0c3c",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Mosourika: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Let's just get this over with..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bc1f5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is now in session for the trial of Stefanic Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5656f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution is ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a9b0e",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "TYRION: The defense is also ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4992",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: Very well.[p/] Prosecutor Steelwind,[p/] could you please list the charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a742",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Stefanic Dracogen is the owner of the Dracogen Trading Company,[p/] located in the city of Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0cb1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: His company has many business ventures in Aurinax and Ratholme,[p/] but his business is most known for the production of artificery devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d9e88",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Judge: Ah,[p/] I thought I recognized the name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0881ba1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Judge: I'm quite pleased with my Dracogen brand dishwasher."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ae32d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Be that as it may, Your Honor,[p/] Mr. Dracogen is charged with criminal negligence resulting in death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3c8dc",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The accident occurred within the Aurinax Arcane Refinery owned by his company."
}

{
  "id": "line:03afde5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The victim: Justin Waye,[p/] leaned against a damaged guardrail,[p/] causing it to break."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c535a5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: As a result,[p/] he fell into a vat of volatile chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ffd6",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Attempts were made to save him,[p/] but by the time they could neutralize the vat,[p/] he was already dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0155ba5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Judge: That's certainly a very gruesome way to go."
}

{
  "id": "line:035811b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant displayed clear negligence in maintaining the refinery's facilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0601d03",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: As such,[p/] the responsibility for Mr. Waye's death falls squarely on his shoulders."
}

{
  "id": "line:074b87d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] This case isn't nearly as mundane as the prosecution is making it out to be."
}

{
  "id": "line:054f9f8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Justin Waye didn't fall into that vat because of a faulty guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a64e02",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He fell because he was pushed off the catwalk by an arcane spell!"
}

{
  "id": "line:010dbcc",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] are you trying to say that the victim was murdered?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038a0b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: ...One of the witnesses claims that they saw a spell hit Mr. Waye before he fell into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e90592",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: However,[p/] that testimony is completely contradicted by the lack of magic traces found anywhere near the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f022f0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you're so confident, Steelwind,[p/] why don't we bring said witness onto the stand so she can testify herself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0956652",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Fine.[p/] Let's hear what she has to say.[p/] But I'm sure you know that even [i]she[/i] has no idea what she saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0776362",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness.[p/] Please state your name and occupation for the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6825c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "She seemed to be okay,[p/] but she looked pretty nervous in the lobby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aab088",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "I only hoped that this wouldn't be too much for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cef6ce",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Fufufu...[p/] So you seek the title of the death-bringer songstress."
}

{
  "id": "line:072a1a9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Scaled Lord...[p/][s/] Was she seriously going to do that [i]here[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f04937",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9042",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I lie between life and death—[p/]heaven and hell.[p/] None are worthy of my name,[p/] so consider this a courtesy."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e31c3",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I am Mosourika Tudor![p/][s/] Mage of [b]Evocation[/b] and the Ashen Lord of Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3203",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Judge: I wasn't aware that our kingdom had a title like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be2be6",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Judge: The world has really changed a lot in recent years."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e3c11",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Your Honor...[p/] The witness is a business owner in Aurinax.[p/] She runs a café."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f7fdb",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Judge: Why would the Ashen Lord of Aurinax run a café?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1f738",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ah,[p/] I ask myself that same question every day."
}

{
  "id": "line:003a473",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Rika, could you please not do this right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ef970",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: It helps me cope, okay?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068932f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]*ahem*[/i][p/] Ms. Tudor, can you please testify about what you saw at the refinery that morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098c00a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: And I think we could [i]all[/i] do without the verbal flourishes."
}

{
  "id": "line:060b81f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Ugh...[p/] Fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1cd06",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: I was delivering food to Justin that morning,[p/] but I didn't see him anywhere in the freight area."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb283c",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: I went looking for him and spotted him on the catwalk.[p/] He looked like he was talking to someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e36f6c",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's when I saw a flash of magical light.[p/] Justin got blasted with a spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:020ebc1",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: It ripped apart the guardrail he was leaning on,[p/] and he fell into that vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0175718",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: I told one of the workers what happened.[p/] They tried to save him,[p/] but I guess it was too late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd875c",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "AriaC: I'm sure Mr. Cuthbert has told you this, witness,[p/] but we didn't find any traces of magic near the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:073b636",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Mosourika: I [i]know[/i] what I saw![p/] Someone definitely used magic on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f8af4",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "She seemed very sure of that.[p/] She definitely wasn't lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc9777",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "But I still couldn't figure out why there weren't any traces of magic there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0606ff3",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "And there was something...[p/] [i]off[/i] about something she said,[p/] but I wasn't sure what."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8cde9",
  "node": "RikaTest",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] you may begin your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:092bc62",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is he normally in the freight area when you make your deliveries?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5427f",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] but I guess he was doing something in the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:08534bb",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to Dracogen,[p/] the victim only worked in the freight department."
}

{
  "id": "line:072e630",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: He definitely wasn't doing his job when he was in the refinery building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f324e5",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you have any idea why he was there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f05c29",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: I-[p/][s/]I don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ea7b9",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: He didn't talk much about what he did,[p/] so I just assumed he was [i]supposed[/i] to be there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84184",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see who he was talking to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b37fa4",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: No, they were too high up,[p/] and the catwalk was blocking them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb6da2",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: But he looked kind of angry.[p/] He also looked a little scared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b703e2",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:012cdd2",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think he was talking to the thief?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0572fbe",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: He might have spotted them robbing my client's office."
}

{
  "id": "line:017450a",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: That is purely speculation on your part, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0509d28",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: At the very least,[p/] you'd need a witness to even entertain that theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2c144",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: And the current witness didn't see who the victim was talking to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515584",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Judge: I'm compelled to agree, Ms. Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fe0a7",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you been able to figure out what kind of spell he got hit with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0884d72",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: No...[p/] I've been thinking,[p/] but I've never seen a spell like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e55ea",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: My expertise is in [b]evocation[/b] magic,[p/] and that spell looked completely different from the spells I can cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca3e16",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: May I remind the court that the Inquisition found no traces of [b]evocation[/b] magic at the scene of Mr. Waye's death?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093f3f5",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: An [b]evocation[b/] couldn't have ripped that guardrail apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5969a",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which can only a mean that a spell from a [i]different[/i] school of magic broke it."
}

{
  "id": "line:093596f",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]Or[/i] the witness is simply grieving and doesn't remember what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0116f72",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: We have records that show that the guardrail was damaged and in need of repair."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c626a4",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client's contractors assured him that the damage wasn't severe."
}

{
  "id": "line:01316b5",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: Yet, the guardrail broke apart anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:013b1c0",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: If you want to posit that a spell broke the guardrail,[p/] you'll have to prove it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02563d9",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: It ripped apart the guardrail he was leaning on, and he fell into that vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9c678",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: A magical expanding prism ripped apart the guardrail he was leaning on, and he fell into that vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b6f83",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: It ripped apart the guardrail he was leaning on.[p/] After that,[p/] he tried to catch himself on it and fell into that vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f991",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: It violently and instantly ripped apart the guardrail he was leaning on.[p/] He fell into that vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f1108",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did they try to save him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0107f8d",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: The chemicals that the victim fell into were extremely volatile and corrosive."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e9d46",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: They poured a neutralizing solution into the vat to keep it from eating away at any implement they used to fish him out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9eb76",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "AriaC: The downside of this process was that it took far too long before they could remove the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a8144",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I thought those chemicals were just toxic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8769b",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Are you telling me those dissolved him while he was still alive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e4d62",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "I winced.[p/] I really wanted to avoid letting her find out about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfba99",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Judge: ...Perhaps, we should move on."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c6b89",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Player: Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1dee",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Celeste: Her testimony is the best piece of evidence we have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c02759",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Celeste: Is it really a good idea to find a contradiction in it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a64252",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even [i]she[/i] doesn't know what happened,[p] and there's something nagging at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:023190d",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I can find it,[p/] it will put us one step closer to the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acc9b0",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Celeste: If you say so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b41f2",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "I would just need to look at the details she's testifying about and find out what doesn't fit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d91b60",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Player: Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:040854c",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] It's clear that the witness's testimony is contradictory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0758ae2",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this piece of evidence proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a6eef",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Judge: I fail to see how that proves anything, Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6ec94",
  "node": "Cross_Rika",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf6a5",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know this must be difficult for you,[p/] but can you remember any more details about the moment Justin fell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0def23b",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: I guess I'd need to know what details you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d8e4b",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "What did the spell look like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d02b9",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did this spell look like?[p/] Any detail might help us identify it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d3846",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: I don't know.[p/] I only saw it for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:0881821",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: It didn't look like an explosion or anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fcde3",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "AriaC: A prism?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c4d53",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah, it had really sharp edges like a cube."
}

{
  "id": "line:091a009",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: But it was wider than it was tall."
}

{
  "id": "line:0390759",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: Witness, could you add this detail to your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc03b",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4b78",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "How did the spell affect Justin?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c65208",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did the spell do to Justin?[p/] How did it affect him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063b03c",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Um...[p/] After that flash of light,[p/] it looked like he lost his balance."
}

{
  "id": "line:040d5f7",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: He tried to catch himself on the guardrail,[p/] but it was already broken apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:058b74b",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: He fell right into the vat of chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5d27",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "AriaC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0200888",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "How did the spell affect the guardrail?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa837c",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did the spell do to the guardrail?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067886b",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: Like I said,[p/] it ripped apart the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a778ac",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did it do that, though?[p/] Did the spell slowly break it apart?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d33216",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "Mosourika: No,[p/] it happened instantly.[p/] It was kind of like what happens when you pull a rubber band so hard that it snaps."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2d20",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "So the spell broke the guardrail instantly?[p/] It must have been some kind of instantaneous effect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a30d96",
  "node": "PressRika",
  "text": "But we already knew that there weren't any traces of [b]evocation[/b] on the catwalk.[p/] So what kind of spell did the mage use?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00604ee",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika, there's something off about your testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4de8c",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: Really?[p/] It's the same as what I told you before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0643b96",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The mistake was mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210093",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was so focused on trying to figure out [i]what[/i] that spell was and who cast it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0620cfd",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't even think about what it actually did to Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf547a",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: This whole time,[p/] we assumed that the spell pushed him into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701ecc",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But how could it have pushed him into the vat if he only fell [i]after[/i] the guardrails had been ripped apart?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2f142",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d19a8d",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika, you said that Justin fell because he tried to catch himself on the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb32f",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought the spell had pushed Justin while simultaneously ripping the guardrails apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26922",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it didn't push Justin at all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0234bcc",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: I guess that makes sense,[p/] but does that really change anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e7f7e",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It does![p/][s/] Because it raises another question:"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b36d46",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: If the spell produced enough force to rip the guardrails apart,[p/] why didn't it appear to affect Justin at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09acb80",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: It didn't appear to affect the victim because there [i]was[/i] no spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51694",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Justin Waye broke the guardrail because it was faulty."
}

{
  "id": "line:094671e",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: No![p/][s/] I saw it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7f6d9",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: He only fell in because the guardrail was already destroyed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cc705",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor,[p/][s/] the defense brought this witness to testify,[p/] only to contradict it during their own cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0491973",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: They [i]have[/i] no case."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a6bfb",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: My witness is certain that she saw a spell destroy the guardrail!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0806414",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Your witness is a business associate of the defendant![p/][s/] She clearly has every reason to lie in her testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0922825",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: So are you baselessly accusing my witness of perjury, Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0202b7f",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "AriaC: I am.[p/] It's not as if this is her first time breaking the law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6e40c",
  "node": "RikaObj",
  "text": "Mosourika: U-[p/][s/]Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07328",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Ms. Tudor,[p/] I understand that you run a café in the food district."
}

{
  "id": "line:07769cf",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: This café would not exist without the generous patronage of the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:096159f",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:089d0a2",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: You must feel quite indebted to him.[p/] After all,[p/] he saved you from the kind of life you lived before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f20b25",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Rika, what is she talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02eddc9",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: You truly didn't know, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0175e16",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Before your witness ran her café,[p/] she had another vocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0164864",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: She survived by robbing the shipments coming into Aurinax Harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acc17c",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika...[p/] T-[p/][s/]That's not true, is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4cbc3",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...So many things changed after you left, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:00abfa7",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Several years ago,[p/] Ms. Tudor was a part of a band of thieves who would frequently rob shipments addressed to Von Sanctus Industries."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c3e7a",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Her group was eventually arrested,[p/] and she only avoided a sentence to the dungeons by taking a plea deal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6fd8e",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3916f",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "Did she seriously do all of that in the years I was gone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06de4b4",
  "node": "RikaObj2",
  "text": "I knew her.[p/] I grew up with her.[p/] Had things really changed that much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011a9f7",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Even so,[p/] the defense still maintains trust in the witness's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:092f640",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I believe the Mistweaving Phantom struck the refinery that morning.[p/] They attacked Justin Waye with magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac8b0a",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1890a",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Is that so?[p/] And how do you know that the [i]current witness[/i] isn't this Phantom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0471636",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Mosourika: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccbcea",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: She was coincidentally present when the robbery occurred,[p/] [i]and[/i] she's a registered mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26217",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Not to mention that her little gang all those years ago used that same name."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ecaf8",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33646",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "...I'd always thought that nickname sounded too much like something she'd come up with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0464691",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Was she seriously involved with them?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d3391",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: I thought you never backed down from a foe, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e03d2",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: You could make a great case for your client by indicting Ms. Tudor in the robberies and subsequently the victim's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a0da",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: What will you do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0441017",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "No...[p/] There could be any number of explanations for what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6687b",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Urban myths tended to be distorted by the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb28f0",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "It's possible people have just been calling this thief the Mistweaving Phantom because of the similarities between the robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8b4fd",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The defense has no further questions for the witness.[p/] She is dismissed."
}

{
  "id": "line:047c9ea",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Hmph...[p/] I'd thought you were more objective than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa809",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't care what she's done in the past."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd5e97",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know my friend,[p/] and I know she's not a murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f46e02",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Clearly.[p/] What happened that morning was the result of simple negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d24e1",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor.[p/] For our next witness,[p/] the prosecution would like to call Orym White to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0a03",
  "node": "RikaObj3",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] Bailiff,[p/] please call the Inquisition Commander to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0004ad1",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "AriaC: Commander, as I'm sure you've heard,[p/] Mr. Cuthbert is trying to connect the accident to the robberies of the Mistweaving Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:089a777",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "AriaC: Please testify about the City Watch's findings regarding the robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bb85e",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: Sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:065c977",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: So this Phantom's been hitting a lot of places—[p/]mostly shipments coming into the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0558804",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: Doesn't matter what kind of lock or security the place has,[p/] he can get in no problem."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc8747",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: He's made off with a bunch of loot,[p/] and the City Watch has been scratching their heads looking for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f94756",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: I know you think the guy hit the refinery too,[p/] but it doesn't match with what we know about him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0807e2e",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "Orym: The guy only stole some documents and left the defendant's gold.[p/] This guy never does that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d353e",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "The connection between the Mistweaving Phantom and Justin's death was already difficult to prove."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e0d0e",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "There was no evidence,[p/] but they [i]had[/i] to be related somehow.[p/] It would be too much of a coincidence otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f55b02",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "How could I prove that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0795cf2",
  "node": "OrymTest",
  "text": "JUDGE: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] You may begin your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b387",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is usually stolen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b05aa",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: All kinds of things:[p/] goods,[p/] appliances,[p/] weapons,[p/] even some artificery devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed4de",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Not to mention there's that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec3f9",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: To amend the commander's testimony,[p/] there was a sensitive shipment stolen from a kingdom ship."
}

{
  "id": "line:011aa38",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Judge: Is there any reason why you're being so vague, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95a44",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: The gag order has come from the Grand General himself.[p/] The item in question is not relevant to this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a78a",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:090bbac",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you referring to the Phantom as a \"he\"?[p/] I thought the City Watch didn't know anything about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:024572b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: ...Are you seriously nitpicking me for that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1158a",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just think it would be in the court's interest not to have assumptions taken as fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e81c3d",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Scaled Lord,[p/] you kids these days and your pronouns."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fadc72",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Look...[p/] Chances are,[p/] that this guy's a guy.[p/] The stats back me up on that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0310911",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, yeah?[p/][s/] How many of your [i]men[/i] did it take to arrest me, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f52d3",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Celeste,[p/] while I appreciate your sentiment,[p/] I wouldn't brag about that here."
}

{
  "id": "line:06701ee",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Fine![p/][s/] If it will get all of you off my back,[p/] I'll change my damned testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b597a9",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Doesn't matter what kind of lock or security the place has,[p/] [i]they[/i] can get in no problem."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b81d07",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: See,[p/] was that so hard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a67a2",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Oh, bite me, mage girl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9f154",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] how sophisticated were the locks and security on the places that were broken into?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deb2e6",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: The places owned by the smaller merchants only had mundane locks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21746",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Those are hard to pick,[p/] but not impossible for someone who knows what they're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b52381",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: But they've also been hitting the ships owned by nobles—[p/]not to mention that other ship I'm not allowed to discuss."
}

{
  "id": "line:0877de7",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: They've got magical locks and security.[p/] Picking those would be like performing surgery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07d19",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: That's not even mentioning all the armed guards they probably had to get past."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ab8d",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Whoever they are,[p/] they're some kind of genius."
}

{
  "id": "line:0617c8a",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: He's made off with a bunch of loot, and the City Watch has been scratching their heads looking for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5983",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: They made off with a bunch of loot, and the City Watch has been scratching their heads looking for them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6dad8",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: I know you think the... person hit the refinery too,[p/] but it doesn't match with what we know about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0585b6c",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: The thief who hit the refinery only stole some documents and left the defendant's gold.[p/] This guy never does that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5cdee",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: The thief who hit the refinery only stole some documents and left the defendant's gold.[p/] This... person never does that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0818",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: His argument is a little weak.[p/] I doubt the theft at the refinery was just a coincidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:079281b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: But he has a point.[p/] The serial robber never leaves any evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcc440",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: There's nothing to tie him to theft that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:093feed",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are they really having that much trouble identifying the thief?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f8f24",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: They're good at covering their tracks.[p/] They don't leave any evidence,[p/] and they never trip any alarms."
}

{
  "id": "line:065504b",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: Half the time,[p/] it's like they're disappearing into thin air."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aa2d4",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: He's good at covering his tracks.[p/] He doesn't leave any evidence,[p/] and he never trips any alarms."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dad3a",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: Half the time,[p/] it's like he's disappearing into thin air."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aab92",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Could the Phantom be a mage proficient in [b]conjuration[/b] magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab7e35",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They could be teleporting to bypass any security altogether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f482",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: ...Maybe,[p/] but most security systems are designed to detect and block teleportation inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0197c3f",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: You can't teleport inside unless you already have some kind of magical beacon already in the place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79d95",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: Not to mention that the locks leading inside were obviously picked and unlocked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f007",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: If anything,[p/] these systems don't prevent teleportation [i]out[/i] of its field."
}

{
  "id": "line:09af360",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Orym: So maybe they're using [b]conjuration[/b] magic to get out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf6b9e",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I doubt a place like the Arcane Refinery would have a system as sophisticated as that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbf9fd",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f19c41",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Orym: The thief has been robbing a lot of merchant ships.[p/] Some of them even belong to Von Sanctus Industries."
}

{
  "id": "line:095e229",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Orym: Places like the Arcane Refinery probably have [i]some[/i] gold.[p/] The owner even mentioned he had some coins in the safe that got broken into."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b756f6",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Orym: But all that is below this Phantom's paygrade."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be46e0",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Orym: Some of the things the Phantom stole were worth ten times the amount of gold in that safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:049feab",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress2",
  "text": "Orym: That's not even mentioning the fact that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:077ddb9",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sometimes information can be more valuable than gold, Commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0044e06",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Orym: Maybe,[p/] but I don't think our guy would risk so much for a couple of business documents."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d2dd",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Orym: Your client might have some enemies,[p/] but the Phantom's good enough to hit the merchant ships guarded by armed soldiers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9e0d4",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Orym: Every time they hit a place,[p/] they run the risk of getting caught."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbfbbf",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Orym: The theft happened this morning when the refinery was already open.[p/] Employees were already on the ground, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b479c",
  "node": "Cross_OrymPress3",
  "text": "Orym: Anyone could have spotted him.[p/] It just doesn't make sense for the phantom to take a risk like that for so little gain."
}

{
  "id": "line:05297de",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander,[p/] it's clear you think the Phantom wouldn't have gone to all that trouble to steal a few business records."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acd459",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] it doesn't make any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7e0f5",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: This person has enough skills to break into heavily guarded buildings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0428e92",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: Why would they bother with some business records?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb2ec3",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: This guy has enough skills to break into heavily guarded buildings."
}

{
  "id": "line:076fd0b",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: Why would he bother with some business records?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5593d",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's where you're wrong, Orym."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dca07e",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: ...Kid,[p/] why do you always have to do this to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d73fc",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's another series of thefts where nothing inherently valuable was taken."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ab3f9",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Mistweaving Phantom also broke into many of the offices owned by the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0628821",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Again,[p/] you're assuming that the Phantom broke into said offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fd336",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: It's entirely plausible that a refinery employee who was a part of the union stole from both of these offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cdb13",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: A union member may have been able to access my client's office,[p/] but they wouldn't have such an easy time entering the union offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:062cfdf",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Many of the unions have anticipated sabotage and have invested in state-of-the-art security systems."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cfffa",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: They've taken precautions to make sure that only high-ranking officials have access to these documents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5fe55",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one person with the skills to break into these locations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26501",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that's the [i]same[/i] thief who's been robbing those ships in the Aurinax Harbor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8bbf8",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: And what possible motive would the Phantom have to steal these documents?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3d42",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's simple![p/][s/] They wanted detailed information on my client's company and the workers' unions!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ada8d",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: In all of your wild speculation,[p/] I think you haven't considered one possibility, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c618bf",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And what's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0820e1a",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: That the unions themselves were the ones who robbed your client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0878bda",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: You said it yourself:[p/] only high-ranking executives had access to the union documents that went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:066e217",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: And none of those executives knew any spells that could rip apart the guardrail.[p/] None of them were even mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b47c33",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's ridiculous.[p/] Why would the workers' unions rob themselves?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08053bd",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Simple,[p/] they wanted to cover their tracks and play the victim when [i]they[/i] were the true culprits."
}

{
  "id": "line:098c51e",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: After all,[p/] we have several reports confirming hostility between your client and the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:005e96a",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think you'll find that those reports are exagerrated,[p/] if not entirely false."
}

{
  "id": "line:0082f51",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client and Noah Morrison can testify to that fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2c10",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: They obviously would.[p/] An employee just died due to your client's negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:095ae50",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Dracogen has every reason to feign amicability with the unions.[p/] It would avoid further outrage."
}

{
  "id": "line:099548b",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: And Noah Morrison has no choice but to do the same—[p/]lest he be incriminated in the thefts himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f5b38",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And what proof do you have that they aren't telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b155b",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: As I've said,[p/] I have several reports from many different individuals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0add738",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: They came from multiple, diverse sources,[p/] and they all paint a very vivid picture of aggression between your client and the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39d40",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Furthermore,[p/] they are far less biased than Stefanic Dracogen or Noah Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:07765ef",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "She had a point,[p/] and I couldn't claim the reports were false without any proof."
}

{
  "id": "line:060a08a",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you want to implicate Mr. Morrison,[p/] I think it's only fair that he be allowed to defend himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:00096c9",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Fine.[p/] Let him testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be52e1",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: But it will be his word against dozens."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f7a1",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Judge: It appears that both counsels are in agreement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0814604",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff,[p/] please escort Mr. Morrison to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f141f",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0460ef3",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Aye...[p/] My name's Noah Morrison.[p/] I'm the harbourmaster of Aurinax Harbor and Union Chief of the Aurinax Industrial Union."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a7be3",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you for taking the stand today, Mr. Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b7700",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: As you know,[p/] there was a theft that occurred at the refinery this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcfeb0",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution is trying to imply that you may have been involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1df64",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Yeah...[p/] I heard."
}

{
  "id": "line:031e905",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you please testify about the thefts that occurred at the union offices?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf16e4",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear you also believe they're related to the theft at the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faa391",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Any details that might help us prove that would help a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0499059",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Alright..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e06d0e",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: I don't know where all these reports of \"hostile tensions\" came from,[p/] but everything's great between Dracogen and us."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c7f1e",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Whoever this Phantom is,[p/] they've got nothing to do with that nonsense.[p/] They've been hitting everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ac63e",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: It's not just our offices and the ships.[p/] They broke into some of the union members' homes, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:030551b",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Those poor blokes had everything stolen from them.[p/] They even had to skip town because of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbac7b",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: They were good people too—[p/]solid,[p/] law-abiding citizens."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b28f",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: As you can see,[p/] Mr. Morrison had very little motive to break into my client's office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6a94e",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: The serial thief, meanwhile,[p/] has been robbing people all over the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c941e",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: ...That's assuming the witness's testimony is true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6b714",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: Take a look at the crime reports!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09544ab",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Noah: You'll see that a lot of the victims were members of the union!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccd9d1",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: I unfortunately don't have access to the reports for those."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67eaa",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you talking about?[p/] You're a prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7fdb",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why wouldn't you have access to those reports?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037ba84",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I'm not certain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf28c1",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: I imagine it's related to the theft that occurred on the imperial ship this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26114",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "That was strange...[p/] Who would have the authority to prevent a Steelwind from accessing those records?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05aff11",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: In any case,[p/] Aurinax is a large city with an average rate of crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a6e7c",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: There's nothing to prove that any of [i]those[/i] thefts are related to this either."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9cb8",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "AriaC: There isn't even anything that proves these thefts are related to [i]each other[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:081d49b",
  "node": "NoahTest",
  "text": "We would see about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:094211e",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: ...So you say."
}

{
  "id": "line:000c816",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: Look, wherever you're getting these reports,[p/] they're completely wrong!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f877ba",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] these reports came from multiple sources throughout the course of several months."
}

{
  "id": "line:020d324",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: For obvious reasons,[p/] the individuals who made them will remain anonymous."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a0050",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: But said reports came from multiple members of the commonfolk,[p/] aristocracy,[p/] [i]and[/i] law enforcement."
}

{
  "id": "line:024dcbc",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: We also have several crime reports of violent encounters between your union members and the defendant's employees."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc66d",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0440a05",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "What was going on here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6464b",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Mr. Morrison seemed just as confused as I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d152c",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Were these reports falsified,[p/] or were these encounters happening without his knowledge?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc432",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Assuming that these aren't just a string of unrelated thefts."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eee29",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: I'll admit that Aurinax is a large city.[p/] Break-ins weren't exactly non-existent before this."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e963c",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: But all of my colleagues started getting hit [i]after[/i] this Phantom showed up."
}

{
  "id": "line:08310fa",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: That [i]can't[/i] be a coincidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c34825",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: It's entirely possible that availability bias is at work here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bb974",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: People will always try to draw trends between genuine coincidences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79aed",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "She was being annoyingly obtuse about this,[p/] but I wouldn't get anywhere until I could prove she was wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c402ab",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: Were these homes as secure as the union offices?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79bcc",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: Not at all...[p/] We're all just industry workers at the end of the day."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb2f5",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you get such a sophisticated security system for the union offices then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042be1c",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: Ah,[p/] it was a generous donation from some friends we have in the city banking house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c23a4d",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: ...The banking house?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f9049",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: I guess there are some folks there who believe in what we're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:023bc7c",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: Regardless,[p/] that means [i]anyone[/i] could have broken into these houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dd5ee",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "AriaC: It wouldn't require an expert that's as adept at committing robberies as the Phantom is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6e9f3",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: What would motivate them to leave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034a868",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: Aurinax is a hot spot for trade and industry."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c06d8",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: There are lots of jobs here now,[p/] but housing's gotten expensive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7bbbd",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: I'm guessing they had to move somewhere cheaper in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:073e561",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait, you're \"guessing\"?[p/] Did they tell you why they were leaving?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f85e00",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: No,[p/] a lot of them were really down about it.[p/] They didn't seem too eager to say more."
}

{
  "id": "line:029fe28",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: They were good people too—[p/]solid, law-abiding citizens."
}

{
  "id": "line:037dd60",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry that happened.[p/] I'm sure they were great people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bad957",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: It's a damned shame.[p/] They were good people,[p/] and they had families to feed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cb23f",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: Aurinax has been going in such a good direction, too.[p/] Crime's been down,[p/] and employment's been up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1cc91",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Noah: I really wish we could've shared that with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0befe60",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Celeste: I can understand robbing the nobility and even the merchant ships,[p/] but I can't believe they were robbing commoners too."
}

{
  "id": "line:00172bb",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a little strange, honestly.[p/] If they were after valuables,[p/] why would they bother robbing them at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031cf12",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Tyrion: The house of an industrial worker wouldn't have that much to steal—[p/]at least not when compared to the merchant ships."
}

{
  "id": "line:066ba77",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe it was because it was easy?[p/] They probably wouldn't have any kind of magical security."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e91b1",
  "node": "Cross_Noah",
  "text": "Possibly,[p/] but that still felt strange to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:014a57c",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "I really didn't want to contradict Mr. Morrison,[p/] but this was the only piece I had left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdd1f0",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "There was nothing else that tied the robberies together,[p/] and I still didn't have a full idea of what the Phantom's motive was."
}

{
  "id": "line:084ebdf",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "But I had to do this.[p/] It was the only way to find out what was really going on in my city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76e28",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Mr. Morrison.[p/] You said that the targets of the thefts were law-abiding citizens."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be09f9",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unfortunately,[p/] that's not entirely true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0363d6c",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09142db",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: I knew most of them.[p/] They were good people."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d0447",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That may be,[p/] but there's one unfortunate fact that tied them all together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0012040",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: They were all later arrested for treason against the Crown!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09df07e",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0448bb6",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "AriaC: That's ridiculous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff5c58",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "AriaC: There have been [i]no[/i] reports of that sort submitted to the City Watch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0086cc4",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: What you're saying is crazy, my boy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f03e6",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: I've known these people![p/][s/] Some of them were close friends of mine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0880874",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Noah: They would have never gotten mixed up in that kind of business!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb08c7",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry, Mr. Morrison,[p/] but I've heard otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6383b",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Mistweaving Phantom hasn't just been stealing valuable items."
}

{
  "id": "line:05912d2",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: They've been specifically targeting citizens who were secretly plotting against the kingdom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b6ac5",
  "node": "NoahObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're part of a larger plot that involves everyone in the city of Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0e01d",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: What are you even basing this off of, anyways?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bae8ad",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: This testimony came directly from Lloyd von Sanctus:[p/] the Duke of Commerce and the ruling lord of Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04334fa",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Lloyd von Sanctus gave you this information."
}

{
  "id": "line:054eebe",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's right, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb495",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Lloyd von Sanctus:[p/] the plaintiff of this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0906b3b",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:028d5d1",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Lloyd von Sanctus:[p/] the man who would have every reason to have you fail."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6a57",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a9834",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I-[p/][s/]I may have miscalculated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1be27",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: But you seem to be so confident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0006560",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Perhaps we should have the plaintiff testify so we can know for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:017a456",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "...Did von Sanctus really set me up?![p/] How could I fall for something like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071d4d8",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "But it made so much sense![p/][s/] The Phantom's targets,[p/][s/] the false reports of hostilities—[p/][s/]all of it seemed to be tied together by some greater plot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067615b",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be a kernel of truth to what he'd told us earlier!"
}

{
  "id": "line:009e9cc",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Maybe he was telling the truth earlier...[p/] He might testify honestly if we called him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eef982",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "No...[p/] These charges against Dracogen were laid by [i]him[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:000efd8",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Even if he [i]had[/i] told us the truth earlier,[p/] he'd never sabotage his own case by taking the stand now."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bf42e",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Judge: We will contact the Duke of Commerce and ask if he's willing to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:0019ff3",
  "node": "NoahObj2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Although,[p/] I can already imagine what his answer will be."
}

{
  "id": "line:029967c",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Without warning,[p/] a large man pushed open the doors to the courtroom and marched towards the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fadf7",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Mr. Morrison sputtered a grunt of confusion before he was quickly carried out of the room by two knights who had accompanied him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0ac50",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "The man had a large figure that was only dwarfed by the gigantic battle axe he was holding in his hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2dd31",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "He was covered in scars,[p/] and he held the jaded expression of someone who lived in death and combat."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e2158",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "His uniform was similar to the prosecutor's clothing...[p/] Could he be who I thought he was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfa207",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Lucio: Lloyd need not take the stand.[p/] My testimony will suffice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f905f7",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?![p/][s/] Who are—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012cb2c",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "AriaC: F-[p/][s/]Father?![p/][s/] What are you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deb202",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Father\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07388e9",
  "node": "NoahObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]That's[/i] her dad?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2ec0c",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": ":[i]This[/i] was the Grand General of Wyverngarde:[p/] the man responsible for countless deaths in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e304f4",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Von Sanctus suspected that [i]he[/i] was involved in the thefts and false reports."
}

{
  "id": "line:073ae29",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Lucio: I've been watching.[p/] Neither of you will get anywhere at this rate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de657f",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Judge: G-[p/][s/]Grand General,[p/] t-[p/][s/]this is quite unprecedented!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007eae1",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Lucio: ...And?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7ad2",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Judge: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9cf6",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "It looked like the judge ran through a thousand possible responses in his head before he simply swallowed his fear and stayed silent."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ffd21",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Father...[p/][s/] Why are you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019b992",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Lucio: Again with that?[p/][s/] I will not accept insubordination[p/]—even from you, Prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5d231",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Grand General Steelwind,[p/] why have you interrupted this trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0686d09",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Lucio: To give testimony that will substantiate the defense's claims."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e99f0",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:076880c",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: You can't just—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3257",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor,[p/] do something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0442655",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Judge: No...[p/] I think I'm okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7b801",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "What was he [i]doing[/i]?![p/][s/] None of this made any sense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09697eb",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Lucio: I hear no objections.[p/] I'll be giving my testimony now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7a28a",
  "node": "NoahObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] what—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e1ea8",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "Lucio: This thief has been striking the houses of multiple commoners,[p/] seemingly at random. [h=\"Or so it would seem...\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c0f45",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "Lucio: And without fail,[p/] the City Watch was called to the scene of the crime. [h=\"Within hours of the|crime being discovered...\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a54863",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "Lucio: As the prosecutor said,[p/] it was clear someone other than the victims was reporting these robberies. [h=\"Perhaps a bystander|truly did make the report.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed1ea3",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "Lucio: And after searching each scene,[p/] the City Watch found evidence of treason within their homes. [h=\"The so-called evidence was poorly hidden,| if at all.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:089cad1",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "Lucio: These individuals were arrested by my men,[p/] and placed into my custody in secret. [h=\"However...|They were clearly not guilty of treason.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b749a1",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "...Why was I seeing so many of his thoughts?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b3ab6",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus only worked on targets who were unguarded or emotionally stressed,[p/][s/] and [i]he[/i] looked like the least stressed person in the room right now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06057c8",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "I guess it didn't matter [i]who[/i] the witness was.[p/] This was just another cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:006cd65",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": ":I just needed to do what I've always done:[p/] pull the truth out of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e128d",
  "node": "LucioTest",
  "text": "...I just hoped I could get through this without being charged with treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:07da00e",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or so it would seem, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a23ce",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cae16d",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] Please refrain from contradicting the witness without cause!"
}

{
  "id": "line:097ac27",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was just...[p/] interpreting the meaning behind his words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feb932",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear he thinks there's some relation between the thefts."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cb736",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: Am I wrong, Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0393ed6",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: Hm...[p/] I suppose not."
}

{
  "id": "line:069e9f7",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: And without fail,[p/] the City Watch was called to the scene of the crime. [h=\"Within hours of the crime being discovered...\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eae689",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: With the serial robber on the loose,[p/] the City Watch must have been getting a lot of these calls."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f4cd6",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Yes.[p/] The City Watch recognized a trend."
}

{
  "id": "line:0befc61",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: At some point,[p/] they arrived in anticipation of what they'd find."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73645",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: ...It was all so carefully orchestrated—[p/]each piece perfectly falling in succession."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3595",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: I'm not sure what you mean by that, Fa—[p/] Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bcdc1",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: You've never stopped to ask yourself why... [h=\"It was far too convenient...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c12972",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: For one thing—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a2443",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: ...The victim isn't always the one to report a crime like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:026aada",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: More often than not,[p/] it's a passing neighbor that calls it in."
}

{
  "id": "line:009fb03",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: A lot of the reports were made by people who spotted a suspicious person leaving the premises."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ea06",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: And did these people make themselves known after the arrest?[p/][s/] Did they provide testimony beyond the original report?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0626e0c",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b28a1",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: These reports were made in-person,[p/] yet each time,[p/] the City Watch was unable to find the individual who made the report."
}

{
  "id": "line:060935a",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: Is [i]that[/i] normal, Prosecutor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04da3a9",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: And after searching each scene,[p/] the City Watch found evidence of treason within their homes. [h=\"The so-called evidence was poorly hidden,|if at all.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5e650",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that was conveniently discovered each and every time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9e358",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: Yes.[p/] Very easily,[p/] might I add."
}

{
  "id": "line:0271bde",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was it because the evidence was poorly hidden?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4fc77",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: Yes,[p/] it's not uncommon for the disciplined to be so sloppy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a452d",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: Some are even arrogant enough to think they'd never be suspected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0292fbb",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: But the eye of the Crown sees more than you'd think."
}

{
  "id": "line:0347930",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Is [i]that[/i] why I haven't had access to those reports?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0283223",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: It was a precaution.[p/] I didn't want my enemies to see what moves I was making."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e493a",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Morrison testified that these individuals had simply moved out of town."
}

{
  "id": "line:073b883",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: I'm sure it looked like that to him,[p/] and it wasn't too far from the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dedbe4",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Lucio: But they were moved by my men to an undisclosed location."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd7924",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "But from what Mr. Morrison said,[p/] it sounded like he had a chance to say goodbye to them—[p/]Not to mention that their families left with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b76f1e",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "That didn't sound like what would happen if you were arrested for treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cadf3",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "This was...[p/] strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccbc01",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "The contradicting thought was staring me right in the face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed1d1",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "There had to be something more to this—[p/]something I wasn't seeing."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d12e4",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Was it really going to be that easy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fde90e",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The witness's testimony contradicts what he truly thinks!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dfd0f",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert, please refrain from spouting nonsense in the presence of the Grand General and his giant axe!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6202e",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba26b0",
  "node": "CrossLucio",
  "text": "Judge: Enough![p/][s/] I will not ask you again!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5a16",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Judge: M-[p/][s/]Mr. Cuthbert!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039acee",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Judge: I know you have a flair for the dramatic,[p/] but please don't shout such things at the man with the [i]giant axe[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcd262",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] I believe the witness knows more about the arrested individuals than he's letting on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0462887",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Oh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d75c",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:022776d",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "With the way the judge was looking at me,[p/] I'd have thought I was putting my head between the jaws of a lion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99074",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "...But it didn't matter who stood in my way—[p/]a noble,[p/] the Grand General,[p/] or the King himself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06367ca",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "My mother may have been gone,[p/] but there were still people I cared about in Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a087e",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "I wouldn't let the city I grew up in become the site of another one of his bloody massacres!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008d2e2",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio Steelwind![p/][s/] I think you know the individuals you arrested aren't what they were reported to be!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2d3de",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]know[/i] that they weren't guilty of treason!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01222f7",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Lucio: That's correct."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d39cc",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07507a9",
  "node": "LucioObj",
  "text": "AriaC: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:095cca5",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Fa—[p/][s/] [i]Grand General[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb8f40",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Are you [i]admitting[/i] that you arrested these individuals with the knowledge that the charges were false?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0babc65",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: I never said that I arrested them for treason.[p/] I said that I took them into custody."
}

{
  "id": "line:0339b9e",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Judge: B-[p/][s/]But for what reason, Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2e037",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: This \"Phantom\" seems to be targeting certain individuals for some unknown reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed5b83",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: They seem to have targeted both Stefanic Dracogen and the Workers' Unions as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b485e",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Grand General,[p/] there's no evidence that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06931b6",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: It is the truth,[p/] and the evidence must be found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0528be4",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: Your Honor,[p/] suspend this trial to give the defense and prosecution time to investigate the crime further."
}

{
  "id": "line:035c018",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Judge: O-[p/][s/]Of course, Grand General!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6c9f",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Judge: Um...[p/] As per the Grand General's request,[p/] I will be suspending this trial!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071c188",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court proceedings for this case will resume tomorrow morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a66bf",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "Lucio: Make it the next day."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f918b",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court proceedings will resume [i]Wednesday[/i] morning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7fd42",
  "node": "LucioObj2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is adjourned."
}

{
  "id": "line:032897a",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: So...?[p/] Out with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0983f",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: You look like you want to say something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b57e7d",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I didn't know any better,[p/] I would think that you tried to help us back there."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ea1d3",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't imagine you care all that much about workers' rights or my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:005bab5",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I have my reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:034b8c6",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: This thief stole something quite important from an imperial ship this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:01050b8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Your daughter mentioned that it was a threat to national security."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a642",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: It is in my best interests for the item to be found and this \"Mistweaving Phantom\" brought to justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0149b3f",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: But most importantly..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c5632",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: I want to know who they are working for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af7426",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you trying to insinuate that it isn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096d1ef",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Lucio: Is that what you think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7463e",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne",
  "text": "Honestly,[p/] I didn't know [i]what[/i] to think at this point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d282dd",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: You always seem to arrive at the truth when no one else will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0432ca9",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: I've read the court transcripts from your past cases,[p/] so I already had some suspicions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6171",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: And they were all but confirmed when you \"cross-examined\" me today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0533ff7",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: You will figure out what happened this morning,[p/] and you will use your [i]eye[/i] to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f211b8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "I tensed for a moment.[p/] Why did he phrase it like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d07b37",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "His thoughts were so easy to read during his testimony...[p/] Was this some kind of test?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa467d",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well,[p/] I'm sure someone like you would have a great use for an eye like mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b01744",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am [i]so[/i] sorry...[p/][s/] I did not mean it like—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0940acd",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: I understood what you meant."
}

{
  "id": "line:077ceeb",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: Well?[p/] Get to work then.[p/] I'll be waiting for your results."
}

{
  "id": "line:049010b",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't take orders from you, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba76f3",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Lucio: Yet you will still do what I have asked.[p/] It's in your nature."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ed96",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "I exhaled heavily.[p/] The more this mystery unravelled,[p/] the more uncertain I became of everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e12747",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "I really wished Ms. Tymora was here to help me.[p/] I could feel a migraine coming on."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ab052",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey, are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee47b0",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I think I'm just a little exhausted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0946f6a",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's pretty late.[p/] Should we just head back to the inn and continue the investigation tomorrow?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0696f4d",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/]No...[p/] I want to take another look at the refinery before the Inquisition gets there."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c1a91",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "The throbbing pain in my skull seemed to disagree with that course of action."
}

{
  "id": "line:02de0e8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] no.[p/] We're heading back to the inn."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2771",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm fine...[p/] Really."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd0aca",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion, I know you're anxious about the trial,[p/] but you need to get some rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e674f8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "I felt a tinge of irritation,[p/] but I knew she was just looking out for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b48b74",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "But I couldn't rest now—[p/]not with that serial thief on the loose."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df0a5",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d1aa8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not.[p/] You're going to work yourself—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0864bf1",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would you just stay out of my way?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f79aaf",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "Once again,[p/] my voice came out louder than I'd meant for it to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0632080",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "Celeste: Fine.[p/] Whatever.[p/] Do what you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4d098",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "It was all because I returned to Aurinax...[p/] It was just dredging up emotions that needed to stay buried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c184d7",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "That was all the more reason to get through this trial as soon as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:065be4d",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "...The soreness in my head didn't seem to be going away anytime soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:05590a8",
  "node": "AfterCourtOne3",
  "text": "She was right.[p/] I'd be better off investigating the scene after some rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0101d07",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "As the night went on,[p/] I found myself falling into another nightmare."
}

{
  "id": "line:08216da",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: What the—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098c6d2",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "A knock rang out on the door leading to Tymora Law Offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8a8f",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby Tymora let out an irritated grumble.[p/] Who the hell was bothering her after-hours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:071afe8",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: I don't know who you think you are,[p/] but we—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bce9da",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "She froze when she saw Frey's son standing at her door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74fad",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "His bright blond hair was covered in dirt and grime.[p/] The clothes that she'd seen Frey sew for him were tattered and torn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da5c72",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "He looked like he hadn't eaten anything in days.[p/] He just stared blankly at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3d0a2",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dada9",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: What are you doing here?![p/][s/] How did you even [i]get[/i] here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb2eeb",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I walked."
}

{
  "id": "line:064c3d4",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a88a3f",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]We need to call someone.[p/] We need to get you back home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55abe",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There's nothing there for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dd6f1",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c721b",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "This was her fault.[p/] If she'd just taken that deal,[p/] his mother would still be alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d71218",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you going to keep fighting the nobility?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8088",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "His words came out weakly.[p/] He sounded like a ghost."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51885",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What?[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efc062",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora, are you going to keep fighting them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9cbf",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: Look,[p/] that's not important.[p/] We need to get you some help."
}

{
  "id": "line:01befc3",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I want to help you fight them."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c55d8",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f9d02",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please...[p/] Just let me help you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:029cb52",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fd78a",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: Look, just—[p/] Just come inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5e08a",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Ruby: We need to get you something to eat.[p/] Then we can get you cleaned up."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0507",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "The boy said nothing as he clutched the final message that his mother had left him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02568bf",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "It was the last comforting memory I'd ever have of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0036b8e",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "...It was something that I'd never experience again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f204",
  "node": "NightAfterTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Mom."
}

{
  "id": "line:098b708",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "It was another nightmare.[p/] It'd been a while since I'd thought about that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845263",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "The nightmares were getting worse and worse.[p/] I really needed to get this case done with as soon as I could."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75872",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hey, are you up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d49ef",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd9002",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "I felt like I should say something to her after what happened yesterday,[p/] but the words didn't come to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3100",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Let's get to work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b13d96",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:015bb1c",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We missed him yesterday,[p/] but Crown Prince Aster supposedly saw what happened to Justin during the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c1885",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He might have seen something that Rika missed."
}

{
  "id": "line:010bad1",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "I had no idea why the Crown Prince helped me back at Von Sanctus Manor,[p/] but he seemed more amicable to us than I'd have expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:01042fb",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "But [i]finding[/i] him in this large city was another matter.[p/] I was sure he was hidden away somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1ebbd",
  "node": "StartInves2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's also something else that Steelwind mentioned during the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0209c91",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika was supposedly a part of a band of thieves,[p/] and their thefts all those years ago seem to be similar to that of the Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddbe80",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do you think one of them is involved in all of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5044e",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think so...[p/] But I don't know why she wouldn't speak up about it if it was related to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a333",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll probably have to talk to her next."
}

{
  "id": "line:075fdeb",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: After all,[p/] I doubt it will be easy to get an audience with—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f42d43",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Aster: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:015c102",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "As we exited our room,[p/] we suddenly came face to face with the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:00929d0",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "We all stood there, stunned.[p/] What was he doing staying at a tavern for commoners?"
}

{
  "id": "line:074bf3c",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Aster—[p/][s/] Er—[p/][s/] I mean—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d53fca",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d124f",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Aster: Tyrion Cuthbert?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16f23",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]You know who I am?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcf42c",
  "node": "StartInves2b",
  "text": "That wasn't usually a good sign."
}

{
  "id": "line:047cb9a",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: I do...[p/] I know you [i]very[/i] well."
}

{
  "id": "line:00844ea",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: Tyrion Cuthbert:[p/] the protégé of the infamous Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fd1cf",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: I'm—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd336",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: —your biggest fan!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff282b",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: I can't believe it![p/][s/] The [i]infamous[/i] Tyrion Cuthbert is standing right in front of my tavern room!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0104f87",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: I've read [i]all[/i] about your feats, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:033daee",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: You successfully indicted the head of House Pierce!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da0546",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: You didn't think twice about confronting a member of House Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff843a",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: [i]And[/i] you even defeated the Duke of Commerce in the chess tournament yesterday!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b34f1",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is it bad that I've become numb to the surprises this week?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c12dc",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: And [i]you[/i]![p/][s/] You must be Celeste McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdb144",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: You're Tyrion's first client,[p/] and the Crimson Demon of the Eastern Kingdoms!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0084334",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Celeste: ...How did you find out about that name?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d5fac",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The Crimson what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d3ae8",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d096fc",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/]Anyways,[p/] Your Highness.[p/][s/] Is it true that you witnessed the accident yesterday morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dccbb4",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: Y-[p/][s/]Yes![p/][s/] I did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4687",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: Are you going to interrogate me about what I saw?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0306470",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "Aster: I'll answer whatever questions you have!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ac85a",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "First Lucio Steelwind,[p/] and now the Crown Prince—[p/]why were so many of my supposed enemies being so agreeable this week?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ef419",
  "node": "StartInves2c",
  "text": "I just let out an exasperated sigh.[p/] I shouldn't look this gift horse in the mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ec31f",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hey."
}

{
  "id": "line:090251f",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What's up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1976f",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094201f",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] Not at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:058d0c5",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Yeah, why would anything be [i]wrong[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f136",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "It seemed we both silently agreed not to acknowledge what had happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0742b47",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "...That was probably making things worse in hindsight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0344bf9",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8ef37",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are [i]you[/i] okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:007fe11",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: It's just a lot to take in."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a2860",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I would've never guessed that one simple accident would turn into some gigantic conspiracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1b64d",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: And to think [i]Justin[/i] was the Mistweaving Phantom this entire time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f3d3a",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know about that story?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b19447",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I've picked up some bits and pieces from the residents here and there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aecb0e",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...It was clearly a dark time for the city from the sounds of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0217465",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: All the more reason to be grateful for your acquittal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43c6a",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...Are you sure you're not getting ahead of yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b4c7",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think so.[p/] We have proof that Justin destroyed the guardrail using his magic ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4c844",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "Tyrion: You had nothing to do with what happened.[p/] It was really just an accident in every sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf8a4",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "Stefanic: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a6fad",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "I had to admit that I shared some of Dracogen's uneasiness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8f851",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "The Inquisition and Kingsguard were moving frantically when we left the tavern this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9ae25",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "It surely had [i]something[/i] to do with the stolen cargo,[p/] but something seemed off about their movements."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b788b",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "It seemed like they were mobilizing for more than just a retrieval."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c7c07",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "...I suppose it didn't matter either way."
}

{
  "id": "line:087e01d",
  "node": "Courtroom2a",
  "text": "No matter what they had in store,[p/] I would acquit Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfd767",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is now resumed for the trial of Stefanic Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:010d826",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Judge: During our last proceedings,[p/] the defense argued that the victim's death was a result of murder,[p/] not simple negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0002878",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Judge: This was supported by a witness who claimed to have seen a spell cast on the victim before his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c98513",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] Over the last day,[p/] we've investigated the crime further,[p/] and new facts have come to light."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e079",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nevertheless,[p/] I maintain that my client is not to blame for Justin's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acfb01",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unfortunately,[p/] the blame lies with Justin himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ddb6",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Judge: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11016",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] The victim was wearing a magical ring that allowed him to cast [b]conjuration[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e33b",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: It seems that he entered the refinery in order to steal business documents from my client,[p/] and the ring was meant to aid in that."
}

{
  "id": "line:094e710",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: After he had stolen the documents,[p/] he activated the ring on the refinery catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b080c",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: It malfunctioned in some way,[p/] causing an explosion of spatial energy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b150",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] energy is what broke apart the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0295e51",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Judge: ...Are you trying to say that the [i]victim[/i] was the culprit behind the most recent string of robberies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfafa7",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unfortunately, I am, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d05fe2",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Is that it, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04245ba",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you talking about, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05414ca",
  "node": "Courtroom2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's obvious that my client didn't have any hand in Justin's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a388e4",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: ...And do you have any evidence of that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0668ce7",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mosourika Tudor [i]saw[/i] a magical effect blast the guardrail apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e2272",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: We've been over this.[p/] Ms. Tudor had every reason to lie in her testimony last session."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba6a0",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: She didn't know about Justin's ring![p/][s/] How could she have known to lie about something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021cbed",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: You're assuming that she [i]didn't[/i] know about it beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb574e",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: The two of them were known friends.[p/] It's not implausible that he showed it to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa0a1c",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, what about the Crown Prince?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bafa8",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: He saw the magical effect as well!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0460016",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: For obvious reasons,[p/] the Crown Prince can't be called to testify in a case of this magnitude."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2fb74",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: As far as the courts are concerned,[p/] you can't use his testimony as evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0045371",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "She was being unreasonably obtuse,[p/] even more so than usual..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a72cce",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "What was she doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:017e949",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: On the subject of the victim,[p/] we've also discovered new facts regarding his...[p/] [i]actions[/i] that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:048a794",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: ...The prosecution would like to call Lucio Steelwind to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec54bd",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Judge: T-[p/][s/]The Grand General?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1118",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: As many of you know,[p/] the serial robber stole cargo from an imperial ship on the morning of the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a453df",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "AriaC: We've since located the cargo,[p/] and what we found paints quite the picture of the victim's intentions that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:02373d2",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02efbe0",
  "node": "Courtroom2c",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort the Grand General to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d2d5e",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, I guess [i]I'll[/i] just say it."
}

{
  "id": "line:090d897",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: Witness,[p/] please state your name and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e2d23",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: Are you really going to waste my time with that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0b10c",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: We all know who I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:019e3fe",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look,[p/] I just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66c59",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: Enough.[p/] I'm giving my testimony now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0238b1a",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: Justin Waye had been committing a string of robberies in Aurinax Harbor,[p/] the last of which included an imperial shipment of high-capacity energy cells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb5676",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: Waye was working with insurrectionists who provided him with an advanced magical ring.[p/] He used that ring during his robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:005189d",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: One of the ring's functions allowed him to teleport himself.[p/] The other allowed him to summon an item to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f63f57",
  "node": "Courtroom2d",
  "text": "Lucio: Waye had taken the stolen energy cells and placed a bomb within them.[p/] He was going to summon it into the refinery and detonate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6b296",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:065995b",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Celeste: There was a [i]bomb[/i] inside that thing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7efa7",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: F-[p/][s/]Father![p/][s/] By the Scaled Lord,[p/] [i]why[/i] would you say that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:005ef20",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Lucio: What are you on about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079bdaa",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Lucio: I gave the testimony as you asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:01430c6",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes,[p/] but I thought you had enough sense to leave [i]certain[/i] details out of it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef0c38",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Lucio: What \"details\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044d129",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Gallery: Insurrectionists were planning to [i]bomb[/i] the Industrial District?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7af6",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Gallery: How could a commoner brazenly rob an imperial ship?![p/][s/] Is the kingdom really so powerless?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c30d0",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Gallery: That boy was a thief and a terrorist![p/][s/] He [i]deserved[/i] what happened to him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066faeb",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]Those[/i] \"details\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03de241",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "So they really [i]were[/i] planning to use those energy cells to make a bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcbca5",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "I can't believe Justin would agree to do something like this...[p/] He [i]worked[/i] with the people there..."
}

{
  "id": "line:029b66c",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Who would have anything to gain from doing something like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cfdc6",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "Was Lucio trying to manufacture a catastrophe so that he could march his soldiers into Aurinax?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0226078",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "...No.[p/] I needed to think through this rationally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c45c92",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "[i]Both[/i] of the Steelwinds have been acting strangely lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca4d38",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "There was something else happening here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5bc7",
  "node": "LucioTestAfter",
  "text": "...I guess it didn't matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a16401",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've learned that Justin was quite skilled at breaking into secure places."
}

{
  "id": "line:042db96",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I never imagined he'd be able to break into an imperial ship without being caught."
}

{
  "id": "line:023f732",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...He shouldn't have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365b85",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: The men stationed there were negligent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b450",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: At least that's the most generous interpretation of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff54f",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Generous\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:007e7ee",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: Waye was working with insurrectionists who provided him with an advanced magical ring.[p/] He then used that ring during his robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:004eaf5",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have any proof to substantiate that claim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0867f01",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...What other explanation is there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0905932",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] [i]you[/i] might want to stage a catastrophe in the heart of von Sanctus's territory."
}

{
  "id": "line:040e778",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That would let you march your soldiers right into the land of one of your rivals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcbc1d",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Just to name [i]one[/i] possible explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0007a37",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...The prosecution does not refute the defense's statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b24fee",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution also does not conclude that the victim was a part of [i]any[/i] insurrectionist group."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5536d",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could he summon [i]any[/i] item he wanted?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0902319",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: He would need to affix a specific kind of energy crystal to the object he wanted to summon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0346799",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: We found such a crystal attached to the metal chest containing the bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea2ab6",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "AriaC: There's no doubt that the ring was set to summon that chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfef2d",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you be so sure?[p/] I thought the ring was too damaged by the vat chemicals to identify that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3ecc7",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "AriaC: Luckily,[p/] the crystal attached to the bomb was not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0063272",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "AriaC: We were able to verify its connection to the ring,[p/] however disrupted it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:052f655",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: It was clear that he meant to summon that chest into the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1707d",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: It was only out of sheer luck that he died before that could happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce638",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Lucio: We're lucky he never got the chance to summon that container.[p/] The results would have been catastrophic."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2e88",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Celeste: Was Justin really planning to blow up the refinery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1093d",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't know,[p/] and it's not as if he can tell us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9bcd5",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Still...[p/] Lucio is making a lot of assumptions about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:073f9dd",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I guess he's the type of person to jump to conclusions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8abca",
  "node": "CrossLucio2",
  "text": "Celeste: He could be wrong about a lot of things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0393b32",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you so sure that he was planning to target the refinery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72449",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Tyrion: He could have been planning to rob my client and place the bomb somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fe633",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "AriaC: Arcane Refineries such as your client's create volatile yet controlled chemical reactions."
}

{
  "id": "line:098fbf4",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "AriaC: Those high-capacity energy cells alone had enough of an explosive yield to level a city block."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbd79d",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "AriaC: If detonated near the refinery,[p/] the ensuing explosion would have been exponentially larger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0261372",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's...[p/] terrifying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0612624",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Lucio: From the way the bomb was constructed,[p/] it seemed that it was meant to be as destructive as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:03278ff",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Lucio: Justin Waye could have transported that bomb to his position at any moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0293c34",
  "node": "Lucio2Press",
  "text": "Lucio: I find it difficult to believe that he'd risk bringing the bomb into the refinery if that weren't his intention."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caadd7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Grand General,[p/] the ring allowed the victim to teleport himself and summon objects to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:081a88b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do both of those magical effects belong to the school of [b]conjuration[/b] magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf6f5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Lucio: Yes.[p/] They both involve instantaneous spatial movement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f9cb",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then I'm afraid you were wrong about what Justin did that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b38ae",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: He [i]did[/i] summon the bomb to the refinery that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ddde0",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Or at least he attempted to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7394a",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Lucio: What are you talking about?[p/][s/] The bomb was found in that old abandoned house."
}

{
  "id": "line:062ec68",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Lucio: [i]You[/i] were the one who alerted us to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0800a6b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That may be,[p/] but we identified that there were traces of [b]conjuration[/b] magic on that box."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302912",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Justin's ring was damaged in the accident.[p/] It couldn't have been activated at any point after he died."
}

{
  "id": "line:082bdfb",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must have attempted to summon the bomb that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce84d1",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: Justin could have simply summoned the box to the abandoned house before he planted it at the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:023faf3",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have a witness who can confirm that the metal chest has been in the abandoned house since the night before the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b01b6",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: Then it must have been teleported in preparation for the bombing."
}

{
  "id": "line:070df14",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: No one knew about that house other than the victim and a few delinquents, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0275079",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: They wouldn't carelessly move around a dangerous bomb without a good reason!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f4ff5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: If it [i]had[/i] been summoned,[p/] why was it in the abandoned house instead of the refinery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0572aa3",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj2",
  "text": "0000"
}

{
  "id": "line:068c23f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj2",
  "text": "Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b197db",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Steelwind had a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ca337",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj2",
  "text": "If Justin had attempted to summon the bomb,[p/] why was it found in my house?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070adc5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because the summoning spell ultimately failed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f23cb",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: He tried to summon that large chest on the catwalk,[p/] but there wasn't enough room!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b62acd",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The spell failed,[p/] and the resulting spatial shunting damaged the chest and blew apart the guardrail!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056e7e6",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...You've contradicted yourself, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d434f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And how's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa4483",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj3",
  "text": "AriaC: Your entire defense is based on the testimony of Mosourika Tudor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1d031",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: She thought the victim had been blasted with a spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ef77e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: If what you're saying is true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dbe6b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Then that would imply that Justin summoned the chest right onto his location!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d23860",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible that Mosourika was mistaken about that one detail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0126355",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Your entire case is predicated on her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0813792",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: If even [i]you[/i] don't have confidence in her testimony,[p/] I don't think you have much of a case."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c0f71",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e8427",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: But let's assume that Justin [i]did[/i] summon the chest at his location."
}

{
  "id": "line:0261bfd",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: That [i]also[/i] contradicts Ms. Tudor's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:021727f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Summoning the chest at his position wouldn't have just inflicted damage on the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:000ea98",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Attempting to summon that large container would have inflicted damage on [i]him[/i] as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c197bd",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Now you [i]could[/i] argue that the spatial shunting was what ultimately pushed the victim off the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0416b0f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: But in our last session,[p/] [i]you[/i] were adamant that the victim fell in [i]after[/i] the rail was destroyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad7cd4",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]did[/i] say that,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4389",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: That's also ignoring the fact that Mr. Waye had been using that ring for several months."
}

{
  "id": "line:015403e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: He was a master thief and had been expertly using that ring to escape the sites of his robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2293",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "AriaC: He would know the dangers of spatial shunting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf071f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "...She was actually making a lot of great points,[p/] and they didn't seem to contradict anything we'd learned so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:071ab7a",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "Rika seemed so sure of what she saw.[p/] The Crown Prince even confirmed it in what he told us."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c87a7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "They both even mentioned a prism-shaped flash of light when the guardrail broke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cee8cf",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj4",
  "text": "They [i]had[/i] to have seen Justin attempt to summon that metal container."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f863e5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "What was going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080e123",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "...I needed to think through this rationally and review everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c98fd",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "With all these facts laid out,[p/] there had to be an explanation that was consistent with all of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a0011",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "It was difficult to get into Justin's headspace before the accident happened,[p/] but I did know one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05284bf",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "Cat: He used the device when he wasn't supposed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:027cc28",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "Cat: He didn't disappear like he usually did.[p/] Instead,[p/] there was an explosion of energy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e96eb9",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "Cat: I was almost caught by it.[p/] I barely escaped the blast."
}

{
  "id": "line:03450c7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] He tried to teleport while he was [i]on[/i] the catwalk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0009a90",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "According to Queen,[p/] he activated the ring on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cf4c7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj5",
  "text": "She seemed to think that he was trying to teleport,[p/] but from what happened afterwards,[p/] he had probably activated the summoning spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0500a12",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj6",
  "text": "No...[p/] Queen said that he attempted to teleport."
}

{
  "id": "line:090edca",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj6",
  "text": "Mosourika and the Crown Prince witnessed him attempt to summon the container to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8d53",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj6",
  "text": "Which one of these was true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0963c88",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "They were [i]both[/i] true."
}

{
  "id": "line:098c955",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind,[p/] the ring must have been designed to activate the teleportation spell and the summoning spell at the same time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7bbe",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Justin wasn't affected by the spatial shunting because he was being teleported elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a618e7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "AriaC: That's an awfully large leap in logic.[p/] I doubt you have anything to substantiate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0934084",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said it yourself, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a67b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Orym: It's kind of weird, honestly.[p/] Artificery fitted into rings usually only has one function."
}

{
  "id": "line:042a642",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090255c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Aria: Unlike spells cast by a mage,[p/] artificery needs to differentiate which spell to cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bb89e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Aria: Usually,[p/] devices with multiple spells will have some kind of switch or multiple buttons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af1608",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]was[/i] no need for the ring to differentiate between which spell to cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb8bc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Both spells were linked to each other,[p/] and they were being activated at the same time."
}

{
  "id": "line:008adf8",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "AriaC: ...That [i]would[/i] explain Ms. Tudor's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04788",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: When the summoning spell failed,[p/] his teleportation must have failed as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:041a7a7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must have tried to catch himself on the guardrail that had been there moments ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d120bc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it had been destroyed by the failed summoning.[p/] He fell right into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db3d63",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "AriaC: If your theory is true,[p/] why would he try to plant the bomb on the catwalk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d547be",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "AriaC: That would be the [i]worst[/i] place to put it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b8d81",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "She [i]did[/i] have a point there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0113630",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "If Justin had been using the ring to teleport during his thefts,[p/] he should have known about spatial shunting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f96c4c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "It was obvious that the large metal container wouldn't fit on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e165b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "And Dracogen's office was close by, too.[p/] If he wanted to plant the bomb,[p/] a closed room would have been far better."
}

{
  "id": "line:001256d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj7",
  "text": "Why would he activate the ring when he should have known it would fail?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0596b6a",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj8",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin had apparently been using the ring for months."
}

{
  "id": "line:022a0b8",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj8",
  "text": "He would have known about spatial shunting."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a335f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj8",
  "text": "It didn't make sense for him to summon the container on that catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:025816c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...He didn't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0147db7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "AriaC: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f169",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: He didn't know the ring would summon the bomb to his position."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9a27c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Lucio: That's ridiculous![p/][s/] How could he possibly not know?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f160fc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Lucio: He'd been using that ring in his robberies for months!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8f0a",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone else [i]gave[/i] him that ring, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbb636",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: They could've only told him about the teleportation function,[p/] not the summoning function."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3593d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: For whatever reason,[p/] he decided to teleport while he was on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0708b60",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "Queen even said that he activated it when he wasn't supposed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb9293",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj9",
  "text": "That must imply that he was expected to activate the ring somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5bda2",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj10",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin had more than one objective when he entered the refinery that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0bbc6",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj10",
  "text": "He obviously deviated from the plan by teleporting while on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0e05f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj10",
  "text": "Where was he supposed to be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaea09",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: If someone had really wanted to plant an explosive in the refinery,[p/] the best place would've been in my client's office."
}

{
  "id": "line:064cc03",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever gave Justin that ring expected him to activate the ring while he was in there."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f1e2f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: He would've teleported away,[p/] none the wiser to the fact that he was switching places with the bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0092731",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "AriaC: But again,[p/] he's been using the ring for months."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a91f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "AriaC: I find it difficult to believe the ring would have a summon function if its only purpose was to summon the bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f79d3",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're right...[p/] He must have been summoning something else to each of the places he was robbing."
}

{
  "id": "line:031b763",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj11",
  "text": "Lucio: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed3e1",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj12",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin had been robbing several individuals and organizations without any apparent goals."
}

{
  "id": "line:097817e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj12",
  "text": "But there [i]was[/i] a trend between some of the people he was targeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:03176f7",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was planting false evidence of treason!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0209106",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Lucio: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9d29",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: At some of the crime scenes,[p/] the City Watch found chests containing weapons,[p/] explosives,[p/] and illegal communications!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cad7d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: The victims were never the ones who reported the robberies.[p/] It was always someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0709fcb",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: At first I thought the serial robber was trying to reveal dissidents,[p/] but the opposite was true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce731c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever was behind this was using Justin to frame people for treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d24d5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: And they were [i]targeting[/i] members of the workers' unions!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba7a5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Grand General,[p/] you [i]knew[/i] something was strange, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6c735",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why you took the victims into protective custody instead of charging them with treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc57bf",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I don't answer to you, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1eee",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "...That might as well have been an admission."
}

{
  "id": "line:0049151",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it seemed like I finally found a proper motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2a3f1",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Someone was paying Justin to plant false evidence on members of the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edc77e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "This person was also filing false reports to make it sound like there were tensions between them and Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab203",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj13",
  "text": "Was the bomb also a part of this plot?[p/] Were they trying to raise tensions further by causing a catastrophe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009b52b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "Who would benefit from something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082465d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "It couldn't have been Lucio.[p/] If it were,[p/] he would've simply charged the union members with treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:03af3dc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "Von Sanctus didn't make any sense, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:043aea9",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "He [i]might[/i] have had something to gain from demonizing the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d5a94",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "But he's the one who would've had the most to lose from that bomb destroying his land."
}

{
  "id": "line:010450e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "...Could it be Sibyl?[p/] I didn't know that much about her personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd4e45",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "All I knew was that her noble house controlled the judicial and legislative branches."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b1291",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "Did she have something to gain from orchestrating this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a4d3a",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "No matter who it was,[p/] I still didn't have any evidence connecting them to the robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0197987",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "That's why they had Justin do their dirty work.[p/] They did everything they could to cover up their involvement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0378a3f",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj14",
  "text": "The only connection I had was..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f60798",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj15",
  "text": "Queen..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2c653",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj15",
  "text": "The mastermind behind this obviously never considered that someone could talk to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e3ff8",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj15",
  "text": "...But according to her,[p/] they were also able to talk to her like I could."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d3abc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj15",
  "text": "I doubted that the judge would suspend the trial just so I could try to catch a wandering cat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b28d1b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj15",
  "text": "There had to be [i]something[/i] that could tell me who was working with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0850d8c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj16",
  "text": "Strap"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9ec9c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj16",
  "text": "No...[p/] There had to be [i]something[/i] that Queen left behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2c836",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj16",
  "text": "Something physical that might help identify what she was doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1ee36",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "This leather strap..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee516",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "Justin dropped it before he fell into the vat,[p/] and the Crown Prince mentioned that Justin grabbed the animal before he fell."
}

{
  "id": "line:058a757",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "Cat: He needed to simply follow the plan.[p/] Instead,[p/] he tried to betray me at the last moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:007cf37",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "Cat: He even tried to pull me in with him.[p/] Luckily,[p/] the only thing harmed was my neckband."
}

{
  "id": "line:09898cd",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "Justin grabbed Queen before he activated the ring.[p/] He must have ripped a collar that was around her neck."
}

{
  "id": "line:0751421",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "This strap had the numerals \"VI\" on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1929",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj17",
  "text": "...Or so I thought,[p/] but there was something else I found that changed the meaning of that engraving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5767d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj18",
  "text": "EttaStrap"
}

{
  "id": "line:032ff41",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj18",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin tore Queen's collar before he fell in."
}

{
  "id": "line:00495df",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj18",
  "text": "He dropped one of the pieces in the refinery as he fell.[p/] The other piece was somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:030052e",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj19",
  "text": "[i]This[/i] strap of leather has \"ETTA\" engraved into it.[p/] They were two halves of a whole."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b255",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj19",
  "text": "Neither of those spelled \"Queen\",[p/] but it's possible she responded to a different name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c70560",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj19",
  "text": "I felt like I'd heard a name like that somewhere before."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cfc45",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj20",
  "text": "Coraline"
}

{
  "id": "line:003e004",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj20",
  "text": "No...[p/] That wasn't it."
}

{
  "id": "line:053d2d4",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj20",
  "text": "I remember I'd heard a name like this before.[p/] Where was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0141c63",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj20",
  "text": "...I think it may have been when we were at Von Sanctus Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:084d20b",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "Coraline: Why not indulge him, Lloyd?[p/] He seems harmless."
}

{
  "id": "line:05342c1",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0438a97",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "Coraline: Anyways,[p/] you're waiting for Violetta to return, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0126042",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "Von Sanctus was waiting for \"Violetta\".[p/] Could that be the name engraved on her collar?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0572644",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "But how could he even be involved in this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:096e8dc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "Even [i]he[/i] wouldn't be insane enough to blow up his own city over his feud with Dracogen..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0271d3c",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "...No.[p/] There had to be something more to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e151",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj21",
  "text": "And there was only one way to find out."
}

{
  "id": "line:018873d",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] I believe there's only one person who can truly tell us the true state of insurrection in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:06838cf",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that's its ruling lord:[p/][s/] Lloyd von Sanctus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:049caa3",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Lloyd?[p/] Are you joking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0671161",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is something wrong, Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a5212",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lucio: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] ...It's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8b754",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Without waiting for the bailiff,[p/] the Grand General marched away from the stand and took a seat in the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aff47",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Thank you for taking the stand today, Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:098c3cc",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lloyd: I don't see why [i]I[/i] have to take the stand.[p/] Surely,[p/] the reports from the City Watch should be enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ad014",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] I guess I wouldn't expect you to know much about what goes on in your land."
}

{
  "id": "line:0299f06",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lloyd: You little brat..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03324a5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "AriaC: I think what Mr. Cuthbert [i]means[/i] to say is that you are able to provide a more valuable perspective as the city's ruling lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab15db",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "AriaC: I'm sure you can understand,[p/] seeing as how...[p/] [i]confusing[/i] these reports of insurrection have been."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84672",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d62be5",
  "node": "Lucio2Obj22",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Very well.[p/] I'll tell you [i]exactly[/i] what the state of insurrection is in my city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7d7c7",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Lloyd: My City Watch has been hard at work apprehending these insurrectionists,[p/] and we've been doing so with no collateral damage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f29e4d",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Lloyd: They've been growing in number,[p/] however.[p/] No doubt because these \"unions\" have been feeding the people's discontent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0074df9",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Lloyd: From what I understand,[p/] they were even planning to plant a bomb in the refinery.[p/] Thank the Scaled Lord nobody was hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:014e3a7",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Lloyd: Tensions have been getting worse and worse,[p/] and the Steelwinds have only been feeding the flames."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b45543",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Celeste: Well,[p/] he's obviously wrong![p/] We [i]know[/i] that someone is trying to frame the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bc0f3",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] but we don't have any hard evidence to prove it yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:06143b2",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "Tyrion: Until we can do that,[p/] it's our word against his."
}

{
  "id": "line:053195a",
  "node": "LloydTest",
  "text": "But if I'm lucky,[p/] his words will give me exactly what I need."
}

{
  "id": "line:0313ab7",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"Your\" City Watch?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09622db",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: They are [i]my[/i] men.[p/] They only succeed under my leadership."
}

{
  "id": "line:0651a90",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: Clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f8575",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I know someone like you can't appreciate what I do for the people,[p/] but I should be [i]commended[/i] for what I'm doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e639f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I've peacefully coordinated the arrests of countless dangerous individuals,[p/] and I've done so without any bloodshed."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c84d3",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's more than I can say for some of the [i]other[/i] noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:070e65b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "He was obviously just stroking his ego,[p/] but I couldn't discount the fact that the Aurinax City Watch technically answered to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0717b90",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "That would've definitely made these frame jobs easier if he were involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:02191eb",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: By \"feeding discontent\",[p/] do you mean they were advocating for basic human rights?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3dae",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I'm not in the mood to have this argument with you again, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ea9a0",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: You seem to like evidence so much,[p/] so here you have it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbeddf",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ever since these unions popped up,[p/] the number of people being charged with treason has also risen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa43cc",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: And all of those suspects were known members of the various workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0574dd9",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I wonder why."
}

{
  "id": "line:016b30d",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Say what you want.[p/] Your ridiculous conspiracy theories have no place here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e4193",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "We would see about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0825b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sure it's a [i]big[/i] relief for you, von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0bb5f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: You seem to have gotten it into your head that [i]I[/i] was somehow involved in this plot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8bcf8",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: But what would [i]I[/i] have to gain from something like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bd5f1",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I may not own many of the businesses in Aurinax's industrial district,[p/] but it is still [i]my[/i] land."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aea626",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I would have the most to lose from orchestrating a catastrophe like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b6af9",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "That was still the one element that didn't make sense to me,[p/] and he [i]knew[/i] that."
}

{
  "id": "line:050ec4a",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Was he truly not involved,[p/] or was there some other reward he would reap from the destruction of the industrial district?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042429d",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: I won't deny that—[p/]at least in regards to the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f63ca",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I doubt someone of your standing would honestly care."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c7f8",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I resent that remark, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d205e",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: You may think you can fool the gallery,[p/] but I know your [i]real[/i] opinions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7438b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: If it weren't for the workers' unions encroaching on your businesses,[p/] I bet you wouldn't give a damn about these tensions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0151f74",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: Dissidence affects far more than just the commoners, boy.[p/] It has vast implications on every aspect of trade throughout the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b1d8d",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Assuming such dissidence actually exists."
}

{
  "id": "line:035d6a9",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I've seen it![p/][s/] And I have the trade records to prove it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c42f37",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: This so-called \"Mistweaving Phantom\" [i]stole[/i] several weapons and other dangerous items!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0739cc4",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: We've had to massively restrict all potentially dangerous items coming into the harbor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb79d2",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's been an absolute headache for our military as well!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a602c",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: We've had to massively restrict all potentially dangerous items coming into the harbor because of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e4b41",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: So at the end of the day,[p/] it's all about how it affects trade."
}

{
  "id": "line:0281df2",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]You[/i] may not understand,[p/] but those shipments were integral to upgrading and maintaining our military."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c23e4a",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A military owned by your enemies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0399a4b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: My house may have a rivalry with the Steelwinds,[p/] but our national defense is integral to Wyverngarde's continued survival."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc13a2",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Lord von Sanctus,[p/] watch your words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b499f9",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: You're blind to it,[p/] but the other nations will strike us the moment we show [i]any[/i] weakness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a9a18",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "AriaC: Von Sanctus![p/][s/] That's enough!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f4ac",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "AriaC: We do [i]not[/i] need you to stoke panic in the public with inflammatory words."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b6019",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I'm afraid I must agree, Lord von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a9fda",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Judge: I don't believe this is relevant to your testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b03737",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7f5f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Celeste: He's just pulling his testimony right out of his—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af1781",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but the only pieces of evidence to contradict it are testimonies from Dracogen and Mr. Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:07296fe",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Tyrion: It will be his word against theirs,[p/] and it's obvious who the courts will side with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf1b6",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Celeste: He's bound to slip up eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0887dbe",
  "node": "CrossLloyd",
  "text": "Celeste: I bet if you keep him talking,[p/] you'll catch him in a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3e76",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus,[p/] why [i]did[/i] you agree to testify today?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e18290",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Lloyd: Why?[p/] You wished for me to testify on the state of insurrection in Aurinax, did you not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0feb398",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Lloyd: I was merely doing my civic duty."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1271",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, [i]I[/i] think you took the stand for another reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a4e60",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You wanted to reclaim control of the narrative,[p/] right in front of the people in the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0681e3a",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Lloyd: Think what you will.[p/] This is just baseless slander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0838c13",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Judge: I must agree, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0961736",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Judge: Please refrain from insulting the current witness.[p/] He took the stand at your request."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e61495",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess I can't disagree with that,[p/] Your Honor,[p/] but the witness made one mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3b115",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: He [i]lied[/i] in order to perpetuate that narrative."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b393a",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Lloyd: Again with the baseless accusations?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023e166",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus,[p/] you testified that you've had to restrict [i]all[/i] dangerous items coming into Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e0ef",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]you[/i] were the one who ordered those high-capacity energy cells from the Crown Prince!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b86468",
  "node": "LloydObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those same energy cells were used to construct the bomb Justin was supposed to plant at the refinery!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7d15",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: H-[p/][s/]How do you know about that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f22ad",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You really don't leave your manor much, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fc24e",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I collected statements from the Crown Prince about that shipment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0c2c",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was even the one that [i]found[/i] the bomb before it could be set off."
}

{
  "id": "line:000d0e1",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cf79d",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Aria![p/][s/] Why wasn't I informed about this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfb22f",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...It wasn't directly relevant to your case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7a2c2",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have no doubt that you were restricting trade in an attempt to [i]pretend[/i] you were doing something about the thefts and \"insurrectionists\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2c93",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You must have ordered those cells from the Crown Prince knowing that it would be difficult for [i]anyone[/i] to get his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d525c1",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Luckily,[p/] I have a way with people."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa0fe",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...More like Aster is just a giant fanboy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0082c09",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Regardless[/i],[p/] one fact is clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28875",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You didn't just restrict all of the items coming into Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd2bd7",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]also[/i] ignored those restrictions to ship in the dangerous materials used to construct the bomb!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad58eb",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: So [i]that's[/i] your game."
}

{
  "id": "line:099e24d",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I knew you didn't bring me on the stand just to testify..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd285a",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: What could [i]possibly[/i] lead you to believe that [i]I[/i] was involved with that thief?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b75f56",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] [i]Violetta[/i] seemed to be [i]very[/i] involved with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cce8d7",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I knew it![p/][s/] How did you even—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcd8b6",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "He looked nervously around the room before catching himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:068df7c",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...So what is it, then?[p/] Are you going to call my [i]cat[/i] on the stand to testify?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0bbb9",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] I think [i]you'll[/i] do just fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d0131",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Fine.[p/] You want my testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a4b99",
  "node": "LloydObj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'll tell you [i]exactly[/i] what's wrong with your foolish theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0027bde",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I've said this time and time again.[p/] What would I have to gain from blowing up my own land?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0506899",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I would have destroyed [i]countless[/i] factories and refineries.[p/] [i]Hundreds[/i] of lives would have been lost!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a548e3",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Not to mention what that would do to my standing![p/] It would render me completely powerless!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0848b45",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Lloyd: My city would have been left defenseless.[p/] I'd just be leaving my land right open for Lucio to march in and \"maintain order\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8621",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": ":And [i]there[/i] was his final defense:[p/] the one argument I didn't have a counter for."
}

{
  "id": "line:04268fc",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Celeste: What he's saying makes a lot of sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c99df9",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know.[p/] I still don't understand why he would be involved in something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b3691",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He may be petty,[p/] but he wouldn't have lasted long in the nobility if he were a complete moron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba3295",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He wouldn't have done this just to spite Dracogen or the unions.[p/] There [i]had[/i] to be something else he was trying to accomplish."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf74a1",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Celeste: But what could be worth attacking his land?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0195b10",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Celeste: No matter what he got from it,[p/] it couldn't be worth giving up power to Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a8a9b",
  "node": "LloydTest2",
  "text": "Something else had to be happening here."
}

{
  "id": "line:003499a",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Judge: I must agree with Lord von Sanctus, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07fb7",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Judge: I don't see any reason to entertain this—"
}

{
  "id": "line:091c05a",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "AriaC: If Mr. Cuthbert wants to waste the court's time with this line of question,[p/] I believe we should let him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79bb3",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "AriaC: Let him get it out of his system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0298dd6",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Something was strange about the tone of her voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf7172",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "It was like she was overplaying how she usually spoke during our trials."
}

{
  "id": "line:0622256",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "...Was she covering for me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6603b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Seeing as how those facilities are no longer owned by you,[p/] I don't imagine you seeing that as a loss."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8be4b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Please.[p/] I know you wish to paint me as a monster,[p/] as you do with every other noble that crosses your path."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3247",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Do you honestly think I'd sacrifice so many lives without a good reason?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02688bb",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which implies that there [i]is[/i] a reason you might make such a sacrifice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3d9e3",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: T-[p/][s/]That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056f88f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "He stopped himself again before drawing in a slow breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d70839",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I am not some bloodthirsty maniac."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f84ec",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: If you want to pursue the nobles with [i]real[/i] blood on their hands,[p/] perhaps you should look toward the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc15b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Witness,[p/] may I remind you that my father is sitting in the gallery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0343bfb",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hrk!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032c11c",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "The duke practically choked on his own words as his head whipped to look over to the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc093",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "He stammered for a bit before he continued."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe5502",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] [i]anyways[/i]—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a694c",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you really telling us the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053177c",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: As the Duke of Commerce,[p/] I'm sure your holdings extend beyond the city of Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:012a671",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Aurinax is our main trading hub with the other nations."
}

{
  "id": "line:092bcc5",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Even if I don't personally own most of the facilities in the city,[p/] our entire trade network is built upon them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c60305",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Without those facilities,[p/] supply lines would crumble and nationwide manufacturing would grind to a halt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf578",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "These were all really good points,[p/] which raised the question as to why he thought this was worth it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e855df",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Was he really willing to sacrifice global trade,[p/] or did he have something else in mind to stop that from happening?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093fdda",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Would that really happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f57b2",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: For someone of your status,[p/] surely [i]you[/i] have your own armed forces."
}

{
  "id": "line:000c01c",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I have access to [i]some[/i] armed guards, perhaps."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b415bc",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: But they exist to carry out the law and protect the city from bandits and thieves."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c691f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: The kingdom would never trust such a small force to protect a key city like Aurinax,[p/] especially after an act of insurrection."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b185b",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "...So what was his plan then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08143c8",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Was he trying to set the Grand General up for another massacre,[p/] or did he have some way to maintain order without the need for Lucio's intervention?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de65bd",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "[i]That[/i] was the last piece I needed to establish his motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:01158dc",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus,[p/] can you add what you just said to your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8fbf",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Whatever."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e82942",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "LLoyd: It's not as if [i]I[/i] have the numbers or manpower required to maintain order in a city under attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ce619",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]are[/i] the Duke of Commerce."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a085d",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your gold could buy a lot of things—[p/]armed forces included."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8a98",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Yes,[p/] but it can't buy trust or loyalty."
}

{
  "id": "line:03858fd",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: The kingdom would never abide me hiring [i]mercenaries[/i] to protect a key city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5fd66",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Not when we have our own military to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8f18",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perhaps the kingdom would be persuaded otherwise,[p/] considering the news surrounding the Grand General's actions in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:072a56a",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Maybe,[p/] but they would never allow me to hire mercenaries based in a town filled with hidden insurrectionists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0442e57",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: We'd risk ceding [i]more[/i] ground to anyone trying to stage a revolution."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aada9",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Again,[p/] everything he was saying was true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1b345",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be a way he was planning to work around that."
}

{
  "id": "line:057c97f",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Celeste: It really doesn't make any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca7aa",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Celeste: He clearly thought this through.[p/] He wasn't just being reckless."
}

{
  "id": "line:004f497",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's making a lot of good points,[p/] which means the real reason has to be something that would circumvent them somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:093f0b3",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He would have ruined industry in Aurinax,[p/] [i]and[/i] he would've invited the Grand General into his territory."
}

{
  "id": "line:067570e",
  "node": "CrossLloyd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must've had a way to mitigate both of those hits to his power,[p/] and what he gained would have been worth that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3fe5",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: House von Sanctus commands the entirety of our kingdom's industrial output.[p/] It directs the flow of trade throughout our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8a905",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: Every cog in the machinery of commerce—[p/]from the extraction of raw materials,[p/] to the construction of finished products—[p/]was my concern."
}

{
  "id": "line:054c070",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: Of course,[p/] one could not expect a workforce of commoners to operate as a perfect unit."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cda95",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: People made mistakes.[p/] People got injured.[p/] People got sick.[p/] Sometimes,[p/] people even died."
}

{
  "id": "line:025c89e",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: Such were the flaws of man.[p/] There was no way around it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efc427",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...At least,[p/] that's what I'd always thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a8f6f",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: You see,[p/] Arcarus is the nation south of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abefde",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's a small nation,[p/] dwarfed by the juggernaut that was our marvelous kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4123",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: But they were protected by the Ordo Astralis:[p/] a peacekeeping organization that had every other nation in the world under its thumb."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f5b9e",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: They were quite useful allies,[p/] and one could purchase raw materials and products from them on the cheap."
}

{
  "id": "line:022e31e",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'd always been curious about how they could turn a profit while charging so low."
}

{
  "id": "line:095315c",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: I decided to travel there myself.[p/] I wanted to see what their secret was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c79750",
  "node": "LloydMonologue",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...And what I saw shook me more than anything else I'd ever seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16ee9",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was beautiful.[p/] It was perfect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a286a7",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I saw legions of workers,[p/] obedient beasts of burden."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ddeb4",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Every hand knew its task.[p/] Every foot knew where to stand.[p/] Every minute was measured."
}

{
  "id": "line:01abe7f",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Supervisors always stood watch over them,[p/] like a noble lord overlooking their kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ca90b",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: They never needed to bark orders.[p/] They simply needed to remind everyone that there was always someone watching."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f42dad",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Arcarus was small,[p/] but its population was dense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0535d9a",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I drove by large stone buildings that towered over anything I'd witnessed in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8c720",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: The people were packed next to each other.[p/] There was only enough room for them to breathe."
}

{
  "id": "line:07da835",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: There would never be enough for everyone,[p/] but that just kept the people hungry."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c03f0",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was only later that I realized that this was a part of the glorious design."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aedec4",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Jobs were always available,[p/] and they were sold to the lowest bidder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b78e32",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Anyone who broke under the strain could easily be thrown away and replaced."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f41871",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: There was always someone else waiting,[p/] eager to take what they had."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af2124",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was a grand symphony of efficiency.[p/] It was a marvelous machine that never stopped."
}

{
  "id": "line:078786c",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: In that moment—[p/]in the moment when I witnessed divinity itself—[p/]I knew that [i]this[/i] was the future of industry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3c14d",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: No...[p/] [i]This[/i] was the future of humanity itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecbf91",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Nothing I'd built in Wyverngarde could even compare to the utopia they'd created there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeb632",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: I spoke with their leaders.[p/] They told me about their plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a87cc",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: They told me about the Arcane Constructs:[p/] mindless machines that did everything they were told."
}

{
  "id": "line:0942152",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: They'd done the impossible.[p/] They'd improved upon perfection."
}

{
  "id": "line:072fc64",
  "node": "LloydMonologue2",
  "text": "Lloyd: We no longer needed the commoners in order to thrive.[p/] [i]I[/i] would be the master of my own universe."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fa634",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You really are a fool.[p/] Aren't you, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15f57",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lloyd: Why?[p/] Because you [i]still[/i] believe I'd destroy my city just to spite your client?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067ca27",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] It seems your plan was far more insidious than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7e68",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lloyd: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08034c7",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've thought it over,[p/] and there's really no other explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aecaf1",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were really planning to do it, weren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02815fa",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were planning to defend the city using a legion of Arcane Constructs!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c6c86",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]Hrrrk[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05257a7",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Judge: ...Arcane Constructs?[p/] Are you referring to those suits of armor at the Imperial Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c23bf7",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's correct, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29822",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have a shipping report proving that the witness received a large shipment of Arcane Constructs recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:045105a",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: And according to the harbormaster,[p/] you've been receiving shipments like that for the last few months!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04385ae",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lloyd: S-[p/][s/]So what if I have?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16a0b",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I don't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97859",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "His head whipped around the room—[p/]first to the gallery,[p/] then to the Grand General himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:079c5b7",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj",
  "text": "Lucio quietly narrowed his eyes at him.[p/] Von Sanctus practically flinched at his glare."
}

{
  "id": "line:083067f",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...You filthy little upstart! [h=\"You're going to|ruin everything!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2a363",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Your Grace?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b610d2",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...So it [i]is[/i] true, then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc65bd",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "The duke's teeth were so clenched that they might shatter."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f97af",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "His breath was practically oozing the vitriol that he wanted to throw at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ca515",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: You are [i]not[/i] going to be the one who undoes me—[p]not [i]you[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5e1ac",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's about time someone taught you your place, you little rat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0854c62",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm ready when you are, von Sanctus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031b02c",
  "node": "Lloyd2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Come and lose another match!"
}

{
  "id": "line:040a302",
  "node": "LloydCornered",
  "text": "Lloyd: You think I was planning to use those Constructs for combat?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21703",
  "node": "LloydCornered",
  "text": "Lloyd: I was merely—[p/][s/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e82e91",
  "node": "LloydCornered",
  "text": "Lloyd: I was planning to use those Constructs to work in my factories!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e18191",
  "node": "LloydCornered",
  "text": "Lloyd: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] That's it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:060a56b",
  "node": "LloydCornered2",
  "text": "UnionTensions2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85b52",
  "node": "LloydCornered2",
  "text": "Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:001100a",
  "node": "LloydCornered2",
  "text": "No...[p/] It may have been true that he was planning to use Constructs for labor after the catastrophe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0549aeb",
  "node": "LloydCornered2",
  "text": "But his plan to do that was based on one large assumption."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c8b5",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't own any of the factories or refineries in Aurinax's Industrial District, von Sanctus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12750",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What jobs could you have possibly had them fill?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:006148d",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I have other cities in which I do business!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f4016",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why would you import and keep them in Aurinax?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec7444",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have no doubt that you planned to use those Constructs as part of a labor force!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04562bc",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you'd only be able to do that [i]after[/i] your bomb destroyed the factories that were already there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01088a7",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was a pretty good plan, von Sanctus.[p/] I'm almost surprised you came up with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13baf",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You would stage an attack on your city,[p/] use your legion of Constructs to restore order,[p/] [i]and[/i] then use them as a labor force to rebuild the damage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9ac48",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Selling your Constructs nationwide would've been easy after a demonstration like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eca2cd",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...It was more than that.[p/] Wasn't it, Lloyd?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4f610",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: A-[p/][s/]Aria,[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0817",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "AriaC: Constructs follow orders.[p/] They're not vulnerable to the disorganization and chaos of living soldiers."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b9b76",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...They'd be less likely to commit the atrocities my father has been allowing to happen in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0870e60",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "AriaC: With the recent news,[p/] you had the perfect opportunity to use those Constructs to encroach on the Steelwinds' domain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca48f3",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: T-[p/][s/]That's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:072f9da",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...That's preposterous![p/][s/] Completely and utterly preposterous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bafb3",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: There [i]is[/i] no conspiracy![p/][s/] These insurrectionists [i]are[/i] real!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e469",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: What proof do you have that I was working with that boy anyway?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de107f",
  "node": "LloydCornered3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Everything he's been doing has nothing to do with me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a696a7",
  "node": "LloydCornered4",
  "text": "Ring"
}

{
  "id": "line:024ba41",
  "node": "LloydCornered4",
  "text": "No...[p/] It wasn't indisputable proof,[p/] but I did have something that at least proved a Pillar Family was involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1e87a",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about this ring, von Sanctus?![p/] It was a crucial tool in many of Justin's robberies!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0763206",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]What about it?![p/][s/] You can't tie that ring to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e849a",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was fitted with artificery that was a lot more advanced than what's available to the public!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e27ee",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Only a Pillar Family would have access to something like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b00fe8",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Lloyd: S-[p/][s/]Surely that's conjecture, at best!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0baeaf4",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe,[p/] but it still points to the fact that someone of high status was involved in this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1b23b",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Lloyd: He was working with insurrectionists!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019e0a5",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Lloyd: Those dissidents are crafty,[p/][s/] and they are [i]all[/i] over Wyverngarde!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c18817",
  "node": "LloydCornered5",
  "text": "Lloyd: That boy was one of them![p/][s/] He was working hand in hand with them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0756e",
  "node": "LloydCornered6",
  "text": "Phantom4"
}

{
  "id": "line:00042bb",
  "node": "LloydCornered6",
  "text": "No...[p/] He was trying to deflect blame to the insurrectionists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f363cc",
  "node": "LloydCornered6",
  "text": "But I knew that the reports of insurrection in Aurinax were false,[p/] and the evidence supported that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a85a1",
  "node": "LloydCornered6",
  "text": "Which meant that something Justin did contradicted what von Sanctus was saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:096923b",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Justin was truly working with these insurrectionists,[p/] then why did he [i]rob[/i] so many of them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d40a6",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]Well, I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ac932",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only did he rob them of all of their possessions,[p/] his robberies \"revealed\" them to the authorities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbdd16",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you seriously think he'd do that to the very people he was working with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5bff",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: T-[p/][s/]Then...[p/] He must have betrayed them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092f8cd",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: He was in massive debt, wasn't he?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b93ede",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: He must have become desperate and took whatever he could to pay those off!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0905651",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did you know about Justin Waye's debts?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082a814",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5078b",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I merely inferred it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b08a3",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's not uncommon for peasants to overextend themselves financially."
}

{
  "id": "line:01de59d",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e87b7",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: I don't have to prove anything to you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4f5b8",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: That boy was desperate,[p/] and both of us know it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d076e8",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: He was a thieving rat![p/][s/] He had loyalty to no one!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022ff8a",
  "node": "LloydCornered7",
  "text": "Lloyd: He would betray anyone to pay off his debts!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6d0e",
  "node": "LloydCornered8",
  "text": "No...[p/] He was trying to paint Justin as some petty thief."
}

{
  "id": "line:0442c12",
  "node": "LloydCornered8",
  "text": "He was pushed into the corner because of his debts,[p/] but there [i]was[/i] a line he wouldn't cross despite that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a90e10",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Except there [i]was[/i] one person he clearly didn't betray, von Sanctus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09defa9",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: When he entered my client's office,[p/][s/] he successfully broke into his safe!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d73acd",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: He had every opportunity to take the gold there,[p/] but he [i]chose[/i] not to!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d548a8",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Lloyd: So he had a crisis of conscience![p/] So what?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06078be",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're trying to paint Justin Waye as some kind of heartless criminal who supported the insurrections!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02650bb",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] that's completely contradicted by his own actions!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007fa0c",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: He had no idea about the fact that he was planting evidence of insurrection within the homes of his targets!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c228",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: He had no idea that he would be planting a bomb in the refinery using your ring!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0336df9",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he had no idea that the person telling him to do these things was [i]you[/i], Lloyd von Sanctus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089de7d",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "The duke's eyes nervously shot around the courtroom.[p/] He looked like a cornered animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:086cba4",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Every eye was on him.[p/] He could have denied everything,[p/] but his nervous indignation had betrayed what he'd done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0187438",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: ...There's no evidence, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa3c2",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: There's no evidence that actually proves he was involved with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:053474d",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: You only have the ring,[p/] and that won't be concrete enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eab990",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081b284",
  "node": "LloydCornered9",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's right![p/][s/] There's no evidence tying me to that boy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:091c174",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Steelwind![p/][s/] What are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008a99b",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "AriaC: You can't indict someone with this little evidence—[p/]especially not a duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5dbb4",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "AriaC: If I were to bring this to trial,[p/] it would never hold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbdc85",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ha![p/][s/] You're completely right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0992062",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "Lloyd: You don't have any evidence against me! [h=\"I made sure to cover|all of my tracks!\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00af654",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "But everyone here knew he did it![p/][s/] It was written all over his face a moment ago!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0922a4a",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "He was going to blow up half of my city just so he could sell some Constructs![p/][s/] Countless lives would have been lost!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c633d",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "After all that,[p/][s/] was he seriously going to get away with this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcbc83",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "Come on![p/][s/] There [i]had[/i] to be something![p/][s/] There was [i]always[/i] something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04969bc",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "They [i]always[/i] leave something behind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e888c",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "...But he was careful about this.[p/] He kept his distance from Justin and used Violetta to deliver his communications."
}

{
  "id": "line:0427129",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "The only reason that [i]I[/i] found out was because of my ability to talk to animals,[p/] and it's not as if I could prove [i]that[/i] either..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08002c8",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "...There was only one move I had left."
}

{
  "id": "line:033d5ac",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ha,[p/] glaring like that is unbecoming of you, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af37b9",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b17790",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be something he left behind—[p/]some sort of mistake he made."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a291",
  "node": "LloydCornered10",
  "text": "He was really careful about this.[p/] I just had to hold out hope that he slipped up somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:08605d9",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Autopsy|Justin|Phantom|Strap2|Queen"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b58089",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Could anyone prove that I was communicating with that boy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b6457",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: No,[p/] I made sure that all of my communications were delivered through [b]Send Message[b/]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0580b44",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I never actually met that boy in person.[p/] I just used Violetta to see him."
}

{
  "id": "line:08afec0",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Damn it all...[p/] [b]Send Message[b/] wouldn't leave any evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e67cb6",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "It was also a [b]conjuration[/b] spell,[p/] and [i]those[/i] traces were already on Justin because of the ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ce858",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Von Sanctus planned for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4156b",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Ring|Teleport|Summon"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b290e",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Could they use the ring in any way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c43cfe",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: No...[p/] That ring may be advanced,[p/] but it can't be tied to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0470075",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I commissioned it anonymously,[p/] and the artificer that made it has already returned to Arcarus."
}

{
  "id": "line:056137e",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Even if they did know who he was,[p/] they would never have enough time [i]or[/i] evidence to extradite him here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fd83f",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "He had the ring manufactured in a way that couldn't be tied to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:055d326",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "How long had he been planning this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfb83d",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Blockade|HousePic|Aster"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c34ab4",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Luckily for me,[p/] that container was already abandoned on the beach."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e007ac",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I cast magic through Violetta to transport the container to the house."
}

{
  "id": "line:03aab9a",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Then,[p/] when that boy placed the crystals inside the chest,[p/] I used Violetta to move the bomb into place."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b8276",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Of course,[p/] that bomb was constructed personally.[p/] I made sure to only use materials that the boy stole."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3325c",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: To anyone else,[p/] it would look like [i]he[/i] constructed that bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21323",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "He had Justin do everything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e1a6a",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "He didn't even place the bomb himself.[p/] He just teleported it into the house using Violetta somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5254",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "And the chest was already covered in traces of [b]conjuration[b/] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4e74",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "He was careful about this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9ed7e",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "UnionTensions|Treason|Noah|Lucio"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b3d88",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: After all that hard work,[p/] I can't believe Lucio saw through our plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:089586c",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: He's more shrewd than we gave him credit for."
}

{
  "id": "line:094e56c",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Either that,[p/] or he just got lucky."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2180",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'll need to talk to William."
}

{
  "id": "line:009dbb5",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "William...[p/] Was he talking about William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052f5f7",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "...Ugh.[p/] It didn't matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:027ad6e",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Tyrion|Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:066fca8",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I knew those two had a vendetta against the nobility,[p/] but to think that they'd go after [i]me[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc7ae6",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]I'm[/i] a duke for crying out loud!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f49de8",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Do they have no sense of fear at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc6c3",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f5539",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I knew the young Steelwind had issues with her father.[p/] The entire aristocracy knows about it by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:029a73f",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...At least that's what I thought,[p/] but were they working together this entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006c2b3",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I thought I could use her against her father,[p/] but she played me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0222ce5",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd"
}

{
  "id": "line:088f35b",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I have nothing to fear.[p/] Even [i]if[/i] they can prove my involvement,[p/] any evidence they had would be flimsy at best."
}

{
  "id": "line:007c71a",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm the Duke of Commerce.[p/] They can't touch me."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b955",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline will hear about this...[p/] What am I going to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f64fbe",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm tired of deceiving her.[p/] She deserves better than this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dce444",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ugh...[p/] What am I thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39695",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I must do everything I can to preserve the future of my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ced04f",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Stefanic"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f2675",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Even if our plan didn't succeed,[p/] I was hoping I could at least wipe that wretch off the map."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ffb1b",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: His insidious ideas would be amputated right where they started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f92a12",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What a mess.[p/] I was really hoping to use that land too."
}

{
  "id": "line:073b542",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "ShipRep"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4534",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I had no choice but to have the Constructs pass through the border officially."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268f6d",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: It would've been impossible to move that much cargo into Aurinax secretly."
}

{
  "id": "line:047eb6e",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "RikaTest"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb2e34",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: That fool ruined everything.[p/] He even allowed people to see him use the ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d15e3",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Well,[p/] no matter.[p/] Even with his act of rebellion,[p/] no one can tie this to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fc137",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Damn it all...[p/] I can't afford to think about such things now."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d244a",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: I need to focus on maintaining this ruse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c802ec",
  "node": "LloydEye",
  "text": "There was nothing there for me to use."
}

{
  "id": "line:047f3ea",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "No...[p/] He'd accounted for everything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0414d58",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: You can ruminate all you want.[p/] There's nothing you can do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0714706",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "Lloyd: Face it, boy.[p/] You've [i]lost[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0435d59",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "I wasn't naïve enough to think that I'd be able to win every case,[p/] but I never imagined that I'd lose one as important as this."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f179",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "...Was I really going to lose, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033f57a",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye",
  "text": "Mosourika: The source of my power is the everlasting support of the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f02315",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Noah: I didn't trust it at first,[p/] but Dracogen's idea really took off."
}

{
  "id": "line:08398ff",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Noah: Finally having a say in things has been great for the workers in the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:083249f",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] The worker's unions were Stefanic Dracogen's idea?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e39dbf",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I've seen how this kingdom treats those at the bottom of society."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e5944",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Stefanic: Those without are treated like tools—[p/]worked by their employers until they break and need to be replaced."
}

{
  "id": "line:095c1d6",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Stefanic: It's a simple thing, really.[p/] When you keep your employees happy,[p/] they perform better,[p/] and that pays itself forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6151c",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I created the first workers' union with Noah to allow workers to better advocate for themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcfb0b",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I'm glad to see it's set a precedent for the employees of other companies to do the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:069e099",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Dracogen was doing a lot of good and setting an example for others to follow."
}

{
  "id": "line:059cbe5",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "The entire reason why I took this case was to defend him.[p/] Somehow I'd lost sight of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3f82b",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tell me, von Sanctus,[p/] do you truly believe that Justin Waye's death was my client's fault?"
}

{
  "id": "line:078b773",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Well, it certainly wasn't [i]my[/i] fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5eb78",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That wasn't what I asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acb279",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you believe that the guardrail broke because of my client's negligence or because of Justin's ring?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0023f56",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "He stayed silent for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab8979",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...It was [i]obviously[/i] because of Dracogen's negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:087017b",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: After all,[p/] there's no proof that Justin attempted to activate that ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5089a",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about the traces of [b]conjuration[/b] magic on the container?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f06f",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Any number of [b]conjuration[/b] spells could have been cast on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfd330",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And the rail-shaped indents on the container?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca9fc",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: A coincidence.[p/] That container could have come from anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5724e",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Look,[p/] unless you can prove that the container was in the refinery,[p/] you have no case."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd6cc",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye4",
  "text": "Strap2"
}

{
  "id": "line:09986ea",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye4",
  "text": "No...[p/] I would need a physical piece of evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0926157",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye4",
  "text": "The container had been in the refinery—[p/]if only for a moment.[p/] What could prove that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cded5",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Justin grabbed Violetta's collar shortly before he activated the ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b30fa",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "We found half of this collar lodged in the container.[p/] Justin dropped the other half before he fell into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99aaf",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this collar, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a5fb0",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's Violetta's collar.[p/] I was wondering where it had disappeared to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b40634",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Judge: ...\"Violetta\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c4364",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the name of the Duke's cat, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:057c859",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye5",
  "text": "Lloyd: And what?[p/][s/] Do you think you can implicate me just because my [i]cat[/i] was at the scene of the accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0679535",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm more interested in where both halves of this collar were found."
}

{
  "id": "line:009f143",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...\"Halves\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a8007",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: This collar is really unique.[p/] It even has a name engraved into this leather."
}

{
  "id": "line:05167f3",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which raises one question."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c76274",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why was one half of this collar dropped by Justin,—"
}

{
  "id": "line:001edcf",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: —while the other half was found lodged in the chest containing the bomb?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04af8de",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d76cbf",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: As you very well know,[p/] Justin activated the ring,[p/] but the spell failed to fully switch his position with the bomb's."
}

{
  "id": "line:0177b21",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But before he did that,[p/] he grabbed Violetta's collar."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b5adc",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure what exactly happened,[p/] but the failed teleportation must have split this collar in half."
}

{
  "id": "line:0765f62",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: One half remained in Justin's grasp,[p/] while the other half was lodged into the chest that briefly appeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d71e0",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: This proves one indisputable fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b482c4",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That Justin [i]did[/i] activate the ring,[p/] causing the metal container to briefly appear on the guardrail and break it apart!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f58ea",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The death of Justin Waye was not a result of my client's negligence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031b624",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Lloyd: So what?![p/] That doesn't prove my involvement in anything that happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ad6f3",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That doesn't matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace76a",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: My job is and always has been to defend and acquit Dracogen from your false charges!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0544cf7",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I may not be able to win this time,[p/][s/] but neither will you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0794e91",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Despite your best efforts,[p/][s/] my client will continue to operate in Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a78d9",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye6",
  "text": "Tyrion: So with that said,[p/] I'll settle for a stalemate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e37919",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Judge: Does the prosecution have any rebuttals to the defense's claims?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae26b0",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "AriaC: ...We do not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0574dd2",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "JUDGE: Then the court sees no reason to prolong this trial any further."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc64d6",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...How typical."
}

{
  "id": "line:094d259",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: You truly are a rat,[p/] scrounging at whatever scraps you can scrape together."
}

{
  "id": "line:003607e",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client is safe now.[p/] That's all that matters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0293646",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: Is his delusion contagious or something,[p/] or are you just trying to cope with your loss?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ca11",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've seen how much Aurinax has changed because of his actions.[p/] There's a significance to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08045ea",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: All you've [i]seen[/i] is our society take one small step closer to anarchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0948ab9",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] No matter.[p/] He's just one man."
}

{
  "id": "line:059987a",
  "node": "LloydAfterEye7",
  "text": "Lloyd: It won't be long before he's forgotten."
}

{
  "id": "line:059a814",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "I exhaled deeply,[p/] the weight of this trial finally off my shoulders."
}

{
  "id": "line:054ea20",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Out of every case I've defended,[p/] this was easily the most stressful one."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0359",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "But I didn't know if I could consider this a victory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84e12",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "I still couldn't believe I just let von Sanctus get away with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0110971",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Was there anything I could have done differently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0359988",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hey,[p/] don't look like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fda625",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you wanted to bring the Duke to justice,[p/] but you did a good thing today!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf029f",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] What I really wanted was revenge."
}

{
  "id": "line:074da51",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't be like that![p/] You did a good thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0353d3c",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Celeste: Dracogen can continue operating in Aurinax,[p/] and Rika gets to keep her café."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf72d",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...For now.[p/] Von Sanctus isn't going to take this lying down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07bf0",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's bound to try something else once the publicity dies down."
}

{
  "id": "line:090d986",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...I wouldn't be so sure about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c150a",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Tyrion: Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddde93",
  "node": "end",
  "text": "Stefanic: He may be acquitted in the eyes of the justice system,[p/] but the court of public opinion is a different thing entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d85eb",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: Everyone saw how he was acting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0197ad6",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: You may not have proved it in the legal sense,[p/] but it was obvious to everyone what he'd done.[p/] I'm sure word will spread."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dec3bb",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that really enough, though?[p/] He should be locked up after what he tried to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:01859c0",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: I don't disagree with you,[p/] but there's something to be said about where his true power lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:00612b9",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you talking about his position?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab7a2",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: Not his position,[p/] but his image."
}

{
  "id": "line:051ca8b",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: People like Lloyd thrive on making the commonfolk feel powerless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0744f3f",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: He needs people to believe that there's nothing they can do in the face of his influence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b96e85",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: Today,[p/] you revealed Lloyd for what he truly is:[p/] a weak and desperate fool,[p/] blinded by greed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2a370",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: His allies will keep him at a distance,[p/] and his enemies will jump at this opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be1b30",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Stefanic: His days [i]are[/i] numbered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc9599",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: ...There [i]is[/i] some truth to his words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c401f5",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Prosecutor Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8b789",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: It seems that my father had some suspicions about what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0992ecd",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: But even [i]he[/i] never considered von Sanctus to be the mastermind behind this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05726d4",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: It's really unlike him.[p/] We [i]all[/i] underestimated what he was capable of."
}

{
  "id": "line:082f067",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You were trying to help me catch him, weren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011c261",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why you kept drawing out the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ae22",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I obviously can't confirm or deny that."
}

{
  "id": "line:033c9cb",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: But I [i]did[/i] think that if [i]anyone[/i] could reveal his crimes,[p/] it would be you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f98a3",
  "node": "end2",
  "text": "Aria: ...Perhaps I was being too hopeful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0345590",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Don't sell yourselves short."
}

{
  "id": "line:0396811",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: As I said,[p/] there's value in how [i]you[/i] appear to the public as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9cd81",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: You've been standing your ground against the nobility.[p/] You even challenged a duke this time around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0774de2",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: I've seen it throughout the kingdom.[p/] You've lit a flame in those who might've lost hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a6d3",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I really wouldn't go that far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba4bf1",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Don't underestimate the light of inspiration."
}

{
  "id": "line:0959e87",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: It may start from a single ember,[p/] but it can spread to all those that are willing to accept it within themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3bdc",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: No one can stop a flame like that once it starts—[p/]not you,[p/] not me,[p/] not even the king himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f02f82",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "Stefanic: That's why I started the workers' unions.[p/] I wanted to show people that our society could become something better."
}

{
  "id": "line:096d1e1",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "...It was definitely hopeful,[p/] and after everything that had happened,[p/] I could use a bit more hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b8b50",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "I would just need to keep doing what I was doing.[p/] The future would show how true Dracogen's words were."
}

{
  "id": "line:088bd4f",
  "node": "end3",
  "text": "...But I still felt uneasy.[p/] Even if von Sanctus would lose power,[p/] a cornered animal was the most dangerous one."
}

{
  "id": "line:02581eb",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...You filthy rat![p/] I [i]will[/i] have words with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bb05b",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Oh,[p/] speak of the devil."
}

{
  "id": "line:0984f3a",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey, back off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1822f",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's fine.[p/] I can handle him, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c30f9",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So,[p/] what's so important, [i]Your Grace[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05385c1",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...There is no arcane spell in the world that can intercept the communications between a mage and their familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:089f99d",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: What did you do to Violetta?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007dd89",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A \"familiar\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e09ae1",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: Don't be coy with me, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:09194d4",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I saw you![p/][s/] I saw you speaking with her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:045aaa2",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...That is not any of your concern, Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:052ee41",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: L-[p/][s/]Lucio..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07903ef",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: I suggest you stop harassing Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Lest you be suspected of coercion."
}

{
  "id": "line:039a430",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: So [i]that's[/i] what this was![p/][s/] He's one of yours!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e64b16",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lloyd: This isn't over, Lucio![p/][s/] This is [i]far[/i] from over!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbab83",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "The Duke of Commerce left in a huff,[p/] grumbling to himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de1668",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "I narrowed my eyes at the Grand General.[p/] For the first time,[p/] he wasn't surrounded by his knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b06c5",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...He was speaking about [b]Familial Bond[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2b64",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: Whatever animal you spoke with was Lloyd von Sanctus's familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84b3f",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "So [i]that's[/i] how he was speaking with Violetta![p/] It was just an arcane spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e45f0",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "But that just raised another question..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9305a",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did you know that I spoke with his familiar?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e012c4",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: An educated guess.[p/] You can speak to all animals, can you not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f639",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "I blinked at him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af6be8",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...What is the Theocracy planning here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0806bb1",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Theocracy?[p/] Are you talking about the kingdom west of us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc2c03",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: Don't play games with me.[p/] I'm no fool."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c61362",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not![p/] I have no idea what you're talking about!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93f02",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd2",
  "text": "Lucio: Then why are you able to use Luminian magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0728fdf",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: You possess the Eye of Radiance:[p/] the ability to read the minds of others."
}

{
  "id": "line:033d84a",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "I eyed him warily...[p/] He seemed to know more about the Eye of Horus than [i]I[/i] did."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8009",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: Like I said before,[p/] I've read the transcripts of your past cases."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd072d",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: And what you did to me during the first session all but proved it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5a4a5",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "The Theocracy of Lumina was the nation west of us,[p/] and Wyverngarde's most hated enemy."
}

{
  "id": "line:006bf6e",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "I didn't know much about them.[p/] Any written information about them was heavily controlled by the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be3ca0",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm not an agent of the Theocracy, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:027b485",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: Perhaps.[p/] Perhaps not."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bec42",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So what?[p/][s/] Are you going to have me executed for treason?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07efdc2",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering what's been happening lately,[p/] I doubt that would be a good look for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2c0bc",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: Just the opposite.[p/] You are now going to be [i]my[/i] agent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6df3f",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: There will come a day when I will require your skills and abilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe49f2",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: The Eye of Radiance is too powerful a weapon for me to squander.[p/] I imagine it will be of great use to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d02a0",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And if I refuse?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d400db",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: Then I will treat you just like any other foreign agent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02574",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Lucio: Be ready.[p/] I imagine the day I call upon you will come sooner rather than later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b528bd",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd3",
  "text": "Celeste rushed over to me as soon as the Grand General left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e81852",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you okay?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c5fec",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah...[p/] I'm fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b07210",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: He didn't hurt you, did he?[p/][s/] What did he say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a73bfb",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think he's forcing me to work for him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0228000",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b83c76",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": ":He knew about the Eye of Horus...[p/] It was supposedly related to the Theocracy:[p/] Wyverngarde's greatest rivals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8bf5",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "After what I'd learned in the last few months,[p/] I figured that there must exist other types of magic.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db251a",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "But I never considered that there might be an entire nation of people with abilities like mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a419d8",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "No wonder I couldn't find any information on the Eye of Horus.[p/] Wyverngarde heavily curated any information about Lumina."
}

{
  "id": "line:0098deb",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess it doesn't matter.[p/] It's a problem for later."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bb185",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll talk to Aria about this.[p/] She might be able to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a877e",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: We're actually heading to a tavern.[p/] Do you want to come with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c855d2",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] I'm going to go see Rika."
}

{
  "id": "line:029d912",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She'll want to know about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05e62",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright."
}

{
  "id": "line:0452ba5",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don't cause too much trouble for her.[p/] She's dealing with a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b2426",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] I [i]never[/i] cause trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:01943e8",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dacbf0",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "It may have come with a side of coercion,[p/] but the Grand General [i]did[/i] give me another lead on the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:02871c3",
  "node": "LloydConfrontEnd4",
  "text": "I needed to talk to Ms. Tymora about this.[p/] We might be able to dig up more information about the Theocracy and [i]its[/i] \"magic\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0344757",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Nobleman: Your Grace,[p/] you have a visitor.[p/] It's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f07cee",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I thought I told you I wanted to be left alone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b776de",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: What idiot—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5efc",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff482d",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]William![p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0466f9d",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: You absolute moron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5555",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]It's not what it looks like![p/] They couldn't even [i]prove[/i] anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e16f9",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: It doesn't matter![p/] Even a [i]child[/i] could have told that you were guilty!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2c1eb",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: We [i]needed[/i] those Constructs to cripple Lucio's hold on the military,[p/][s/] and now those bloody things are attached to [i]your[/i] accursed name!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0926947",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: Do you have any idea how difficult it will be to sell these things to the House of Lords now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00238ff",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: Enough.[p/] Your house will soon be in shambles."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5edee",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "William: I have a plan that will at least allow us to salvage what's left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0141645",
  "node": "WilliamEnd",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...\"S-[p/][s/]Salvage\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033b93c",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: It's all a bit anticlimactic, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0062ff2",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eris: What is, Father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0836639",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I was really counting on all hell breaking loose in this city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7440e",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Either old Lloyd would suceed,[p/] or Lucio would sus him out and take his head in a bloody spectacle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa872c",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Ruby's kid really pulls through to a fault, doesn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048a31c",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Everything ended too peacefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f918b0",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eris: ...He does tend to do that, doesn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b9a53",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: We don't even have Justin to show for all our trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a22c7",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I was really betting on him entering the fold with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2699",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: It's a pity.[p/] He was taken from us too soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e03abc",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eris: Don't worry.[p/] We still have Frega on our side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0647643",
  "node": "EyetakerEnd",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Yeah...[p/] We'll just have to put the final piece on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da6aea",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "I walked into the cafe again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9e45c",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "I was coming after the lunch rush.[p/] There weren't that many people there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c680dd",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "I spotted her talking to one of her employees."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b91e4c",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "Mosourika: Check the inventory and tell me if we're running low on anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:081de79",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "Mosourika: I don't want us scrambling around like last week."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babcf2",
  "node": "RikaNTyr",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2713",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Everyone's talking about what happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7b3b1",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: It seems the Duke of Commerce was no match for the Lightsworn Monarch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f79b63",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...What's that look for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4e90d",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: You [i]did[/i] win, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0041313",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a bit more complicated than that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7f3cd",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc1062",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbe720",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Is that really all we are to people like him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e74fb",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: So many people could have gotten hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:038632e",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I live pretty close to the industrial district.[p/] [i]I[/i] could have been caught in that explosion."
}

{
  "id": "line:011b091",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't imagine what would've happened if Justin had never decided to rebel against von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d2315",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Did he really do that though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:024998f",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Do you really think he was rebelling against the Duke?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b43f8c",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Maybe he just decided to teleport on that catwalk instead of the office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61fd6",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought you believed in him more than anyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2e6f",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I did,[p/] but did I really know anything about him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1c56b",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: He was different after he served his sentence...[p/] Not [i]worse[/i],[p/] just different."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3e018",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I never knew he had debts to a criminal overlord."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ebcbb",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "Mosourika: I never knew what actually happened to him in the dungeons over those years.[p/] He [i]never[/i] wanted to talk about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09228d3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "I'd read a lot of stories about what happened in the dungeons throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5913",
  "node": "RikaNTyr2",
  "text": "I couldn't imagine what he must have gone through in there."
}

{
  "id": "line:008ad03",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...It was my fault he went through that.[p/] I should have never let him take the fall for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65a27",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't say that.[p/] He made his own decision,[p/] and that decision was to protect you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc243f",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3b",
  "text": "Phantom"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c04b3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3b",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin [i]was[/i] robbing a lot of people,[p/] including innocent commoners who were a part of the union."
}

{
  "id": "line:02270f9",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3b",
  "text": "But there was a point this week where he made a decision."
}

{
  "id": "line:077961c",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3b",
  "text": "He decided he wouldn't just take what he wanted for his own gain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9a39e",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: He had every reason to take the gold in Dracogen's safe,[p/] but he left it there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0108acd",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: He didn't know what those documents would be used for,[p/] but he knew that taking that gold would harm Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1ade3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: He left it.[p/] Despite everything he was doing,[p/] he still held gratitude and respect towards Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:02311eb",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I guess that makes sense when you put it that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3a3d",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Thanks."
}

{
  "id": "line:09334df",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Mosourika: I know it's been a while,[p/] but if you ever need to talk,[p/] I'm here."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c1dd9",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "And that ended another chapter in my life as an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:05146e5",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "I always swore that I'd never return to Aurinax.[p/] I thought I needed to keep the past buried."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f5326",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "But coming back here was exactly what I needed to start burying what happened all those years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f5040",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "I honestly still felt an indignant fury towards the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce76c9",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "I didn't think I could ever forget what he had planned for this city."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cbbfc",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "But I wasn't alone anymore.[p/] I had Ms. Tymora,[p/] I had Celeste,[p/] and I had my friends in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa3b4",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "I didn't need to carry all of this by myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f33725",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "And in that moment—[p/]thinking back to the night Celeste comforted me—[p/]I realized something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10383",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think I have feelings for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fdcb3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "I stood up from my seat,[p/] my eyes wide in terror.[p/] The migraine returned with a vengeance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0262b5d",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord![p/][s/] I think I have feelings for Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c485",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Mosourika: O-[p/][s/]Oh![p/][s/] Shi—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec526e",
  "node": "RikaNTyr3c",
  "text": "Mosourika: That's great, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f758e1",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...[i]Is[/i] that great?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddfe61",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: I don't actually know what the deal is between you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0036",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's my coworker, Rika..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cfe3f",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah,[p/] but you're obviously more than that.[p/] You're friends, at least."
}

{
  "id": "line:0785a9d",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "I'd never even considered romantic relationships until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0783462",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "We spent a lot of time together anyway...[p/] What would that even change if we went down that route?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021413b",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "...Humans entered romantic relationships to fulfill emotional needs and engage in intimacy,[p/] both of which enriched the lives of both parties."
}

{
  "id": "line:037eed3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "...Thinking about the intimacy was [i]very[/i] distracting.[p/][s/] I needed to focus on something else..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d21e3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Rika,[p/] what do I do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0700baf",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Tyrion,[p/] I've known her for [i]three days[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a97627",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: You really need to give me more to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:006dedf",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Uh—[p/] Well—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ebf8f",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess it all started a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:00125c3",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I met her at a tavern,[p/] and she introduced herself with a joke about masturbation—[p/]I think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:026669a",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It made more sense the way she said it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65f52",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: Okay,[p/] let's just start with something simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210aad",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: How did she start working as your bodyguard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba01fd",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/] [i]that's[/i] a bit of a long story too."
}

{
  "id": "line:088e78a",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Rika sat down at the table nearby as she called over the waiter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0427245",
  "node": "RikaNTyr4",
  "text": "Mosourika: I've got some hours to kill before the dinner rush.[p/] Tell me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0548fd7",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Walkway"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a045f1",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a walkway that overlooks the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0156cd7",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a little concerning how close it is to the vats."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4b55e",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I suppose the guardrails [i]should[/i] keep the employees safe when they're up there."
}

{
  "id": "line:01575de",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Stairs"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde7f1",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: These metal stairs lead up to the walkway above."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84cc1",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Vat"
}

{
  "id": "line:0356208",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a vat filled with chemicals that I can't quite identify."
}

{
  "id": "line:05af536",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to Celeste,[p/] these chemicals are used to refine and create Arcane Crystals."
}

{
  "id": "line:045d955",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Power Box"
}

{
  "id": "line:04eac73",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a power box.[p/] It contains artificery hardware and an arcane power cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b43ad",
  "node": "Factory1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's connected to the chemical vats.[p/] So, it must control some function of the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0328c6c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Victim"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5adad",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika mentioned that Justin was an employee of yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d613ac",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you tell us more about him?[p/] What was he like when he was working here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5df9f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: Yes...[p/] I hired him just a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b007c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: It's a shame what happened to him,[p/] and at such a young age too."
}

{
  "id": "line:01adc9d",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was he a good employee?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035ae1c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: He was a hard worker,[p/] but he was a bit rough around the edges when he first started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0476452",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: He wasn't great at following the rules at first,[p/] but he was good with his hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422e5d",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: I wasn't sure what to make of him at first,[p/] but Ms. Tudor practically begged me to hire him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6b1a",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "That [i]did[/i] sound like her.[p/] She always had a habit of getting involved in her friends' business."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d345d4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: He was a good man.[p/] All he needed was some structure and direction in life."
}

{
  "id": "line:073c4d5",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: After only a few weeks of working for me,[p/] he was following the rules more than anyone else here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a47795",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...Which only makes me more confused as to why he was up there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0074c72",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Walkway"
}

{
  "id": "line:0558e51",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Earlier,[p/] you mentioned that Justin wasn't \"supposed\" to be on the walkway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0705b9c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0697d61",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: Well, Justin worked in an entirely different department."
}

{
  "id": "line:00520b0",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: He was part of a team that managed packaging and freight."
}

{
  "id": "line:019c288",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: He had no business being [i]inside[/i] the refinery building—[p/]much less up on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0636ae4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Was he the type of person to wander around places that he wasn't supposed to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4e69c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: We had a few issues like that when he started a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0896e89",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: But like I said before,[p/] he always followed my rules when he was working today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abba44",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: It all just makes this whole situation [i]that[/i] much more confusing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0379167",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] My contractors assured me that the damage to the guardrail was nothing to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3a53f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: From what Rika said,[p/] someone used a spell to break the guardrail apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:062be84",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that's true,[p/] I doubt Justin's death was your fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:0434c06",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Robbery"
}

{
  "id": "line:0028cca",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that the Mistweaving Phantom hit the refinery this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b22cad",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which part of the refinery did they break into, and what did they steal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a325a",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...That's the strangest thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac9b4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: The thief broke into my office and cracked my magically locked safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b9b31",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: That safe contained my business records and several gold coins I keep on hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c74d2",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: They stole the records,[p/] but left the gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce9957",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Why would they leave it after going to so much trouble to break in?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5c784",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is the Phantom actually after?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05052ee",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: Your answer is as good as mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0007fb2",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Was the location that Justin fell from close to your office?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0060a30",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Stefanic: Yes,[p/] my office is positioned there to overlook the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f255f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "If the robbery occurred close to the time of Justin's death,[p/] did he spot the Phantom while he was up there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053396d",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Workers' Unions"
}

{
  "id": "line:012617a",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041dad7",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0422703",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: This morning,[p/] a factory worker named Justin Waye was walking on the catwalk above us."
}

{
  "id": "line:040f088",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: When he put his weight on the guardrail,[p/] it broke apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:070fe48",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: He unfortunately fell straight into a vat of corrosive chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69b7f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: It wasn't exactly a peaceful way to go out."
}

{
  "id": "line:082be70",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: One witness:[p/] Mosourika Tudor,[p/] saw this happen and reported what she saw immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5066c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: The workers quickly followed safety protocol and poured a concoction into the vat to neutralize its corrosive properties."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f177d4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: But it was far too late.[p/] By the time they pulled him out,[p/] the only thing left of Justin's body was his bones and one of his personal effects."
}

{
  "id": "line:040b8a5",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I have the Autopsy Report if you'd like to take a closer look."
}

{
  "id": "line:034e9ea",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027d8c9",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: If the chemicals were strong enough to dissolve his body,[p/] how did this \"personal effect\" survive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6421",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: We're not sure.[p/] The item was a well-crafted ring,[p/] so it's possible it was made out of a material resistant to dissolution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a91de2",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: The workers' union had previously reported the damaged guardrail to the refinery owner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9f368",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: We're charging Stefanic Dracogen with criminal negligence for failing to repair it in a timely manner."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8244",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Mosourika said that she saw a spell push Justin into the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0123a60",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...That's what she told law enforcement too,[p/] but the evidence doesn't support that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b841f8",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: There were no traces of magic anywhere near the guardrail,[p/] save for the magical chemicals in the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78353",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: We didn't find any traces of [b]evocation[/b] magic to suggest an explosive spell pushed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26216",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: And there weren't any traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic to suggest that anyone weakened the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:044d787",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "It was possible Rika was in too much shock to remember what happened accurately,[p/] but it was still strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:09001af",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "I would need to talk to her again and get a more detailed description of what she saw this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:03438c0",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Dracogen Trading Company"
}

{
  "id": "line:0787c1f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you know about the Dracogen Trading Company?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f829a4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...I know that I've had to listen to the Duke of Commerce incessantly complain about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04802c3",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm guessing he doesn't get along with them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038b31b",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Stefanic Dracogen's trading company is supposedly posing a threat to his holdings."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fc6cc",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Lloyd also doesn't seem to approve of how he's been handling the workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:02008ae",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure he'd take issue with the simple fact that he allows them to exist."
}

{
  "id": "line:068fdae",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: It appears so.[p/] We've also received a lot of reports of rising tensions between Mr. Dracogen and the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff167f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Apparently, many known dissidents have joined them as a way to indirectly fight back against the aristocracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9d28",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: This refinery's union head:[p/] Noah Morrison, has denied this,[p/] but the reports tell a more honest story."
}

{
  "id": "line:0103176",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] [i]Mr. Morrison[/i] is the leader of the workers' unions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9d8a9",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Do you two know each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0770d0f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:069df6d",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Mr. Morrison was the harbourmaster of the Aurinax Harbor when I used to live here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56a64",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "He was a kind and generous man who used to watch me while my mother was working."
}

{
  "id": "line:082b4b6",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "I felt uneasy about talking to him after all these years,[p/] but I needed to warn him if he was getting himself involved with dissidents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c03b",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "...Although,[p/] it had been more than ten years since I'd last seen him.[p/] He could very well be one of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cbdca",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know where Dracogen is?[p/] I'd like to talk to him about this directly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08d96",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: The old timer's being questioned by the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d865e",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: They're asking him about the robbery that occurred before the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0b4d8",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sure he'll be back later today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e979b5",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Wait,[p/] the refinery was also robbed this morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025dfca",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Other Matter"
}

{
  "id": "line:053c267",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned you were here investigating another matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f10b0",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did something else happen here this morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0257b74",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...Over the last few months,[p/] there have been a string of suspicious robberies within Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbd41c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: They're a criminal who calls themselves the \"Mistweaving Phantom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1d0a9",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "...That style of naming sounded oddly familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4552",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: This city is a hub of global trade,[p/] and several ships belonging to the trading companies have been robbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dc838",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: These thefts were expertly executed.[p/] No one witnessed them,[p/] and they left no evidence behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7a20c",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: The few times when the Phantom [i]did[/i] trigger an alarm,[p/] it was as if they disappeared into thin air."
}

{
  "id": "line:060d757",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess this \"Phantom\" lives up to their name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6366b",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: What's most alarming is that an extremely dangerous shipment was stolen from an imperial ship this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0825fca",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did they steal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da217",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry,[p/] but [i]that[/i] is a matter of national security.[p/] I've already told you more than I should."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9aae3",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: It's not relevant to the case,[p/] so just leave that matter to my father and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:048c6e4",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: The Kingsguard have completely blockaded the city to keep anyone from getting away."
}

{
  "id": "line:028fb85",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "So [i]that's[/i] why they were blockading the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:08de864",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] Did you just say that your [i]father[/i] is here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f7a3",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Grand General Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4fdbe",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why is [i]Lucio Steelwind[/i] here?![p/][s/] What is he planning?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0887a26",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041a225",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: You have every right to be concerned,[p/] but it's out of our hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba4cc1",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: As I told you,[p/] the stolen shipment is a threat to national security."
}

{
  "id": "line:017a752",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: My father has taken it upon himself to search for it personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0838b78",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03210d3",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "...No.[p/] I needed to calm down."
}

{
  "id": "line:09013fb",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Lucio Steelwind may have been a bloodthirsty monster in the countryside,[p/] but Aurinax was a central trading hub in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a917e0",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "If he started a bloodbath here,[p/] it could very well cause the kingdom's economy to grind to a halt."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f85aa",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Even [i]he[/i] wasn't insane enough to do something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c681bc",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: My father has the best mages in the kingdom searching for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ac588",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: It's clear, however,[p/] that someone is using powerful [b]abjuration[/b] magic to mask its location."
}

{
  "id": "line:031d47f",
  "node": "Factory1_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: We'll just need to wait for this \"Phantom\" to be apprehended."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf4cd6",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How is your relationship with the local workers' unions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04abf0b",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: I'd certainly hope they're good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0529c55",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: We’ve had our disagreements, of course,[p/] but nothing we couldn't work out through discussion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4673d",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: Working in a refinery isn’t without its risks,[p/] and people want to be properly compensated for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f212",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: I just hope we can put this accident behind us and take more precautions in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:01337a6",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "He seemed to genuinely care,[p/] but it honestly sounded too good to be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3f2af",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Merchants tended to be more emotionally guarded.[p/] It naturally came with the occupation."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3804",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "I didn't see any thoughts through the Eye of Horus.[p/] What was he really thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ab85c",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I have to ask.[p/] Why would you propose the formation of the workers' unions in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b14e47",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: With all due respect,[p/] I'd think someone in your position would have every reason to [i]stop[/i] that from happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2fb1b",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: I don't blame you for thinking that,[p/] and I'm sure many other merchants in this kingdom would agree with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af5a1f",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: But that's exactly why I proposed it to Noah."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3d55",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: But tell me, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Do you own any appliances made by Von Sanctus Industries?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039edd1",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have a Von Sanctus brand oven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8c4b6",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Celeste: You mean that one that keeps breaking down?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed566",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: That's exactly the problem.[p/] The Duke's employees are so overworked that they naturally can't do their jobs properly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd95f3",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: Quality control is non-existent,[p/] but it's all about doing the bare minimum required to turn a profit with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:098889f",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "Stefanic: I'm not one to brag,[p/] but my products have been touted to be far more reliable than von Sanctus's."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c1b14",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "I guess I could see his logic there,[p/] and Von Sanctus' products [i]were[/i] pretty poorly made."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b8538",
  "node": "DracUnionConv",
  "text": "...Which only made those reports of tensions between them all the more strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bc021",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...Oh,[p/] is that a Runestone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008b8c9",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an [i]Attorney’s[/i] Runestone.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ebfa8",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I'm familiar with the concept.[p/] I know that law enforcement and certain members of the nobility have these."
}

{
  "id": "line:087467c",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...Honestly,[p/] I've always wondered how convenient my life would be if I had one of those."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cdc84",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would you need to take notes and pictures of crime scenes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b312f3",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I really appreciate you helping me in this matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2e30c",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's fine.[p/] If it weren't for the trial,[p/] I'd probably be stuck in the blockade like everyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0770e8e",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Nevertheless,[p/] I'm happy to have the infamous \"Tyrion Cuthbert\" as my counsel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a45fa7",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"Infamous\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0000972",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Oh,[p/] my apologies if that was offensive.[p/] That's just what the papers call you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ab0bd",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "I cringed at the thought of what they might be saying about me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f04f3",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "If it was anything like what they said about Ms. Tymora,[p/] I was probably better off not reading those articles."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dc1c9",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you know about the Duke of Commerce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09053de",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I've occasionally met him at some gatherings."
}

{
  "id": "line:01751a5",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: One time,[p/] he even \"complimented\" my company's success."
}

{
  "id": "line:0684d33",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: \"It's impressive how much one of such modest birth can accomplish,\" he said."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe939",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess his pettiness isn't limited to when he's losing at chess."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d638f",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d585f",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika mentioned that you gave her the capital to open her café."
}

{
  "id": "line:05597d8",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: After trying her food,[p/] I would be remiss not to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdbd05",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I'm aware of how difficult it is for a commoner mage to succeed in our society."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bf021",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's quite philanthropic of you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0643e8c",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Well,[p/] many other businessmen would show reluctance in dealing with a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ec889",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: That makes them an untapped resource."
}

{
  "id": "line:0971224",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "\"Pragmatic\" might be a better word to describe him..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7094c",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've heard a bit about your business.[p/] It sounds like it's expanding quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0684c28",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: It is.[p/] I'm honestly quite taken aback by how much success we've seen despite von Sanctus's interference."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d6cda",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...It's honestly growing a little too fast for my liking,[p/] but such is the world of commerce."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcd06",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I only hope I can properly take advantage of these opportunities."
}

{
  "id": "line:088328e",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Autopsy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0657f3a",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...I can't believe something like this happened in my refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bf8b3",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I [i]had[/i] been told that there was an issue with the guardrail,[p/] but I was assured it wasn't a problem."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a07cb",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: From what Rika said,[p/] the damage wasn't what caused Justin to fall."
}

{
  "id": "line:0061e97",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Right...[p/] There's also this mystery mage who may have attacked Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0805748",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: I honestly feel a little out of my depth right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:054bcfc",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] That's why I'm here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0995a49",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this ring?[p/] Justin was supposedly wearing it at the time of his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4b0f2",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...I'm not exactly sure.[p/] I never noticed him wearing it while he was working for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0958e2a",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It apparently wasn't damaged at all by the chemicals in the vat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8bb43",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: That [i]is[/i] strange,[p/] but there are certain alloys that are resistant to those chemicals."
}

{
  "id": "line:08424a8",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: The metal those vats are made of is the most obvious one."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c2e5",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Dracogen?[p/] Would you happen to recognize this leather strap?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a78e8",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Hm...[p/] No.[p/] It doesn't look all that familiar to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01783b1",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0544163",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure.[p/] Rika just said that Justin dropped this from the catwalk moments before his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3cde1",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...I'm sorry I can't help you,[p/] but I can at least say that it's not mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9bfe",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Noah|UnionTensions"
}

{
  "id": "line:007e97c",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: The \"Mistweaving Phantom\"...[p/] They're quite the urban legend from what I hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b606a",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have they ever robbed any of your shipments?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00927d0",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: A few times,[p/] but only the ones made through the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898976",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: A large portion of my shipments are made through land caravans,[p/] and none of those have gotten hit."
}

{
  "id": "line:060ec62",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess the Phantom prefers sticking to the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cac44a",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Although,[p/] he also hit the homes of some of the union members."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ffb90",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0900541",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Stefanic: Sorry, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] But I don't think I can tell you much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0729c98",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...I am well aware that you're an attorney, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ae3b7",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] I don't know why I always show this thing to people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6d265",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: It [i]is[/i] very useful.[p/] The artificery embedded into it is actually quite fascinating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1467f",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I wouldn't fault you for being excited about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c916",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You could fault him a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:011330e",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: It seems we're going to be facing each other again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7f5ea",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Although,[p/] I wasn't expecting our next case to be so mundane."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b2c3d",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: That remains to be seen.[p/] I still believe what happened to Justin wasn't an accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc93e",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I'd say that you're mistaken,[p/] but I have a feeling I may regret that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a76d",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Are you doing well, Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c009ae",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Yeah."
}

{
  "id": "line:03501c2",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7cb78",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I finally met Altheris Duskweaver."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ad8d",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I told you to temper your expectations."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d05a3",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I just didn't expect her to be so—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c993b",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Insufferable?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092c7e9",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: She wasn't always like that.[p/] She was once the humblest person I knew."
}

{
  "id": "line:0947e47",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...But as I said,[p/] fame has a way of changing people."
}

{
  "id": "line:071d0db",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I liked the food at that restaurant, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:069c5f5",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Yes,[p/] I'm quite a fan of it myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0804912",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Let's go there without her next time."
}

{
  "id": "line:012d0e3",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Will Tymora be joining as well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a07e55",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] I didn't even plan on defending a case while I was here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a53234",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's still back at our office in Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b592fd",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...Probably for the best."
}

{
  "id": "line:0259980",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I heard you defeated the Duke of Commerce in the chess tournament yesterday.[p/] Congratulations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0795eb8",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you.[p/] I'm surprised you even heard about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:024abb0",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: The Duke of Commerce has been complaining about your \"insolence\" non-stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:0597aab",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0561eab",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...Why do you look so satisfied with yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02940f1",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Come on,[p/] you have to admit that it's a [i]little[/i] funny how indignant he can get."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7be9a",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...You have a lot more in common with Tymora than I thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:038afd2",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: You must be seeing something that I don't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1379e",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: This was clearly and indisputably an accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0430e54",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll just have to see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebd7f6",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wouldn't be so quick to dismiss what Rika saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba3dd2",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I can't help but be wary of these workers' unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d6d20",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why?[p/][s/] They're just advocating for their basic rights."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2b8fc",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I don't disagree,[p/] but tensions between the wealthy and poor are at an all-time high."
}

{
  "id": "line:0491e21",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: The unions have noble intentions,[p/] but I'm worried they'll inevitably be dragged into that conflict."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a920ea",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: The \"Mistweaving Phantom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:00516bd",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have any idea who came up with that name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0331714",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Rumors like that tend to spread very quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af6794",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: It's difficult to find the true source of urban legends."
}

{
  "id": "line:09497c6",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "I had [i]some[/i] suspicions about the source of that particular name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd3d58",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Blockade2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79537",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you sure you can't tell me more about the missing shipment?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000cbbc",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: No.[p/] It's a matter of national security,[p/] and knowing would only put you in danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f11dc1",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: It's not relevant to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268953",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Blockade"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f727af",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you know why the Kingsguard are blockading the city?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0def832",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...Something dangerous was stolen from an imperial ship this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5cdbd",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: We need to make sure that it doesn't leave the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c00da",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: That's all I can tell you for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d62fbe",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0211da2",
  "node": "Factory1_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry.[p/] But I'm afraid I can't say much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fbbd",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "We arrived back at the refinery.[p/] The Inquisition was still sweeping factory ground,[p/] but Steelwind seemed to have left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0668f02",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "As we entered the factory,[p/] I spotted a large, unfamiliar figure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee316",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "He was old in his years,[p/] but his build carried the strength of someone who hadn't spent his life sitting idly."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e8a87",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "I could see a powerful yet steady temperament in his eyes.[p/] His posture carried the shrewdness of a clever businessman."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdeef2",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "The refinery employees who were still present were deferring to him.[p/] He must've been the owner of the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c893d",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "As we approached,[p/] he quickly noticed us and began waving us over."
}

{
  "id": "line:033e968",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: Hello, there.[p/] You must be the \"famous attorney\" that Ms. Tudor spoke about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2c2b",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am.[p/] I take it that you're the guild master of the Dracogen Trading Company?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb994",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8a650",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: I really appreciate you lending your aid in this matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:081611a",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I already told Rika this,[p/] but I've never tried a case like this before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af8823",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I honestly don't know how much help I'll be."
}

{
  "id": "line:012dbf1",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: Well,[p/] there isn't a single attorney in Aurinax that [i]will[/i] represent me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01765d3",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: So,[p/] I'd appreciate having you as my attorney—[p/]especially with the trial in only a few hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bf6a0",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: I thought it was strange too.[p/] The Duke must be pulling some strings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc114a",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "The courts usually only rushed cases to trial when they involved magic,[p/] but there was supposedly no magic involved in what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b07c3f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Did the prosecution know something I didn't?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1892f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "...I guess it didn't matter.[p/] I would just have to do what I could."
}

{
  "id": "line:07631ec",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay.[p/] If your trial is coming up,[p/] we'll need to move quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4c6f2",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can I ask you some questions about what happened, Dracogen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0276e57",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's clearly something more going on with this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1e573",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Stefanic: Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:05552ee",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "We made our way to Aurinax's Arcane Refinery.[p/] I'd always avoided the industrial district when I was a child."
}

{
  "id": "line:038232f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus always showed me a miasma of exhaustion and hopelessness draping over this part of town.[p/] I definitely felt less of that this time around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13547",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "I had gotten more used to dealing with my powers.[p/] Either that,[p/] or Aurinax's working conditions really had taken a turn for the better."
}

{
  "id": "line:09954b6",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow.[p/] So [i]this[/i] is an arcane refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:059b79f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never really understood what they do here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb69e1",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Those machines refine the arcane crystals that they use in artificery devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d70d7a",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Crystals like that can power everything from simple lights to advanced stuff like your Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97508",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How do you know this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9e3c7",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I basically [i]had[/i] to with all the extra reading I've been doing to learn how to fix your Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40e14",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry,[p/] I can't sense magic like you can."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c4f7d",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: ...Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ebd3f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "As we arrived,[p/] we spotted Steelwind directing the knights as they investigated the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e28f1f",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm surprised to see you all here.[p/] I thought what happened this morning was being considered an accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:075a49d",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: I should say the same to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a9662",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "...Was Rika right?[p/] Did a mage really murder her friend?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03727ca",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: My friend is an associate of the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b68dd6",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: She asked me to take a look at what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b7e2c",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: Right...[p/] I'd forgotten that Lloyd was charging Dracogen with criminal negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba6b9b",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Isn't that why [i]you're[/i] all here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad83c3",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: We're here because of another matter.[p/] Honestly,[p/] the death of Justin Waye seems fairly straightforward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feeee6",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: I'll be prosecuting the case, of course,[p/] but I doubt there's anything to dispute there."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f6aa2",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, if you're so confident,[p/] I guess you wouldn't mind answering my questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:041959e",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:013ad61",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: Why do I feel like you're about to make my job much more difficult?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfc1db",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Weren't you the one who said that the courts operate by having two balanced powers of opposition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0154570",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] So you [i]are[/i] going to defend him."
}

{
  "id": "line:079d71c",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "I wanted to say that I wasn't sure yet,[p/] but that would probably be a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fef90",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: ...Very well.[p/] If there's something here I'm not seeing,[p/] I'd appreciate your perspective."
}

{
  "id": "line:081e6ae",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Aria: I'll tell you what I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:03502c9",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it seems like I'd learned everything I could for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ffdd1",
  "node": "Factory1_Check",
  "text": "It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c56b0",
  "node": "DracDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's something strange going on with this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c8d65",
  "node": "DracDeduce",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] especially with this \"Mistweaving Phantom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a98e",
  "node": "DracDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's that,[p/] but there's something else that also stood out to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0899028",
  "node": "DracDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: After personally talking to Mr. Morrison and Stefanic Dracogen,[p/] one thing is clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e33487",
  "node": "DracDeduce1",
  "text": "No...[p/] Steelwind cited several reports of tensions between the Dracogen Trading Company and the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da31c8",
  "node": "DracDeduce1",
  "text": "But Mr. Morrison seemed surprised when I brought this up.[p/] So did Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eec24a",
  "node": "DracDeduce1",
  "text": "What was really going on here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:078ac1a",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]are[/i] no tensions between Dracogen and the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3148",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They had very little reason to lie to me,[p/] and even if they had,[p/] their statements wouldn't have matched so closely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77d53",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: But what about those reports Steelwind talked about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb7a0e",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: They didn't just say things were bad between them.[p/] They said they were \"hostile\" to each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c68c73",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think those reports might actually be related to the Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a893",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] How?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e723a2",
  "node": "DracDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know for what reason,[p/] but the Phantom isn't just looking to steal items of monetary value."
}

{
  "id": "line:0795474",
  "node": "DracDeduce3",
  "text": "No...[p/] The serial robber's actions seemed strange and sporadic,[p/] but two things stood out to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02afb59",
  "node": "DracDeduce3",
  "text": "They broke into Mr. Morrison's office to steal documents related to the unions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab3bf",
  "node": "DracDeduce3",
  "text": "And they broke into Dracogen's office without stealing his gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5b56",
  "node": "DracDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The serial robber seems to value records and documents,[p/] specifically those relating to the workers' unions and the Dracogen Trading company."
}

{
  "id": "line:079ea93",
  "node": "DracDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not concrete,[p/] but if we connect their actions to Steelwind's reports,[p/] something becomes suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f68d91",
  "node": "DracDeduce5",
  "text": "No...[p/] The robber was clearly doing more than just stealing valuables."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd87e5",
  "node": "DracDeduce5",
  "text": "They had another goal in mind,[p/] and it's related to those false reports."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b992da",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Whoever the Mistweaving Phantom is,[p/] the documents they stole are being used to file these false reports."
}

{
  "id": "line:044722e",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Celeste: Why would they do that, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07192c4",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It can't be for anything good.[p/] They're not just a common thug looking to make some easy money."
}

{
  "id": "line:0671de9",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're working towards something—[p/]something that's already affecting the political climate of Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0378e5a",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "I could feel my hand clenching into a fist.[p/] Whoever was filing these false reports was putting everyone in the city in danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4e0fe",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "If this continued,[p/] Lucio Steelwind might not leave when they find the shipment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0841042",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "He'd continue his bloodthirsty crusade here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ff8cc",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm going to find them,[p/] and when I do,[p/] I'm going to wring the truth out of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:02de590",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one person who can tell us more about what's happening in Aurinax:[p/] Lloyd von Sanctus himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1474",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Okay,[p/] but do you really think he's going to help you, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c42f0b",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We don't have a choice.[p/] We'll just have to see what we can get out of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a6e1f",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "And if [i]that[/i] didn't work,[p/] I'd just grab the information I needed out from his mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3594f",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Stefanic: The Duke's manor is in the upper district west of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a14c63",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...But I'd be careful if I were you.[p/] The duke of a Pillar Family is not someone to be trifled with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cba951",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's never stopped me before."
}

{
  "id": "line:034d7a9",
  "node": "DracDeduce6",
  "text": "Stefanic: Ha![p/] Clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ed4e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Houses"
}

{
  "id": "line:0761b8f",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: A row of houses line the edge of the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d20ee",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: When I was a kid,[p/] I always dreamed of saving up enough gold to buy my own house on the harbourfront..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e71947",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, you have a job as an attorney now.[p/] You can always move back here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e21ce",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] If possible,[p/] I never want to return to this city again."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e74a9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Ship"
}

{
  "id": "line:0089239",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a modest ship.[p/] It's probably used by local businesses to transport goods by sea."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0770",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't help but feel nostalgic seeing these ships."
}

{
  "id": "line:0654a11",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I used to travel by sea all the time when I was traveling the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:011fb5a",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: It was probably my favorite part."
}

{
  "id": "line:002a2d2",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] That [i]does[/i] sound pretty nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:001b301",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd like to try riding one, one day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a7dc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you sure?[p/] You get motion sick pretty easily."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd9c6",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Sailing on a ship might kill you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f31c6",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "She had a point there."
}

{
  "id": "line:029a1ac",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Crate"
}

{
  "id": "line:095bf99",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are several crates containing all kinds of goods."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d2f85",
  "node": "Harbor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: They must be the merchandise of the local businesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7a2ed",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Noah Morrison"
}

{
  "id": "line:04769cc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Robberies"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b693a6",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard there's been a string of robberies happening throughout town."
}

{
  "id": "line:05678ba",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They said that Dracogen's office was hit before the accident at the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b93e11",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Ah,[p/] the Phantom even hit the refinery?[p/] It's been a real headache, that one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea3d8e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Inquisition seems to suspect that one of the members of the union is this \"Mistweaving Phantom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d4bdc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: What?![p/][s/] That's a load of bollocks!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee655",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It made sense when I'd heard about the tensions between Dracogen and the unions,[p/] but if that's not true—"
}

{
  "id": "line:057a209",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: It can't have been someone from the unions![p/][s/] [i]Our[/i] offices have been hit the most!"
}

{
  "id": "line:059675c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] what could a thief possibly steal from a union office?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05eb205",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: That's the strangest thing...[p/] The Phantom broke in,[p/] but all they took were some documents."
}

{
  "id": "line:04512ea",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: We were wary of the Duke and the other nobles,[p/] so we had some advanced security systems installed at each of our offices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a338ee",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: But it didn't matter.[p/] This thief just slipped right past them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdfafd",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What kind of documents did they take?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0807201",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Things with lists of our members,[p/] our budget,[p/] and minutes of our meetings with employers in the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:07066f7",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, that definitely can't be for anything [i]good[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27992",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that implies that the Phantom is stealing more than just valuables."
}

{
  "id": "line:0165060",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are they trying to accomplish?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce0dab",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Robber's Profile"
}

{
  "id": "line:02efc21",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "What was going on?[p/] The more I learned about the Mistweaving Phantom,[p/] the more their motives became unclear."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad98d",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Morrison,[p/] Steelwind told us that several ships were robbed in port.[p/] Do you know which ones?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ec630",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Ah,[p/] give me a second.[p/] I've been making some notes on the shipping reports right here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdfd72",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow,[p/] they even hit von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f8d07",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: It's not on the report,[p/] but they even hit my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c328e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Who [i]is[/i] this guy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0386c98",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's difficult to see what the stolen items have in common."
}

{
  "id": "line:0645544",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you think they chose targets to intentionally mislead anyone trying to figure that out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb3c59",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Honestly,[p/] that's very likely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9b7a3",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever they are,[p/] they might be after more than just gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b8cc9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Mystery Ship"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e79cb",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are the items from the Aethergarde shipment marked as \"unknown\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0234978",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Oh, that.[p/] I think the ship was owned by a pretty high-profile noble.[p/] He said his name was Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0581ab0",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You met him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d550f9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Yeah,[p/] pretty nice bloke that one—[p/]nothing like old Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:02eb1c3",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: A lot of his retainers were causing a fuss when they realized that their ship had been robbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0968d47",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: It sounded like something really valuable was stolen from it."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a08d",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you think that's the imperial ship that Aria mentioned?"
}

{
  "id": "line:074e3bc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe...[p/] They seemed to be really secretive about what was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9478a",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It also looks like the Duke was supposed to receive whatever was on that ship."
}

{
  "id": "line:07128cc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: He might be able to tell us more about what was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9abe3",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you seriously think he'll talk to us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26566",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You kind of intentionally set him off the last time you saw him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00be2b5",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ugh.[p/] You're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b34955",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We might have more luck trying to find this \"Aster\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd8fe8",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: He didn't seem to pay any mind to what happened.[p/] He even paid me to show him around town."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7a13",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: We were actually at the refinery when the accident happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5acdf",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?![p/][s/] Why didn't you start with that, Mr. Morrison?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df67c5",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: Oh,[p/] you never asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cecace",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, did you see the accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0572819",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: No.[p/] My knee was acting up,[p/] so I was taking a sit-down in the yard outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f6f39",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: But I think [i]he[/i] saw something.[p/] He gave his statement to those knights when they showed up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af21da",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind never mentioned that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:038e4f0",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Is she hiding [i]another[/i] witness from us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088a6cc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Noah: That girl seemed really jumpy around him, too.[p/] She could barely hold a conversation with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c2c7",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, wow...[p/] I've never seen her like that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:028a39c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Talk",
  "text": "Whoever this \"Aster\" was,[p/] it sounded like I'd need to have a talk with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6ebb3",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad to see you're doing okay, Mr. Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d0b83",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: Things have really turned around since you were last here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1d0f6",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a little difficult to take in sometimes.[p/] So much has changed..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8f697",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: I know it's a little tough to trust sometimes,[p/] but change can be good."
}

{
  "id": "line:043a9fc",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: It's all really new,[p/] but I feel like the city's in good hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adea66",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's good to hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dda92",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: You're...[p/] okay, aren't you?[p/] Things weren't exactly—[p/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0103839",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "He was really trying to choose his next words carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:021c971",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm okay.[p/] Apparently,[p/] everyone's seen as much in the papers lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b1e3e",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: Right...[p/] I guess you're a defense attorney who saves mages. [h=\"Is he doing this because of|what happened to his mum?\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:028aa03",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9d9af",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: I know all that happened a long time ago,[p/] but it's okay if you're still not okay, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041d905",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "It sounded like he was clumsily stumbling around his words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a16ca3",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: You're probably all settled down in the capital,[p/] but I hear there are some support groups that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:014c620",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm okay.[p/] Thank you, Mr. Morrison."
}

{
  "id": "line:0678073",
  "node": "NoahNoahConv",
  "text": "Noah: R-[p/][s/]Right, of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e87426",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that you're leading one of the workers' unions in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:012e37a",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: Ah,[p/] so you heard about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb87b",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] The workers' unions were Stefanic Dracogen's idea?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082bfb9",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: Yeah,[p/] I was just as confused as you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:084ed7f",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: I had no idea what he was trying to do,[p/] but I wasn't going to look that gift horse in the mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c718a",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must be bittersweet considering how hostile things have gotten between you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0528f89",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c1d90",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard about it from the prosecutor.[p/] I know about the tensions between the unions and Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f57f1",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: This again?[p/] The knights said something like that, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea6488",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: But things have never been better between Stefanic and us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf73e3",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The prosecutor said they received several reports of hostility between you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d8e32",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: Well, this is the first [i]I'm[/i] hearing of this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0060e27",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "He seemed sincerely confused.[p/] What was going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf713",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: Who sent these \"reports\" anyway?[p/] Surely not any of the union members."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9b4da",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure...[p/] But from what she said,[p/] these reports came from numerous sources."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7d839",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: The prosecutor's a Steelwind, ain't she?[p/] Are you sure you can really trust what she says?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0077694",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Celeste: She's not the type of person who'd lie about something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b83235",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: Hm...[p/] If you say so."
}

{
  "id": "line:08601e7",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Were all those reports wrong,[p/] or was Mr. Morrison lying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0047b00",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: The more I hear about that story,[p/] the less it makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be0822",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: I talked to the man who inspected that guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3111b",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "Noah: He said that it was only dented.[p/] It should've never broken like they keep saying it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc676",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "So was Rika right, then?[p/] Did someone break that guardrail apart using magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0135bd4",
  "node": "NoahUnionConv",
  "text": "But if that were true,[p/] why weren't there any magical traces there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08da787",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: What's this?[p/] Some kind of amulet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0154f14",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I really can't believe you're some bigshot attorney now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de0295",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I mean, look at you.[p/] I never imagined I'd ever see you wearing a suit."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5bb9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Frey would be very proud of you, my boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1647c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I hope so."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f4ea0",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I'm glad you're safe.[p/] We assumed the worst after we heard you went wandering off into the woods."
}

{
  "id": "line:015c021",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I needed to talk to my mother's attorney.[p/] I thought I could [i]walk[/i] to Ratholme to see her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4ee93",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: [i]No one[/i] could make that trip on foot,[p/] much less a small boy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf5307",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] a passing merchant picked me up.[p/] I got really lucky."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f113d",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: ...I'm just glad you didn't get mauled by a wild animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0340918",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "It came pretty close a few times,[p/] but the Eye of Horus really helped me in that regard."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b5add",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: So,[p/] who's this?[p/] Is she your ladyfriend?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1bd02",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] She's my bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:070e047",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Bodyguard...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03764e9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I know my looks imply a far more delicate occupation."
}

{
  "id": "line:07baa5a",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It makes more sense when you've seen what she can do to a pile of logs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb1bd1",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Those knights were taking forever.[p/] How do you make it into the Inquisition and not know how to chop firewood?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bb216",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] you ripped those logs apart with your bare hands.[p/] It was terrifying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe29c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Sometimes it's good to remind everyone what I'm able to do.[p/] It keeps you all in line."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9946a",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you met the Duke of Commerce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4f8c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: ...Only because of how many of his shipments are being robbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4e3e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I don't know what he expects me to do.[p/] It's [i]his[/i] armed guard that are being slipped past."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df4e55",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know the Mistweaving Phantom is good at what they do,[p/] but how are they slipping past that much security?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3f926",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I have no idea.[p/] The streets are definitely a lot less safe with them out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a301",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Have you had a chance to go to Mosourika's café?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04636a9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes, actually.[p/] That's how we ran into her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5ca6",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: She's always making pastries, that girl.[p/] I'm glad she's able to live off of it now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5bcdd",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does she still make you those pastries from when we were kids?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f745f7",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Ah,[p/] the ones she made shaped like a fish?[p/] She still brings those to me every week."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae1afa",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know anything about the blockade the Kingsguard have set up around the city?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004fc37",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: ...All I know is a pretty important imperial ship got robbed this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:019000b",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I don't know what they stole,[p/] but it's even got the Grand General in a huff."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f04e05",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you have any ideas who this Mistweaving Phantom might be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07014fc",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: No idea..."
}

{
  "id": "line:004c646",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: There are so many rumors about them,[p/] and the people have all kinds of theories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0288531",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: I think there's even a rumor that it's me.[p/] Can you imagine?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d86557",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, you [i]are[/i] the harbormaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:084291d",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Oh, not [i]you[/i] too."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ec975",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Player: ShipRep"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a92023",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: This shipping report lists a lot of imports from the other nations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc4b1f",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Yeah, Aurinax is situated perfectly to receive shipments from Arcarus,[p/] Symett,[p/] [i]and[/i] the Eastern Kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:03230d3",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Organizations from all over Wyverngarde receive foreign shipments here."
}

{
  "id": "line:064618c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Of course,[p/] with how Wyverngarde is,[p/] the knights check every ship that comes into harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:041f571",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell us about this, Morrison?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f90e82",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: Ah...[p/] Sorry.[p/] I don't know much about those sorts of things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2ae9",
  "node": "Harbor1_Present",
  "text": "Noah: You'd better ask someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0246e2b",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "It had been a long time since I'd been to the Aurinax harbor,[p/] but the ocean breeze and the smell of seawater were unmistakable."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d0c2c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "The city had clearly changed a lot over the years,[p/] but at least one thing had stayed the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:022163e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "I remembered when I'd sit by the docks,[p/] bored out of my mind,[p/] while my mother read people's fortunes on the boardwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0440839",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "I hated it.[p/] I never had anything to do or anyone to play with."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b557a",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "...I would give anything to get those days back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0e4c8",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c63f14",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] We should get going."
}

{
  "id": "line:08eb7ea",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you sure?[p/] We can stay here a bit longer if you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:004f661",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "It sounded tempting,[p/] but I knew it wouldn't be long before I started remembering everything else that had happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:039545f",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Sometimes it's good to take a rest,[p/] and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cc320",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] I'm [i]fine[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfb807",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "The tone of my voice turned a lot sharper than I'd meant for it to."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1a67",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:013a208",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry...[p/] I didn't mean to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06be410",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]It's okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e64de",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't worry about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf8d05",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: ...I'd heard from Rika,[p/] but I still can't believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccdc40",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: It really is you, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b6410",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Mr. Morrison?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bcd9f",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: ...It's good to see you, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0635de4",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: Look how much you've grown!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0910f38",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: H-[p/][s/]Hi..."
}

{
  "id": "line:034ea35",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "I drew in a sharp breath.[p/] The guilt over how I'd left the city was clawing at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b2520",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry I never kept in touch."
}

{
  "id": "line:07084e0",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: ...I'm just glad that you're safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad903",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: Some of the lads were sure you'd died in the woods."
}

{
  "id": "line:075722e",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: Color us surprised when we saw you in the newspaper taking on some noble in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1d51c",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Actually,[p/] since I have you here,[p/] I'm investigating the death of Justin Waye."
}

{
  "id": "line:022ab2b",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: Oh, you heard about that.[p/] It's a terrible thing that happened to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:023d5d3",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can I ask you some questions about the Dracogen Trading Company?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b55086",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "Noah: Of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e71e8",
  "node": "Harbor1_Check",
  "text": "I think I actually learned a lot more than I thought I would."
}

{
  "id": "line:068151b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: Hmph...[p/] Why not just enter and claim the territory for yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052ea16",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That would be a crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f693d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] so you're a coward then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9d5e7",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Why was I trying to explain this to a cat?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f10f7",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: I'd recommend against trying to scavenge these ships for supplies."
}

{
  "id": "line:04765fc",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: If they leave while you're still on them,[p/] you'll find yourself stranded on the sea,[p/] surrounded by savages."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f116e",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't think I'd ever make a mistake like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:045fcae",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] I do love going through these containers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c82475",
  "node": "Harbor2_Examine",
  "text": "Cat: Sometimes I find something quite delectable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e69160",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Why were you at the refinery?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d40e3",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay...[p/] Let's start from the top."
}

{
  "id": "line:049cd04",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why were you at the refinery yesterday morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0935ef3",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] that building with all of those metal constructs?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05821f7",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: I was keeping watch over that boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6f11d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: I needed to make sure he completed his task."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38358",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did you know what his \"task\" was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0607c77",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: Because I gave it to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace2cd",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: I gave him the task to rob those documents from Stefanic Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24b35",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...B-[p/][s/]but—[p/][s/] I—[p/][s/] WHAT?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0157e8b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "I just incoherently stammered for a while before clapping my hands together to stop myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:087729a",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "I took another long, deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1461f",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would a [i]cat[/i] want something as worthless as a few documents?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e04db",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: \"Worthless\"?[p/][s/] I think we both know those documents are quite valuable in the proper hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:089f539",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: I told him he could take the old fool's gold as well,[p/] but he left it for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3f405",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Oh my god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0277b10",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: It's such a shame what happened to the boy,[p/] but he brought that onto himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:06777ea",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: If he had never disobeyed me,[p/] he would still be among the living."
}

{
  "id": "line:079f229",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "...I felt that migraine returning."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bfad3",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The True Killer At Last"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1f7b7",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you saying that [i]you're[/i] the one who murdered Justin Waye?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed4f89",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: Well, it was [i]my[/i] device that pushed him from that platform."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d8067",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What kind of device was it?[p/] What did it do exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095d93d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: ...It allowed him to move from one location to another."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3bf24",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: They were quite instrumental to the jobs he was completing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e17372",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Aster: There was a flash of magical light centered on his position.[p/] It blew apart the guardrail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af256a",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "This \"device\" must have been some kind of artficery machine."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bd86e",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "That at least explained how she was casting magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cebf26",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: After he was disposed of,[p/] I had to complete the job myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13104",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: Luckily,[p/] the boy already unlocked—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0464888",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f64ddb",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "Cat: Sorry, I have to take this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fff8b0",
  "node": "Harbor2_Talk",
  "text": "She didn't respond.[p/] She simply looked up at the sky, distracted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c714ad",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: What's this?[p/] Some kind of trinket?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0590901",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Her body suddenly froze.[p/] She was staring at the small ray of sun being reflected from my Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c92b8d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: So you seek to torment me again, you luminous orb!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041439b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "She immediately pounced where the light hit the ground and tried to paw at the circle of light.[p/] Her tiny paws were trying to grasp what wasn't there."
}

{
  "id": "line:089926b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Curse your ethereal form![p/][s/] I will find a way to slay you, you spectre!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bff362",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "She darted from spot to spot as I slowly angled my Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edcb4f",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...This is kind of fun."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd00e0",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion|Lloyd"
}

{
  "id": "line:05eb3de",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: I've only met one other human that reminds me of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d258be",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: The world is quite a curious place."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e819d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Was she talking about someone who looked like me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060ac8b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "...Did this cat meet my mother before she died?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba968c",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: There are two types of creatures in this world:[p/] those who eat and those who are eaten."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b492b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: I can't believe that predator hasn't slain you yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c7d7b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's very nice once you get to know her."
}

{
  "id": "line:025de8b",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: ...Well,[p/] she does know to revere me.[p/] I'll give her that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c248b9",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Wyatt"
}

{
  "id": "line:01331f8",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] I remember this round one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f20fe6",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: I once caught him spying on me while I was running my errands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0a92f",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What kind of errands were you on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f86d6f",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: ...Important business that is none of your concern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0110a5f",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] my device.[p/] How did it fall into [i]your[/i] hands?"
}

{
  "id": "line:087c47e",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Nevertheless,[p/] I appreciate you returning this to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b382",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is just a picture.[p/] The Inquisition probably took the real ring back to their barracks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8b373",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Hmph...[p/] Thieving rats."
}

{
  "id": "line:047bc53",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: ...Give that to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:093a75d",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know you'd like a toy,[p/] but this is important evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d425f1",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: ...I suppose I'll allow it this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0278260",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: It's not as if it's of any use to me in that state."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2e627",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Player: Phantom|Justin|Autopsy"
}

{
  "id": "line:087848a",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: That boy—[p/]his actions perplexed me to the very end."
}

{
  "id": "line:064e626",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: He was quite the thief.[p/] I might even say he was more dextrous than [i]me[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:088eeb6",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: It's a shame he couldn't follow such simple instructions."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c3ccc",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Player: HousePic"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c46d2",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Ah,[p/] it seems you've found my liar."
}

{
  "id": "line:023cbc1",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's technically [i]my[/i] house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a823",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "Cat: Really?[p/][s/] I haven't seen anyone enter that place for years."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d56d1",
  "node": "Harbor2_Present",
  "text": "She didn't seem that interested in what I was showing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9da2b",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: I'm sorry, Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:093b269",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: There was so much that I wanted to tell you—[p/]so much that I wanted to show you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0142899",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: But I'm afraid I was never meant to walk this path with you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:045e7d9",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: This world is bleak,[p/] merciless,[p/] and unforgiving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9cb0c",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: But don't let it extinguish the flickering flame I can see within you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d06f4f",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: Use my eyes.[p/] Peer beyond the Divine Gate just as I once did."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d8559",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frey: Use it to build your own path to happiness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecc6b7",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: Preposterous![p/][s/] Completely and [i]utterly[/i] preposterous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a281db",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is something wrong, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041c46f",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: You [i]filthy[/i] rat![p/][s/] You cheated, didn't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea73e",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's it, isn't it?![p/][s/] You're just a cheat—[p/][s/]a cheat and a charlatan!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b76185",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have any evidence to prove that claim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8212e",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: I mastered chess before you could [i]crawl[/i] out of whatever [i]rat-hole[/i] you were born in!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97f1c",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: Do you honestly expect anyone to believe that [i]you[/i][p/] could defeat [i]me[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092dee9",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Tyrion: Honestly,[p/] I'm just as disappointed as you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0073fee",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Tyrion: I expected more from a Duke,[p/] but I guess all the gold in the world can't buy you a modicum of skill."
}

{
  "id": "line:01db635",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: You little upstart![p/][s/] I'll—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5448c",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Nobleman: [i]*Ahem*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0c80",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Von Sanctus's attendant silently tilted his head toward the spectators of the tournament."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe32cc",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "The crowd had fallen silent,[p/] save for a few aristocrats who were muttering among themselves.[p/] Some were even chuckling at the spectacle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6ff3d",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Absolutely preposterous."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dc663",
  "node": "Chess",
  "text": "He repeated it like a prayer as he stomped away from the tournament grounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0039415",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] [i]That[/i] was...[p/] something."
}

{
  "id": "line:055b066",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Did you have to be such a sore winner?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0025a75",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Come on.[p/] That was hilarious."
}

{
  "id": "line:038597f",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Embarrassing nobles like him is half of the fun of these tournaments."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9a1bf",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Where's this confidence when you're in the courtroom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b601e7",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Steelwind is far less of a pushover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef6637",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hm...[p/] I wonder if [i]she[/i] plays chess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe67c3",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Now [i]there[/i] was an interesting thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd6c8",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm going to challenge her next time we go out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73a2c",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You two have really been spending a lot of time together lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4dad0",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?[p/] Are you jealous?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093b38e",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just never expected you to get along so well with a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dea52",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: I mean,[p/] you've talked to her.[p/] She's not like most of those stuck-up heiresses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0630118",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: She really takes her job seriously—[p/]maybe even more than you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a48ada",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'd just be careful around her.[p/] You've seen what the papers have been saying about her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a2d40",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] she's [i]nothing[/i] like her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:05df146",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't say things like that when she's around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3380d",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Does he ever come up when you talk to each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076a097",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Nope,[p/] and you better not bring him up the next time we see her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03abba9",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "She seemed oddly protective of the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:030644b",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "...It was probably fine.[p/] Despite our differences,[p/] Steelwind was oddly fair when we were in the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:045c01b",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste spent most of her time protecting me,[p/] so I was glad she had someone she could spend her days off with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0963ee8",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Anyways,[p/] we should celebrate!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d18d31",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: He was a pushover,[p/] but you just beat a [i]duke[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c02cd",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you want to head to that restaurant in Ratholme?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072bdaf",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: What are you talking about?[p/] There are plenty of places here we haven't tried before."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8bd2",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "I only returned to Aurinax for the chance to finally defeat the head of a Pillar Family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f1ee",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "I really wanted to leave,[p/] especially before anyone in town recognized me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd8dda",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you remember that café we passed on the way to the tournament grounds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04626c1",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Celeste: We should grab some lunch there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de99df",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "I wanted to object,[p/] but she had this way of making it impossible to say \"no\" to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0865793",
  "node": "Chess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Alright,[p/] I guess there's no harm in staying a little longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c13c8",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": ":We traced our steps back to the café.[p/] I looked at the sign hanging above it: [i]Darkk Roasts and Light Magic[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0901e54",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "As we entered,[p/] we were struck by the powerful aroma of freshly baked pastries and coffee."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be7832",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "The scent of bread and butter swirled around me,[p/] slowly washing away my reluctance to come here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0438d64",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: So…[p/] You dare to enter the domain of the Alabastor Siren."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1718d",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: Whether you were seeking glory or oblivion,[p/] it's found you all the same!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6cd90",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: You stand before Mosourika Tudor:[p/][s/] the Ashen Lord of Aurinax!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78372",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "My childhood friend appeared before us,[p/] her posture firm and over-the-top as always."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd607f",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika was much older than when I'd last seen her,[p/] but I could recognize that theatrical cadence anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a41a18",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "She clearly hadn't lost her flair for the dramatic.[p/] Her cloak somehow billowed with every exaggerated pose she snapped to."
}

{
  "id": "line:043eda6",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: I'll have you know that my confections are not for the faint of—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76d11",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "She froze up.[p/] She recognized me immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f286b5",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0246da0",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "I winced as I rubbed the back of my neck."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fddd1",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: I knew it![p/][s/] It [i]is[/i] you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:062b514",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Mosourika: Do you have any idea how worried we've all been?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09388f4",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do you two know each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0575346",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:007d473",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mosourika,[p/] this is my bodyguard:[p/] Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0879234",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste,[p/] this is Mosourika.[p/] We kind of grew up together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4394",
  "node": "CafeIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's actually a commoner mage like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d6217",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Celeste: You used to live here?![p/] But you were in such a rush to leave!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf717e",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...You came here to eat, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030cd44",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Let me bring you some of our best dishes,[p/] on the house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc56b2",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No.[p/] We couldn't possibly—"
}

{
  "id": "line:086e410",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Don't be like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c99fe",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: It's been years since I've seen you,[p/] and you [i]know[/i] how good my cooking is."
}

{
  "id": "line:02875d4",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay,[p/] but only for a little bit."
}

{
  "id": "line:00048ed",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Also,[p/] a bit of a warning,[p/] Celeste is kind of a glutton.[p/] Her stomach is basically bottomless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1136b",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e640f0",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: Oh,[p/] I'll accept [i]that[/i] challenge."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d5bfa",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Rika set a table for the three of us before calling over a waiter."
}

{
  "id": "line:021d68a",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "I ordered the Eggs Benedict,[p/] and Rika ordered the French toast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2e2c3",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "...Celeste ordered the omelette,[p/] ham skillet,[p/] shaved steak,[p/] breakfast wrap.[p/] a stack of pancakes,[p/] a stack of waffles,[p/] a chocolate crepe—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e612a7",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "—and the avocado toast,[p/] because she wanted something light."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac7fb9",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am so sorry, Rika.[p/] I'll pay for her food."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec6a7d",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: H-[p/][s/]Ha![p/][s/] This is nothing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1d25",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: My café has dealt with far greater foes than this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d5b29",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Celeste: Can I also get the eggs benedict and the french toast?[p/] Their food smells great."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c4a32",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll pay for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:001d274",
  "node": "CafeIntro2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aed1d6",
  "node": "CatDeduce0",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] As articulate as she was,[p/] her understanding was still limited."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df067b",
  "node": "CatDeduce0",
  "text": "I would need to work out what she really meant on my own."
}

{
  "id": "line:047952d",
  "node": "CatDeduce0",
  "text": "It let him \"move around from one location to another\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9d6be",
  "node": "CatDeduce1",
  "text": "No...[p/] Queen said that the device helped him to move from one location to another."
}

{
  "id": "line:04268f9",
  "node": "CatDeduce1",
  "text": "They were also apparently instrumental to the other robberies that Justin has been committing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a63a94",
  "node": "CatDeduce2",
  "text": "This device had been allowing Justin to teleport![p/][s/] No wonder he'd been so elusive."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e524e",
  "node": "CatDeduce2",
  "text": "The security systems that he bypassed were designed to keep mages from teleporting in,[p/] but they didn't stop people from teleporting out."
}

{
  "id": "line:05707aa",
  "node": "CatDeduce2",
  "text": "He must have used his skills as the Mistweaver Phantom to break in.[p/] He then used this device to make an instantaneous getaway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca13ff",
  "node": "CatDeduce2",
  "text": "...But if I wanted to use this in court,[p/] I would need physical evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eb1b0",
  "node": "CatDeduce2",
  "text": "There had to be something that I could identify as the device."
}

{
  "id": "line:012c01f",
  "node": "CatDeduce3",
  "text": "No...[p/] Justin was supposedly using this device during his robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51ada",
  "node": "CatDeduce3",
  "text": "For whatever reason,[p/] he didn't go through with robbing Dracogen's office."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fe980",
  "node": "CatDeduce3",
  "text": "But he wouldn't have entered the refinery unless he was initially planning to rob it."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ae973",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "It was the ring![p/][s/] Magical items were more durable and resistant to magical effects!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a861b",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Justin must have been wearing it when he fell into the vat..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba443",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "It dissolved his body,[p/] but it couldn't dissolve the magical ring he was wearing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:043a4b8",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "But if he was wearing it when he died,[p/] that could only mean one thing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04659a5",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You didn't kill Justin Waye, did you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c45c4",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Cat: No...[p/] When did I ever say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01711a5",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "...She spoke so articulately that I almost forgot."
}

{
  "id": "line:009be3f",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Animals tended to be extremely literal compared to humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cfb0d",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that Justin died because he disobeyed you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca26c",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: What exactly did he do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aad38c",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Cat: He didn't disappear like he usually did. Instead,[p/] there was an explosion of energy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee86a",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would he do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d117e4",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Cat: I have no idea.[p/] The results speak to how foolish that was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc0184",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Regardless of why,[p/] that must have been the magical effect that Rika and the Crown Prince saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0109fa7",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "They didn't see him getting blasted with a spell.[p/] They saw him cast a spell on himself using his ring."
}

{
  "id": "line:051c6c8",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "...But how would that destroy the guardrail?[p/] Did the ring malfunction and create a small explosion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084c185",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Something like that should have still left traces of magic,[p/] and there weren't any on the catwalk."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fbb2b",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "I would need to know exactly what kind of magic the ring could cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f30fe6",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "Only the Inquisition had access to mages who could analyze it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01903a6",
  "node": "CatDeduce4",
  "text": "I would be showing my hand to Steelwind,[p/] but I didn't have a choice if I wanted to use this in court."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a0e59",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you for answering my questions, Queen,[p/] but I have one last question."
}

{
  "id": "line:062c11d",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Who are you [i]really[/i] working for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f3946",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: ...What are you on about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04347fa",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: [i]I[/i] am the brains of this operation."
}

{
  "id": "line:01324d9",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you expect me to believe that [i]you're[/i] behind these false reports of insurrection?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0009868",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: ...I don't concern myself with the minutia of my underlings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70bf3",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: ...All [i]you[/i] need to know is that I'll be standing at the top of this city by the end of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:033dfbc",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "I knew it...[p/] She may not have been able to lie,[p/] but she was grossly misunderstanding her role in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c764de",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But someone trained you, didn't they?[p/] You knew what the objective was."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c80fd",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: \"Trained\"?[p/] I'm insulted.[p/] I was [i]debriefed[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:06433b1",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: It's quite strange, really.[p/] He spoke to me in the same way that you are now."
}

{
  "id": "line:010a5ef",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: In any case,[p/] it seems I must be going now.[p/] He seems quite anxious about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be2dbb",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0687831",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "I tried to grab her,[p/] but she gracefully leapt over me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c0b7",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "She pivoted off my back before landing softly on the bench behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0308387",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Cat: Ha![p/][s/] Try again in ten years, boy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6aa5",
  "node": "CatDeduce5",
  "text": "Laughing triumphantly,[p/] she scurried away into the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8f0a",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Oh, come on![p/][s/] I told you not to scare her off!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d3451",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Celeste arrived back,[p/] wheeling a ten-foot-long tuna in a wheelbarrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f57fe2",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "I blinked at it for a moment before looking back at the city.[p/] There were more important things to focus on right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb6707",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Whoever was behind this had been speaking to that cat,[p/] and they were using an ability similar to mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:022e858",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Was there someone else in Aurinax who could use the Eye of Horus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e929a",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "...If only I'd caught her before she ran.[p/] I might've been able to get more information out of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b2b94",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d99cc",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "There was no helping it.[p/] I'd just need to work with the only lead I had."
}

{
  "id": "line:01648d6",
  "node": "CatDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We need to talk to Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee670c",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f957",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: Can someone tell me why the mage girl is roasting a giant fish outside?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0605955",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Aria: Ignore that, Orym.[p/] What did the diviners say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0102e54",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: Turns out the kid was right.[p/] That ring's artificery,[p/] and it's pretty sophisticated too."
}

{
  "id": "line:077d98d",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: Its functions got scrambled by the chemicals in that vat,[p/] but we were able to figure out that it triggers two spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0118274",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Two[/i] spells?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0959769",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] one spell teleports the caster,[p/] the other summons a target to their location."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9965f",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: It's kind of weird, honestly.[p/] Artificery fitted into a ring usually only has one function."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e39888",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d0c7d",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Aria: Unlike spells cast by a mage,[p/] artificery can't intuitively choose which spell to cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f69965",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about our Runestones?[p/] They project a visual interface for us to use."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c62a5",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Aria: Yes,[p] but a system as sophisticated as that wouldn't fit in a ring like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:019095a",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] Justin must have been using the ring to teleport away from his crimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e36eae",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "But what was the function of the second spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee8f8",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know what target the summoning spell is linked to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054415e",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: No idea.[p/] It wasn't physically damaged,[p/] but the magic's too disrupted."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c135c",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: It's been fading since the accident, too.[p/] We're lucky we could even identify the spells at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c071f5",
  "node": "Inves2End",
  "text": "Orym: If the kid had figured this out a day later,[p/] it might've been too late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd3c8",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: ...Which raises the question as to [i]how[/i] you figured this out."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0610",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] it was [i]my[/i] resources that allowed you to analyze the ring in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0543dfd",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: I believe I deserve to know why."
}

{
  "id": "line:0025085",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Fair point,[p/] but I'll only tell you on one condition."
}

{
  "id": "line:00680dc",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't want Mosourika Tudor to be implicated in [i]any[/i] of the crimes of the Mistweaving Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbcf54",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: ...Fine,[p/] but only if [i]she[/i] isn't the Phantom herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f08cf8",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's not.[p/] It was Justin Waye."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea752",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Orym: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fd8c4",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: ...How certain are you of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a6ac",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm fairly sure.[p/] It follows everything I've learned so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f81c66",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "The prosecutor cursed under her breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d58b0d",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Aria: ...That only means the location of the Crown Prince's cargo has been lost with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4f91",
  "node": "Inves2End2",
  "text": "Orym: Oh, speak of the devil."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a4e7",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "From behind Steelwind,[p/] the Crown Prince began approaching us eagerly,[p/] but he paused when he noticed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:072e665",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay...[p/] I know it's [i]me[/i], but I can't eat this much fish by—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0670b88",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c52a8",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Celeste froze as she saw the Crown Prince approaching Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5a24",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "The Crown Prince had told us earlier how much Steelwind hated him..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0015299",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "The prosecutor raised an eyebrow at all of us.[p/] She probably saw the looks on our faces."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0e85",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Aria: ...What are you all looking at?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4975c",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "She slowly turned her head before completely whipping around at the sight of the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:084dfa9",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Aria: Y-[p/][s/]Y[p/][s/]-Y[p/][s/]-Y[p/][s/]-Your Highness?! [h=\"Why is he here?!\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:046d140",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Aster: The last thing I want to do do is disturb you during your work,[p/] but I wanted to see you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0902c65",
  "node": "Inves2End3",
  "text": "Aria: Oh?![p/][s/] Okay!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79dd9",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "I looked over to the Commander.[p/] He looked like he wanted to pull out a bag of popcorn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc7687",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aster: I wanted to apologize to you in person."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f858",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aster: I can't believe they're pulling you into this nonsense with the arcane crystals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3ff60",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aria: N-[p/][s/]No,[p/] it's—[p/][s/] it's my duty as your queen—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a513c",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aria: Sorry, I meant \"wife\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df1837",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aria: \"Fiancée\"—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d27d6",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, boy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:018750e",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aster: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I can't believe they're stirring up so much trouble over this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0463f95",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Aster: How difficult is it to find one giant chest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041f347",
  "node": "Inves2End4",
  "text": "Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c1b58",
  "node": "Inves2End4a",
  "text": "HousePic"
}

{
  "id": "line:07158b0",
  "node": "Inves2End4a",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Crown Prince mentioned that the stolen cargo was contained in a \"giant chest\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:035b31f",
  "node": "Inves2End4a",
  "text": "Hadn't I seen something like that somewhere?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a50a70",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The giant chest you mentioned didn't look like this, did it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08aef0c",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: Hm...[p/] No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3bfc3",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: It was definitely made from a different material,[p/] and it wasn't nearly so damaged."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c65d1",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: ...Although,[p/] this chest [i]is[/i] suspiciously large.[p/] Do you know what was inside it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbad44",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] It was too dented.[p/] We couldn't open it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210e57",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: Then it might be worth looking into."
}

{
  "id": "line:0721313",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There's an old abandoned house near the forests along the ocean side."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cf190",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll find it there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a622f5",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aria: Orym![p/][s/] Since you clearly have so much time to stand around gawking,[p/] you'll be personally responsible for looking into this suspicious container!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c6325",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Orym: Aaaaaaaaand, she's back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2964f",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aria: ...What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067e739",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Orym: Nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac0c3",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: Thank you so much, Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:045636f",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aster: I already know you're busy with von Sanctus's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0293c6c",
  "node": "Inves2End4b",
  "text": "Aria: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] well.[p/] The stolen shipment [i]is[/i] related to the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:02347cd",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02951d6",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: Oh—[p/][s/] Uh—[p/][s/] I meant—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f78420",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb7f45",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "The Crown Prince stepped closer to her,[p/] a concerned look on his face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0765477",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: ...I-[p/][s/]Is it just me,[p/] or is it [i]absurdly[/i] hot in here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034317b",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: Really?[p/] I don't feel anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0141670",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: Although,[p/] your face is looking a little flushed right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:046aef9",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: Oh, Scaled Lord, no..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bd964",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: I-[p/][s/]It's fine, really!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6556f",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aster: You still look as beautiful as always!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019042e",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: Ahhhhhhhhhhhh... [h=\"dsfhkjsadlkfsjfd|lksghdlkjsahfjsa\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0586337",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: I'm going to get some—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1da83",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26551",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Water?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030f31e",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "Aria: Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:05af030",
  "node": "Inves2End4c",
  "text": "The stonewall that was the prosecutor nearly walked into a pole before scurrying away to a nearby washroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e74d9",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "As she left,[p/] the Crown Prince exhaled."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0173",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry you two had to see that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d60415",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Aster: It's as I said before.[p/] She absolutely detests me."
}

{
  "id": "line:049a84f",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Aster: You saw it, didn't you?[p/] She could barely look me in the eye..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e11fe5",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Oh my god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94e68",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Aster: I suppose you missed it.[p/] She does tend to be subtle about her feelings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0810c98",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "...As subtle as a brick to the face."
}

{
  "id": "line:025c2e8",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] I had clear proof that the guardrail broke because of Justin's actions,[p/] not Dracogen's negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1951",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "...But that somehow felt unsatisfying in a way.[p/] I still never found out who Queen was working with."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aac48",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "He felt like such a massive piece of the puzzle.[p/] It may have just been my arrogance,[p/] but I never imagined I wouldn't catch him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365392",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "I could just investigate him after the trial was done,[p/] but my resources would be limited as an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9533",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "...Was this really okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16910",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e26a02",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0745774",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm just checking in."
}

{
  "id": "line:037c466",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You look [i]really[/i] tired."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef38a2",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:022f7c8",
  "node": "Inves2End5",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't apologize.[p/] You've been running yourself ragged since we got up."
}

{
  "id": "line:018a170",
  "node": "Inves2End6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess it [i]is[/i] getting late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0149737",
  "node": "Inves2End6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's head back to the room for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0525e8a",
  "node": "Inves2End6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can work through everything we've learned there."
}

{
  "id": "line:00181a4",
  "node": "Inves2End6b",
  "text": "We arrived back at the tavern room.[p/] The lobby was still packed with people waiting for the blockade to end."
}

{
  "id": "line:090f400",
  "node": "Inves2End6b",
  "text": "Despite myself,[p/] the soft mattress of the bed was just too appealing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0444013",
  "node": "Inves2End6b",
  "text": "I could probably work through all of this while lying down."
}

{
  "id": "line:007e65e",
  "node": "Inves2End6b",
  "text": "The soft linens felt like a cloud trying to engulf me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e61061",
  "node": "Inves2End6b",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] I needed to focus.[p/] I couldn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8ab20",
  "node": "Inves2End7",
  "text": "I fell asleep immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03890",
  "node": "Inves2End8",
  "text": "Orym: Come on![p/][s/] Put your backs into it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea8c3e",
  "node": "Inves2End8",
  "text": "Knight: It's stuck pretty tight, Sir.[p/] We might need a mage to transmute it open."
}

{
  "id": "line:0752fd6",
  "node": "Inves2End8",
  "text": "Orym: Bah![p/][s/] Why use magic when some elbow grease will do the trick?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02172f4",
  "node": "Inves2End8",
  "text": "Orym: Come on![p/][s/] Open, you piece of junk!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0742176",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Orym: Ha![p/][s/] Didn't I tell you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece5c5",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Orym: All it took was a little—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f5f5a",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Knight: Boss?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df941c",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Orym: ...We need to get out of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:04227e7",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Knight: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060036d",
  "node": "Inves2End9",
  "text": "Orym: Everyone,[p/] get out![p/][s/] We need to get as far away from this thing as possible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0767788",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: I'm here.[p/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095bc5c",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: The kid was right.[p/] The energy cells were in there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0583b26",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: ...But someone rigged another device to it.[p/] It could be a bomb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddc2dd",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: I'm going to take a look at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab19c6",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: Are you crazy?![p/][s/] I just told you it could be a bomb!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea7054",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: If it's allowed to detonate,[p/] we'll lose any evidence pointing to who did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3eb6d",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: Next time,[p/] we might not be so fortunate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0209ed0",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: Then I'll go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2a1e1",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: ...Commander, you can't possibly expect me to—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6d89",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: Hey, I'm just looking out for myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01851ad",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: There's a long list of people who'd have my head if I let the future queen get blown up."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c164f",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: We'll go together then."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ffd3a",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: What?![p/][s/] I just said—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca1dd5",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: With all due respect, Commander,[p/] you're not great with artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0451015",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: With the two of us there,[p/] we'll stand a better chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93987",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Aria: A compromise is an agreement where neither party is pleased."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e33e06",
  "node": "Inves2End10",
  "text": "Orym: Ugh...[p/] Have it your way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be6381",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "Another nightmare overtook my sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d17c8",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "I clutched the note tightly in my hands as I read it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8650c",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her \"eyes\"...?[p/] I...[p/][s/] I don't understand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fa485",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "...It didn't matter.[p/] All I had to do was stop the execution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0cfe0",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "If I could just distract the knights long enough,[p/] I could save her,[p/] and we could run away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b89e02",
  "node": "LastNightmare",
  "text": "We'd have to abandon our home,[p/] but there was nothing she couldn't do."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e1faf",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "I tried to sprint towards the gallows,[p/] but a knight grabbed my arm and lifted me back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bca22d",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "Knight: Hey, kid.[p/] You can't cross this point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2c913",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "I tried to break his grip by striking him with my bare fists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7fc71",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "They just fruitlessly clanged against his plate armor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33122",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "Knight: H-[p/]Hey![p/][s/] Stop that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:099264c",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "It wasn't doing anything,[p/] but I was in a frenzy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d760a",
  "node": "LastNightmare2",
  "text": "I just threw punch after punch.[p/] My knuckles were starting to bleed."
}

{
  "id": "line:02224f4",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Having had enough,[p/] the knight pinned me to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dfc5d",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Knight: Damn kid..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a80c4f",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "I desperately struggled against him to no avail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd96af",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "From this position,[p/] I had no choice but to watch what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b1eb5",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cde28",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "I made eye contact with my mother one last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db19fb",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Her body went limp.[p/] I stared blankly at the hanging corpse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0480b27",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/][s/] This isn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ce88b",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Mom...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50374",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "I held her note tightly in my hands,[p/] the paper nearly crumpling in my grip."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a4f44",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "I felt a comforting yet fleeting warmth from it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2bdf",
  "node": "LastNightmare3",
  "text": "I was all alone now."
}

{
  "id": "line:068ee60",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cc567",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/]Celeste...?[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b81406",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "I snapped back awake.[p/] It was just another nightmare..."
}

{
  "id": "line:038a493",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "It took me a while before I realized that tears were streaming down my face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da5a64",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "I quickly tried to bring up my sleeve to wipe them away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0096529",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "...But I realized that Celeste was firmly gripping my hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9f21",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/]Wha—?[p/] Why are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030f787",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/][s/]Ah![p/] S-[p/][s/]Sorry!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6730",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] You were kind of...[p/] shouting in your sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf768e",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: You seemed to calm down whenever I held your hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05839c3",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] I've been...[p/] doing that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2fd5b",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae9da8",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion, are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fb3ab",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you're not,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a83949",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f7421",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: It's [i]not[/i] fine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f22163",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Does it have something to do with what happened to your mom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091def3",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: For the last two nights,[p/] you've been calling out for her in your sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc37c",
  "node": "LastNightmare4",
  "text": "Celeste: Please.[p/] Just talk to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11912",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "I didn't have many people in my life after I left Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a06724",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "I only had Ms. Tymora,[p/] and my mother's death had always weighed heavily on her, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b50b78",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "But Celeste had been there since I started my career."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c50153",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It all happened a long time ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644593",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I lived here together with my mother in that old house."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f0843",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was a merchant...[p/] and a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f53c73",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Celeste: Your mom was a mage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0889bb1",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess the gift of magic skipped my generation...[p/] [i]I[/i] could never use it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00032b6",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...About ten years ago,[p/] my mother's business partner was found murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e15c7",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And they found traces of magic at the crime scene..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03578a5",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Celeste: They thought that your mom did it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e180",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora was my mom's attorney at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bd89b",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: She did everything she could,[p/] but they couldn't find the real killer."
}

{
  "id": "line:083fd9a",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I tried to stop her execution,[p/] b-[p/][s/]but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c86eae",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "My voice started breaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce9748",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0969200",
  "node": "LastNightmare5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0704d50",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was saving people from being killed like my mother was.[p/] I thought I'd finally moved on."
}

{
  "id": "line:053bdc4",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I'm back in Aurinax...[p/] And these feelings are just as fresh in my mind as they were back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fd28b",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Celeste: What was she like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac810d",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Celeste: What was your mom like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd2a7d",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "I thought for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e0b1",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was amazing.[p/] She raised me by herself while working as a fortune teller."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d89705",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...A fortune teller?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fb463",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know how it sounds,[p/] but she wasn't a scam artist."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e211",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: People would come to her with all sorts of problems."
}

{
  "id": "line:0987051",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: They'd tell her all about their relationship issues,[p/] their financial troubles,[p/] even their existential crises."
}

{
  "id": "line:06de9f0",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the time she pulled a single tarot card,[p/] she already knew exactly what they needed to hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2ae3",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tarot readings are funny like that.[p/] You can assign any meaning you want to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbac55",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sometimes she'd do them for me, too.[p/] I always had something on my mind back then—[p/]stupid kid stuff."
}

{
  "id": "line:017ace2",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she always knew just what to say to make me feel better."
}

{
  "id": "line:083991b",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "It wasn't until years afterwards that I realized she had the Eye of Horus too."
}

{
  "id": "line:04463d5",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think she always felt bad that she was working all the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8598e",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: On her days off,[p/] she'd always take me out with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:091ef44",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'd eat at restaurants.[p/] We'd play chess by the docks.[p/] She's the one who taught me how to play."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7ec46",
  "node": "LastNightmare6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sometimes we'd sail out at night and watch the lights of the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:045cb7f",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those memories are still happy for me,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf43d7",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: They remind you of what you've lost."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d84b5",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I still feel like I'm the same powerless kid from ten years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:036bc27",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm really sorry, Celeste...[p/] I know that I've been taking that out on you."
}

{
  "id": "line:023db0f",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I get it.[p/] I know what it's like to lose someone like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22da0",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: If it weren't for you,[p/] I'd still be trapped in that terrible night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7687",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: You gave me my life back."
}

{
  "id": "line:014c579",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste, I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0238a1a",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste slowly clasped my hand within hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb4cf2",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "It was warm and comforting.[p/] Had this been the warmth I'd been feeling for the last few nights?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004132a",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you're dealing with a lot right now,[p/] but just let me be here for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b762b",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "I could feel myself dozing off.[p/] I had to snap myself awake."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5b4d",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry.[p/] The last few days have been...[p/] a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:051e155",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: It's okay.[p/] Just rest now."
}

{
  "id": "line:06538ec",
  "node": "LastNightmare7",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll stay with you for as long as you need me to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b0be",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*yawn*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0188046",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'm also feeling pretty tired, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0671b15",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll just rest my eyes a bit..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c2791",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "For the first time since I arrived in Aurinax,[p/] I'd finally received a good night's rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca56d",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "I woke up the next morning feeling well-rested—[p/]almost too much in a way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8e74e",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "The pillows and blankets felt like warm clouds embracing me.[p/] I didn't want to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:005a575",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste?[p/] Are you there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78eb5",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "My hand felt warm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0802c46",
  "node": "LastNightmare7b",
  "text": "I could feel my heart stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5ec6",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...C-[p/]Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000647e",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugggggggh...[p/] What do you want?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5e5b",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Her eyes slowly opened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3373",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Through half-lidded eyes,[p/] she scanned her surroundings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d63f81",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8610a",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "We both immediately jumped out of bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00df245",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/][s/] So—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f41f7",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]You're okay now, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095ae8f",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You seem to be doing better."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d149d",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-Yeah...[p/][s/] Thank you for last night."
}

{
  "id": "line:075c4e5",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "The words stumbled out of my mouth before I realized how poorly I'd phrased that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed207e",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "I just cleared my throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aeee9",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]We should get ready for the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf57f6",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "Celeste: Yep![p/][s/] The trial![p/][s/] Let's go do that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d235f",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "I'd lost a lot of time,[p/] but it was my own fault for ignoring my fatigue for so long."
}

{
  "id": "line:069d6c6",
  "node": "LastNightmare8",
  "text": "I would just need to play this by ear."
}

{
  "id": "line:061b4b7",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Painting"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e5107",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a landscape painting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5cb8d",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Coraline: Is that Lake Galakrond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e602e",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: Yes,[p/] I had it commissioned last month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0445f94",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: The view of the Grand Cathedral is quite lovely this time of year."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513e79",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a shelf full of books."
}

{
  "id": "line:025c7b2",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What's this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b46d8",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: D-[p/][s/]Don't touch that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ce430",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Chess Theory for Dummies\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f331",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]Hrk[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b47e86",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well, at least you're being honest with yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f600",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...You know I can still have you thrown out."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c058b",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Mirror"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3aec8",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a large mirror."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ced9",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure a nobleman like von Sanctus spends hours looking at himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb1208",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm standing right here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:066671e",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:09956a7",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a window.[p/] I can see the entire city from up here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1481",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sure the Duke of Commerce enjoys looking down on the people he's ruling over."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dd3a8",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: ... [h=\"Well...|That's not [i]untrue[/i]...\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f6908",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are two cups of tea poured out on the table."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29f5d",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: The fragrance is refreshing.[p/] It must be an exotic brand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf8a5c",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm not going to offer [i]you[/i] any,[p/] if [i]that's[/i] what you were expecting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0889c21",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Fireplace"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2bb61",
  "node": "Manor1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a fireplace.[p/] I can smell the sweet scent of applewood burning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7480",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Charges Against Dracogen"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f84ee",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:07df864",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You've been awfully quiet."
}

{
  "id": "line:05df8ae",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: ...I didn't want to interrupt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0688216",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yet, you're just as responsible for the commoners' suffering as he is."
}

{
  "id": "line:05db7ef",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06901e4",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: Tell me, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Do you think artificery plays a vital role in our society?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031db3f",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Of course I do.[p/] It's the only way for us commoners to use Arcane Magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0089339",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: Correct.[p/] The existence of the arcane refineries is essential for our society to function."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e20450",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: So, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] would you ever work in one?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069fec7",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] No,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e4fe4",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: You wouldn't,[p/] because you were afforded privileges that many others do not have."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cf9f8",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: No one wants to do that sort of work,[p/] but [i]someone[/i] has to for society to function."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1a32",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: Everyone has their role in Wyverngarde,[p/] and more often than not,[p/] people don't receive a role they like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10e14",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: No one decides what kind of circumstances they are born into.[p/] Only the Cosmic Balance decides that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd4ec5",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"Cosmic Balance\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13009",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ugh...[p/] Please don't get her started on that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0771e9d",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: The Cosmic Balance is the chaos of the universe—[p/]the law of averages made manifest."
}

{
  "id": "line:009bf5a",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: No one can control the outside forces that determine their lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:035a0a5",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: Some are born into the aristocracy,[p/] and some are born into poverty."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ce437",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's awfully easy to accept when you were born in the former."
}

{
  "id": "line:0020e76",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: The world is not fair.[p/] It has never been fair."
}

{
  "id": "line:01487cb",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: So we build systems to keep it from crumbling under its own cruelty."
}

{
  "id": "line:026014e",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Systems that benefit you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0800ede",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Systems that protect the aristocracy and grind everyone else down until they've outlived their usefulness."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c031d",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: There must be stability...[p/] Even if it causes discomfort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce9f96",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: The chaos of the universe may seem cruel,[p/] but it's fair."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eee7fe",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: The system wouldn't be this way if it didn't work."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ed5d1",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The False Reports"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc372",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since you two care about the \"system\" so much,[p/] you should know that someone's abusing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:089282d",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c372d2",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure you've heard about the \"Mistweaving Phantom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5332",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I believe they've been stealing official records from the unions and the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc1e9",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They've been using those records to craft false reports about hostile tensions between them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceebcc",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:053fa83",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bfc6f",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "He paused for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0783e11",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Coraline: Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00303a6",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I think what he's saying is actually quite plausible."
}

{
  "id": "line:071d389",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Wait, really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb3ba0",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: There [i]has[/i] been something peculiar about the recent string of robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0090db7",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Namely, [i]who[/i] they've been targeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc6857",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you talking about how they hit the union offices?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5bda",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm sure I'll regret telling you this,[p/] but there's something about his targets that hasn't been released to the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:075faee",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Many of the individuals who were robbed were secretly plotting treason against the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e5af4",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you only saying that because they were members of the unions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0055097",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm saying that because law enforcement found hidden illegal communications,[p/] weapons,[p/] and explosives at the sites of most of the robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0117d84",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was strange.[p/] There were many times when the victims returned home to find their houses ransacked."
}

{
  "id": "line:098fc07",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: When the City Watch arrived to investigate the crime,[p/] they noticed one peculiarity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0582b00",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: The victims never called the City Watch to report the crime.[p/] Someone else did."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9048",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Despite the clear fact that a crime had occurred,[p/] some of the victims resisted attempts to search their home."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d7678",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: The knights found that quite suspect and found that as probable cause."
}

{
  "id": "line:0697099",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: They found evidence of treason when they searched the victims' homes."
}

{
  "id": "line:037f760",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was as if the Phantom were intentionally targeting those who were plotting against the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e87338",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What reason could the thief possibly have to do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021b4d1",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's clear the thief wants the Crown to be aware that insurrection is brewing within Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a624d",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: And with those false reports,[p/] a far more dire situation is being painted."
}

{
  "id": "line:042f340",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "Lloyd: Who do you think would benefit the most from something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0156709",
  "node": "Manor1_Talk",
  "text": "[i]One[/i] prolific noble came to mind..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3b54",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't suppose you'd be willing to drop the charges you've laid against Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d527b7",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ha![p/][s/] I thought you were smarter than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c98725",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was worth a shot,[p/] but it's obvious you're not one for competition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15848",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why else would you be trying so hard to squash a small company?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f22247",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Oh, is [i]that[/i] what you think?[p/] How simpleminded of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0795442",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Am I wrong?[p/] Von Sanctus Industries is massive and has operations throughout Wyverngarde.[p/] He's just one merchant in one city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0953399",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: That \"one merchant\" is spreading insidious ideas like it's the plague."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fee08b",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: So,[p/] encouraging workers to unionize and protect themselves is \"insidious\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006bbb3",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Oh, yes.[p/] It sounds very flowery and marvelous when [i]he[/i] says it,[p/] but have you ever stopped to think about what he's doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3cd1c",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: He's encouraging those at the bottom to stand together and take power away from those above them."
}

{
  "id": "line:091a897",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: What's the difference between that and insurrection?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f900be",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Celeste: They're advocating for their basic human rights!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0181f73",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: And do you want to know something?[p/] That's not entirely unreasonable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eafa8b",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'll admit that I'm actually pleased that fewer employees are getting hurt in this city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eff455",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, [i]really[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea742",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: You may think I'm heartless,[p/] but I'm not a monster."
}

{
  "id": "line:058a4a8",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: If these unions simply kept people safe,[p/] I would take no issue with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0508d0a",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: But it's never going to stop there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eddb98",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: You give these people power,[p/] and they'll just become hungry for more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607b7d",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: They'll take and take and take until there's nothing left for the rest of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa45ee",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Celeste: So they'll do what you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f02c25",
  "node": "LloydChargeConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: The difference is that [i]they[/i] won't care when our society devolves into anarchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abc2e9",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: What's this?[p/] A Runestone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4b71",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's my [i]Attorney's[/i] Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0657b32",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ah,[p/] I guess they must give the older models to people of your station."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c0322",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: As the Duke of Commerce,[p/] [i]my[/i] Runestone is always the latest model."
}

{
  "id": "line:0638937",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Can I see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056893f",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...No."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ee048",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] I thought the papers were exaggerating,[p/] but you truly are just as impertinent as they say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5d496",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: From you,[p/] I'll take that as a compliment."
}

{
  "id": "line:075df38",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: What goes on in that head of yours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e2d03",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Do you people honestly think you're changing [i]anything[/i] by slinging mud at the nobility?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065df0b",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: As long as I can save one person,[p/] I'll be happy with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69363",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Taking whatever you can get.[p/] I suppose that suits someone of your birth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4a2a6",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ruby Tymora...[p/] She's been a pain for as long as I can remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac38ac",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: How do you people live with yourselves?[p/] You're just as responsible for this unrest as the criminals you protect."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bfc54",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We only work within the confines of [i]your[/i] corrupt system."
}

{
  "id": "line:05926ba",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: If justice sides with us,[p/] then that's your own fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:0129cf8",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ah,[p/] so you're simply in denial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0945de4",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] you're the Duke of Commerce and the patriarch of one of the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece7b1",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What of it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03475b9",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just imagined the face of my enemy to be a lot less weasel-like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515125",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] And people like you look [i]exactly[/i] like what I imagined."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cfcd4",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: You're all just naïve and bright-eyed children."
}

{
  "id": "line:0630d8e",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Stefanic Dracogen,[p/] ever the thorn in my side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26636",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0278b71",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's nothing.[p/] Talking about it would be pointless."
}

{
  "id": "line:032b301",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: As the Minster of Justice,[p/] he probably sees you as the face of \"corruption\" in his line of work."
}

{
  "id": "line:003f565",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: I understand you may have grievances with the current justice system,[p/] but it exists like this for a reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4fb91",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's easy for you to say.[p/] [i]You're[/i] not the one affected by it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3f53",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: ...How could I not be affected by it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da61b1",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: My house's sole responsibility is managing and facilitating the laws of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0730cd7",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your system sentences innocent mages to death!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ca715",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...I would watch your tone, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d511f",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's only by her generosity that I haven't had you thrown out."
}

{
  "id": "line:031aa61",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: It's quite all right, Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8574c",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: You may think the justice system is cruel.[p/] You may even think it's been corrupted,[p/] but one cannot expect perfection from a system so large."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e1a5b",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: I believe the generation that came before me had created the closest thing to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:094ecd3",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Really?[p/] How self-gratifying of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbd401",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: The laws of our kingdom aren't a monolith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0832186",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: They are changed and reinterpreted by the House of Lords.[p/] As it was designed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9f270",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: The House of Lords is just filled with nobles who mold the laws to suit them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0851b7f",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: You may hate the nobility,[p/] but they have the best perspective on how Wyverngarde must be run."
}

{
  "id": "line:02960f1",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: And aristocrats aren't the only people who have a voice in the House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c77004",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: The commoners have their own representatives there as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4545d",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: The records of our assemblies are in the public record."
}

{
  "id": "line:061df44",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: You'll often see those same representatives vote in harmony with the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:00754c3",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because the nobles are probably paying them off!"
}

{
  "id": "line:097a8f6",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: ...That's a grave accusation.[p/] Do you have any evidence to support it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05debd1",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I don't,[p/][s/] but—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6e9ed",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: Wouldn't it be simpler to say that those representatives are voting in disagreement with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bedb38",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: You do not speak for the commoners.[p/] The only voice I trust is that of the House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf064e",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know the victim in the accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0a54",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...No.[p/] Why would I?[p/] He was just a factory worker."
}

{
  "id": "line:026e3b2",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this ring, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c7a11",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...No.[p/] Why would I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0432c36",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I can feel myself hemorrhaging gold with each hour Lucio maintains this blockade."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a379d",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Coraline: I'm sure he's just being cautious."
}

{
  "id": "line:080e37a",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Really?[p/] Because I suspect this is retaliation for the words that were said at the Grand Cathedral months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0685410",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you say at the Grand Cathedral?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cd58c",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...It's none of your business."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f9197",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this leather strap, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0277c58",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Player: UnionTensions|Treason"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a45ab",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] This is what happens when we make concessions to those below us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f425f8",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: The hierarchy becomes muddled,[p/] and they try to take more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff7110",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: These tensions are grossly exaggerated.[p/] Mr. Morrison and my client are on good terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:03113b0",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...So you say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15433",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Player: ShipRep|Phantom"
}

{
  "id": "line:0875eb5",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: This \"Mistweaving Phantom\" has made off with so many of my shipments.[p/] It's been such a headache."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7e154",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you actually tell me how they got past your armed guards?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1df1",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: There's nothing to say.[p/] He's clearly a master of stealth.[p/] My men can't make heads or tails of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9d8a",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: The only silver lining of Lucio's little blockade is that he'll finally be caught once and for all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ac2d",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: Don't waste my time, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b5e3d",
  "node": "Manor1_Present",
  "text": "Lloyd: I have nothing to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c4c6e",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: My apologies,[p/] but Lord von Sanctus isn't accepting any visitors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0870fbf",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: This isn't a visit.[p/] I need to talk to him right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0875565",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "The nobleman gestured towards a guard who was standing at the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b8679",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] get them out of the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0693720",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0787d08",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: We are [i]going[/i] to see von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e4ad1",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Either step aside,[p/] or we're going to go through you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6a00d",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait, Tyrion.[p/] This does [i]not[/i] sound legal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4db9b",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: ...Let him in."
}

{
  "id": "line:07736a8",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05872c2",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sure Mr. Cuthbert has no untoward intentions."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8adc",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: I think it would be in everyone's best interests for him to speak with Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ff550",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: Your—[p/][s/] S-[p/][s/]Sir![p/][s/] You can't be serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fbad2",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: ...Is there a problem?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0043805",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] Of course, not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10ce0",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: Please come in, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa9a77",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Thank you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:084c2c6",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: Know that I'm wishing you luck in the upcoming trial, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:033340f",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd86b",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Without another word,[p/] the mysterious man started to walk away from the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d634b",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, sorry![p/] I didn't catch your name."
}

{
  "id": "line:069c5d9",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Aster: You can call me \"Aster\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dc788",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "...Wasn't Aster the high-profile noble that Mr. Morrison mentioned?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0588184",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "He also owned the ship from which that \"threat to national security\" had been stolen!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ccb58",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "I looked at the nobleman,[p/] then at Aster who was walking farther and farther away."
}

{
  "id": "line:00724fa",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "I really needed to know what he saw,[p/] but I knew they'd never let me into the manor a second time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bec62",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "The trial was coming up,[p/] and I would need to make a choice.[p/] Do I talk to Aster or von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079280e",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "We already had Rika's testimony,[p/] even if it contradicted the lack of magic traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee6839",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "The most important aspect of the case was the Mistweaving Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e89cf7",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "I would have to just focus on von Sanctus for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:017cdf8",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "The Duke's attendant led us into the manor before stopping at a closed door.[p/] I could hear voices coming from inside it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddeb2f",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "One of the voices was distinctly Lloyd's.[p/] I'd recognize that nasally,[p/] high-pitched whine anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9d3ba",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Nobleman: Wait, here.[p/] I need to...[p/] [i]inform[/i] the Duke of your arrival."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0feaa",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "He entered the room while we waited outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0014f13",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...So do you want to tell me what [i]that[/i] was about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7148f",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: You were trying to sic me on those two like some kind of dog."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a06062",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm not some goon you can use to threaten people like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:060dc4a",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I'm sorry.[p/] I was just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b56a0f",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: You're usually way more level-headed than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cef4f",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You've been acting differently since we got here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6fe4e",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] Did something happen here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0715ee3",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry for barking orders at you like that.[p/] I just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:007a3e2",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I grew up here,[p/] and I really don't like what's happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3a94e",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Things are so much better now,[p/] and I don't want whatever's happening to ruin that for everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10313",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay, I get it.[p/] Just don't do that again, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b4f71",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: And if you ever need to talk to someone—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94f12",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's just focus on the investigation for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:092781d",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b85d2",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "As we entered the nearby room,[p/] we came upon Lloyd von Sanctus speaking with another unfamiliar individual."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee923",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I just knew you meeting the Crown Prince was a disaster waiting to happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afdc89",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: I heard about what happened.[p/] Crown Prince Aster let you in, didn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010b59b",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: That man was the Crown Prince?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebb1af",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "I [i]knew[/i] I'd recognized that name somewhere.[p/] This is what I got for not reading the paper more regularly."
}

{
  "id": "line:08725d7",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] Okay.[p/] One thing at a time."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ab3aa",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since I have you here,[p/] do you mind if I ask you some questions about Aurinax?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cfd75",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Absolutely not![p/][s/] Get out of my house!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0282757",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "He stayed silent for a while before he let out a heavy sigh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1cfa3",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a644b",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'll answer your questions,[p/] if only to show you how little of a case you have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e00e35",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Maybe you can convince your client to accept the futility of his situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a94b63",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you, Ms.—[p/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a0d83",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Coraline: I am Coraline Sibyl:[p/] head of House Sibyl,[p/] and Wyverngarde's Duchess of Law."
}

{
  "id": "line:092d3ac",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07efc20",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Grand General Steelwind is involved in this somehow.[p/] I'm sure of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecd689",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline,[p/] I understand you've always cared for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0307a8e",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: However,[p/] even [i]you[/i] must admit he's never been the same since that tragedy with Ophelia."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3eb4",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Coraline: Even so,[p/] it's not my place to decide that.[p/] It will be up to the House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e722a1",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Really?![p/][s/] Even now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0852775",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Coraline: You have no evidence.[p/] The House won't condemn Lucio based on hearsay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0437bab",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Coraline: Until then,[p/] the Grand General will fulfill his role in our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ddb51",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even while countless innocent lives have been lost under his watch?"
}

{
  "id": "line:066db13",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Lloyd: Pah... [h=\"Soon the Grand General|will be obsolete...\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00dd89c",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Could the Mistweaving Phantom really be an agent of Lucio Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0251927",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "But if their intention was to reveal insurrectionists,[p/] why would they have bothered robbing the merchant shipments?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05624da",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Was it just to create a cover to hide their true intentions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc4826",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "...Either way,[p/] if the Phantom was at the refinery that morning,[p/] it's possible Justin spotted them."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f020c",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "They'd remained unseen throughout their string of robberies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc89d3",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "Did the Phantom attack Justin to keep their identity hidden?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0312221",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "...The trial was coming up soon,[p/] and I still didn't have any definitive evidence to prove Justin was even attacked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0739022",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "But it couldn't be helped.[p/] I'd run out of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7a913",
  "node": "Manor1_Check",
  "text": "I would just need to work with what I had."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb62df",
  "node": "RikaFail",
  "text": "Mosourika: Look...[p/] I already told you that I don't want to talk about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0193a8b",
  "node": "RikaFail",
  "text": "Mosourika: Can you just drop it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036289f",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "I needed to know more about the people that Mosourika used to run with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0586c9a",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "And I couldn't ignore what Steelwind said during the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee0b5",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "Supposedly,[p/] the Mistweaving Phantom's thefts were similar to the thefts she took part in all those years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cf3c5",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "She was holding something back.[p/] I just needed to convince her to tell me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe9aef",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "Yes"
}

{
  "id": "line:049378b",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "No"
}

{
  "id": "line:065d43f",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b94502",
  "node": "RikaArgue",
  "text": "Mosourika: Can you just let this go?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e02db",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"I need this information if I want to save Dracogen and find out who killed Justin.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:047b7af",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know I'm asking a lot,[p/] but there's too much at stake here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01141ee",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I need this information if I want to save Dracogen and find out what really happened to Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa470",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Empathy [c=\"I can imagine it's a difficult subject. I'll understand if you don't want to share.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc89b1",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can imagine it's a difficult subject."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6efe7",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll understand if you don't want to share."
}

{
  "id": "line:030735c",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Mosourika: Good.[p/] Then stop asking me about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f61fa",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "...There was no way around this."
}

{
  "id": "line:023803c",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "I felt bad for digging up old wounds,[p/] but I was running out of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:02992fa",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "I needed this information.[p/] I just needed to get her to understand that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0668a39",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Call [c=\"Someone killed your friend. Are you seriously not going to tell me what I need to know?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:043aa2b",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What am I supposed to think after all of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd859",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone killed your friend.[p/] Are you seriously not going to tell me what I need to know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62262",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Mosourika: You don't need to know about that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f035fd",
  "node": "RikaArgue1",
  "text": "Mosourika: It has nothing to do with this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:044f162",
  "node": "RikaArgue2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...I'm [i]not[/i] hiding anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cec909",
  "node": "RikaArgue2",
  "text": "Mosourika: What Steelwind said about this new thief isn't true.[p/] It's just a coincidence. [h=\"Only [i]he[/i] was ever good enough|to get away with robbing an imperial ship.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bdf31",
  "node": "RikaArgue3",
  "text": "Logic"
}

{
  "id": "line:002cd96",
  "node": "RikaArgue3",
  "text": "Intuition"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dda77",
  "node": "RikaArgue3",
  "text": "Empathy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeec14",
  "node": "RikaArgue3Fail",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] you obviously don't think that."
}

{
  "id": "line:035bb41",
  "node": "RikaArgue3Fail",
  "text": "Mosourika: Yeah?[p/] And how do you know what I really think...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0826470",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think you really believe that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0799921",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: One of the people you used to work with was really good, wasn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048d380",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Only he was ever good enough to successfully rob an imperial ship."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f8ca1",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: How did you know that...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06df5d4",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Naught can remain concealed from the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f386c9",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion,[p/] don't joke around right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ba3c4",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09deb15",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] this person is dangerous."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5336",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: You don't know that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a36a8",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you say that?[p/] He attacked your friend!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd875",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: I keep telling you![p/][s/] That's [i]not[/i] what happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f2363",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: Whoever they are,[p/] they were just trying to survive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc96ae",
  "node": "RikaArgue4",
  "text": "Mosourika: They didn't kill Justin,[p/] and they're not dangerous."
}

{
  "id": "line:039784c",
  "node": "RikaArgue5",
  "text": "Blockade3"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffbe74",
  "node": "RikaArgue5",
  "text": "Mosourika: What's [i]this[/i] supposed to be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d81224",
  "node": "RikaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's proof that the serial robber is more dangerous than you think he is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac1677",
  "node": "RikaArgue5",
  "text": "Mosourika: Tyrion...[p/] That doesn't prove anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1c026",
  "node": "RikaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0500fe6",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika,[p/] the Mistweaving Phantom stole something important from a ship owned by the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae1618",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: He did...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054d8a5",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: He stole several high-capacity arcane crystals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5905f",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those crystals could be used to construct an explosive powerful enough to destroy a city block."
}

{
  "id": "line:0995048",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why do you think Lucio Steelwind has been blockading the city for the last few days?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0624a37",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08eaab8",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know you're just trying to do the right thing,[p/] but whoever the Phantom is,[p/] their actions could have unimaginable consequences for the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fd1e6",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: How can I trust you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06306a8",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: How can I trust you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b6a8a",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: You just disappeared into the forest after the execution![p/][s/] I thought you were dead!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f16c7",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: And then ten years later you show up in the paper,[p/] working for some shady lawyer!"
}

{
  "id": "line:011fc6d",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: Lucio Steelwind saved you at the trial yesterday,[p/] and you're even friendly with his daughter!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08edd7d",
  "node": "RikaArgue6",
  "text": "Mosourika: What am I supposed to think?![p/][s/] How am I supposed to trust you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c95582",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"I'm sorry, but believe me when I say that I want to save you and this city.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0860b4f",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"That has nothing to do with this. The serial robber needs to be caught.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:083b630",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: That has nothing to do with this.[p/] The serial robber needs to be caught."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76346",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Mosourika: It has [i]everything[/i] to do with this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c27d88",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Mosourika: I have no way of knowing if I can actually trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bdb31",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"All of the evidence I have says that I need this information. Please don't make my job harder than it is to me.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7dc77",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: All of the evidence I have says that I need this information."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ba7e5",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please don't make my job harder than it is to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0473703",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Mosourika: How do I know you're not lying to me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97383",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Mosourika: You've changed a lot...[p/] So have I."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cffe4",
  "node": "RikaArgue7",
  "text": "Mosourika: I barely even know you.[p/] I can't trust you with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39f4e",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry.[p/] There's nothing I can say to make up for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b7915",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know I've changed a lot,[p/] but believe me when I say that I want to save you and this city."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c20bc",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please, Rika.[p/] I [i]need[/i] you to tell me who the serial robber is."
}

{
  "id": "line:02abb71",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't defend Dracogen or stop Lucio unless I know that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd2bed",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "Mosourika: [i]*sigh*[/i] ...Okay.[p/] I'll trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5ab5a",
  "node": "RikaArgue8",
  "text": "I successfully PERSUADED Mosourika Tudor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44e58",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Sea"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd72b2",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "The view of the sea was just as I remembered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a408c1",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "It was probably the only thing that hadn't changed since I left Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af833b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "Player: House"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4269",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "I really wished I could've avoided returning to this house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df4b1b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "The wood was dirty,[p/] but otherwise in good condition.[p/] So much time must've passed since I was last here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb8465",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Examine",
  "text": "...Damn it all.[p/] I felt a headache coming on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b092ba",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Justin Waye"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4c8e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about Justin Waye?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fecc1d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to a witness we spoke to,[p/] you two seemed to be friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0c1ae",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: \"Friends\" is kind of pushing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d26f6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: We used to hang back in the day,[p/] but we don't no more. [h=\"It was weird when he started talking to us again.|I thought he left for good.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06db930",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But he started talking to you again.[p/] Why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07022ca",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...! [h=\"They already know?!\" e=\"f\"]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0751b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: We didn't go lookin' for him![p/][s/] He just showed up here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0843",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: He said he needed to stay at the hideout for a while!"
}

{
  "id": "line:030aede",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "I cursed under my breath.[p/] I couldn't believe these people were living in [i]my[/i] house."
}

{
  "id": "line:025e4f4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: You know he's dead, right?[p/][s/] You don't exactly need to go looking for him. [h=\"Are they still trying to|collect on his debts?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:098336f",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "...Justin had some debts?[p/] Who were they to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0226e32",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Justin's Debts"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da1a2",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt apparently thought that we were sent on behalf of someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c1cdc",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "And from what I'd seen,[p/] Justin apparently owed a debt to this person."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c5061",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "If this person was some kind of criminal,[p/] could [i]they[/i] have been his accomplice in the robberies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b4b39",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did Justin tell you [i]who[/i] he owed his debt to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0b69",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: A-[p/]Ah![p/] Nah, man.[p/] H-[p/]He didn't say nothing. [h=\"They might whack me too|if I tell them the truth.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec894d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "So, he [i]did[/i] know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b78946",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's no point in playing dumb.[p/] Just tell us what he told you."
}

{
  "id": "line:091379e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did he give you a name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0384b36",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: U-[p/][s/]Uh...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:009a68a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Answer the question."
}

{
  "id": "line:081ead9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: T-[p/][s/]The Eyetaker![p/][s/] He owed gold to the Eyetaker!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c5113",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "\"The Eyetaker\"...?[p/] Was that some kind of street name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba8f25",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "It sounded familiar for some reason.[p/] I couldn't shake the feeling that I'd heard it somewhere before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe2cf",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Eyetaker"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2028d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about the Eyetaker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d432f5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Is this a test or something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea20dc",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3326c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: W-[p/][s/]Well, it ain't a secret![p/][s/] He's the criminal kingpin of this region!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09056cc",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: Anything that happens here happens under his watch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0a98",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "So Justin had a debt to a crime lord...[p/][s/] Was [i]that[/i] why he returned to a life of crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db152a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did they get into contact?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08aea74",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: It was when he was locked up in the dungeons.[p/] He made a deal with the Eyetaker's shot caller there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baa765",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: Justin didn't say much about it,[p/] but I think he got into something deep while he was serving his time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3e36",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: The Eyetaker bailed him out,[p/] but that ran a debt that'd be collected when he got out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9d808",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Knowing how the dungeons were,[p/] he might've needed the Eyetaker's protection to survive in there."
}

{
  "id": "line:085e61d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Justin was a remarkable thief.[p/] The Eyetaker must have seen that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b564b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "I could imagine a number of reasons why a crime lord might want to stir up trouble,[p/] but I needed something more concrete."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d383",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Player: What was Justin doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e01878",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You said that Justin was staying in the house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0c92",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know what he was doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0982b12",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: I don't know, man.[p/] I don't ask nothing! [h=\"I guess he was back|to being the Mistweaver Phantom.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d746f9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is there [i]anything[/i] you can tell me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d77eb",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: I don't know![p/][s/] I guess it was kind of weird that he'd always leave the house but never enter it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfd110",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: Gavin said the same thing the other day!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087ebe5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "Wyatt: We always saw him leave through the front door,[p/] but we never saw him enter it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05332d9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Talk",
  "text": "...Was Justin sneaking past them?[p/] But why would he only do that when he [i]entered[/i] the house?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00efb18",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...What's this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5b1c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Oh,[p/] you're like one of those criminal lawyers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0840157",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] I didn't see nothing, man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f52593",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: But I'll take the stand if the Eyetaker needs me to."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed6d4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/][s/]That's fine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b32a0b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Hey...[p/] You look kind of familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0743ffa",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Are you from here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee728d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...No,[p/] I'm just visiting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d54e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Nah,[p/] I could've sworn I've seen you in the paper."
}

{
  "id": "line:0468e02",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: I can't remember what the article was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0066681",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're mistaken.[p/] I just have one of those faces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0958e28",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Really?[p/] I don't see many blonds around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0475907",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Who the hell is that girl?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082b72d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's my bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0617576",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Oh, I get it.[p/] She's your muscle."
}

{
  "id": "line:000122a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "...He wasn't exactly wrong about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:015254c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you know about Mosourika Tudor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0513302",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Hey,[p/] she don't got nothing to do with any of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fb5c3",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: She got out a long time ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b11f25",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you two friends?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3ea3",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Nah,[p/] we used to be,[p/] but I got my path and she got hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0717b77",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: We live in two different worlds now.[p/] No sense in hanging onto the past."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa3e0",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "That was surprisingly mature of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ded927",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Player: Gavin"
}

{
  "id": "line:008aeff",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Yo,[p/] is Gavin going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c11bf",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We both got a little enthusiastic."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a16a7",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll be fine as long as you tell us what you know."
}

{
  "id": "line:081001b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure he's in good hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b829ab",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] is a male arm supposed to bend this way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef2bb",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I don't think so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0815bb4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7c200",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You might want to take him to a doctor after this."
}

{
  "id": "line:006e91d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do you and Gavin [i]do[/i] here exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c581d1",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: We just hang around here, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd6761",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: It's nice and quiet,[p/] and I don't think anyone else knows about this place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2bc12",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "I had to temper myself.[p/] [i]I[/i] was the one who left this house behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0271650",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "For all they knew,[p/] the residents had abandoned it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b960f6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Player: Autopsy|Justin|Phantom"
}

{
  "id": "line:038432a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Hmph...[p/] Justin was always too big for his britches."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b37e90",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: He gets some cushy job at the refinery,[p/] and suddenly he's too good to hang with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:091c490",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Well, look where that got him."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b8d0",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: One word from the Eyetaker,[p/] and he comes crawling back to the life."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a871e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you recognize this ring, Wyatt?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d19e2",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: Oh, yeah.[p/] Justin always had it on whenever he was at the house."
}

{
  "id": "line:026766e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "...That was strange.[p/] Every other witness who regularly saw him didn't recognize the ring at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f1a65",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about [i]this[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc815",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "Wyatt: S-[p/]Sorry, man...[p/] I don't know nothing about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07492d4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Present",
  "text": "He appeared to be telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3bf6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "We arrived at my old abandoned house.[p/] From far away,[p/] I could already tell it had fallen into a state of disrepair."
}

{
  "id": "line:045c2b3",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "My mother had always kept our home hidden from the city.[p/] I guess she really liked her privacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:083aa1b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "It didn't seem like anyone was living there,[p/] but the front door was hanging open.[p/] Some looters must have gotten to it at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b432f4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001fcbb",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yeah.[p/] Let's look around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa7b0b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I wiped my eyes and began looking around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382e3b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I suddenly heard the sound of glass breaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0945be6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I rushed over to the other side of the house and spotted two young teenagers throwing rocks at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:026d532",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "The shattered remains of a window were lying on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6456",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: Ha,[p/][s/] nice one, Gavin.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06773c6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0143274",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "One of the teens,[p/] apparently named Gavin,[p/] noticed us approaching."
}

{
  "id": "line:02466d5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: ...Wyatt,[p/] we've got company."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9ef8",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: Huh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bce10",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I stared blankly at the broken glass lying on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf3a4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I just stood there for a moment.[p/] I felt like I wanted to say something,[p/] but nothing came out of my mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:002aac9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Instead,[p/] I found myself storming towards them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8710a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: Eh...?[p/] What the hell do you want?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0426939",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: Agh![p/][s/] What the hell?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a1cb1",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Before I even realized what I was doing,[p/] I threw a punch straight into Gavin's face."
}

{
  "id": "line:05654cd",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "My eyes were slowly tearing up.[p/] I was seeing red."
}

{
  "id": "line:078dbfb",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I grabbed Gavin by the collar and lifted him off the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ac013",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Get.[p/][p/][p/] The [i]hell[/i].[p/][p/][p/] Away from my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:068eb0f",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: Oh?![p/][s/] You want to go?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad8a11",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: Ha![p/] If you came looking for trouble,[p/] you sure found it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e27e1",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: U-[p/]Um...[p/] Okay.[p/] Let's [i]all[/i] calm down and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fef7dc",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: Stay out of this, you little shit!"
}

{
  "id": "line:033a038",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "...That comment sobered my rage immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ddf6d",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "I just stepped away from the inevitable bloodbath."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fd855",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Excuse me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3939e",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: What?![p/][s/] You got cotton in your ears or something?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0832f2c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Yes, actually."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d7e18",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Why don't you go and repeat what you said?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c12669",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: I [i]said[i/], \"stay out of this\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041d7b5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: You[p/][p/][p/][p/][s/] [i]little[/i][p/][p/][p/][p/][s/] shi[p/][p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:049346c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7056a",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0284107",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry for losing my temper back there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eee815",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] didn't mean to drag you into this."
}

{
  "id": "line:025050f",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: It's okay.[p/] You're going through a lot right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0116df8",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a50ca",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think you [i]might[/i] have overdone it a bit."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d865b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Nah."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c14bd2",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think he's breathing."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a82ca",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Just give him a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:05075e5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "The very bruised and broken form of Gavin began sputtering and wheezing as he regained consciousness."
}

{
  "id": "line:09812f5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: See?[p/] He's perfectly fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecb12b",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Gavin: [j]AGggGGgGggGGggGGGgGgGGGGGh[/j]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:093ab64",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: You're [p/][s/][i]fine[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e3e07",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f55ffb",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt jumped when our attention turned to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb02a0",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "His legs were trembling,[p/] but he was too frozen by fear to run away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3f334",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Don't bother running.[p/] Even with a head start,[p/] I'll catch up to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b47e4",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Eep!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05472a9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Anyways,[p/] these two are probably Justin's former \"delinquent friends\", right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c5329",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you okay with talking to them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039365f",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Y-[p/]Yes.[p/] O-[p/]Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:060bbad",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "My emotions were a mess.[p/] I'd completely forgotten why we came here in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8f5c5",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Would you two happen to know the young man who died at the refinery yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:046beaa",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...! [h=\"These guys are after [i]Justin[/i]?!|He's already dead, ain't he?!\" e=\"sf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f79b70",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "\"After Justin\"?[p/] Did Wyatt think we were sent here on someone else's behalf?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0509ed6",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] It might not hurt to play the part to get the information we needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a137a9",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] We're not going to hurt you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e20e0",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baa7a7",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We're not going to hurt you [i]anymore[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a1bee",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'd just like to ask you a few questions about Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9765c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Wyatt: Y-[p/]Yeah![p/][s/] S[p/][s/]-sure, man![p/][s/] Whatever you want!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16ba0",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright,[p/] you two talk."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a2832",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Gavin's shoulder is bent at a weird angle.[p/] I might need to pop his shoulder back into place."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b349c",
  "node": "TyrHouse_Check",
  "text": "…It was a little disturbing how nonchalantly she could say things like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0314fbd",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Wyatt: Look,[p/] that's all I saw!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0676e03",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Wyatt: I didn't see the magic cat![p/][s/] I didn't see nothing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:065a5d8",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "I blinked for a moment and took a slow, deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5661d",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do you mean by \"magic cat\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b64b4",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Wyatt: E-[p/][s/]Er—[p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I— [h=\"Are they going to off me|because I saw it?!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0a1d2",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "I had to massage my temples.[p/] I felt a migraine coming on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3fbc",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wyatt.[p/] Just tell me what you saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dac09",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Wyatt: Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a91d6e",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Gavin: [j]AGGGGGGH![/j][p/][s/] [j]SON OF A—[/j]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6987",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Celeste: I [i]told[/i] you to brace yourself![p/][s/] Popping your shoulder back in isn't exactly painless!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af92b6",
  "node": "WyattFinished",
  "text": "Wyatt: Alright, fine![p/][s/] I saw the magic cat, okay?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0832729",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What \"magic cat\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fe83a",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Wyatt: I saw it walk into the house last week![p/][s/] It looked [i]gross[/i],[p/] so I peeked in to see what it was doing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064f124",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Wyatt: And I saw it![p/][s/] I saw that cat put something in that box using magic! [h=\"That stuff was crazy!|I still don't believe it!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00623c9",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "And [i]there[/i] was the migraine."
}

{
  "id": "line:09de481",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay...[p/] And what did this cat look like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdec88",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Wyatt: It didn't have any hair.[p/] It kind of looked like a piece of raw meat."
}

{
  "id": "line:09292c0",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Did he seriously expect me to believe he saw a hairless cat casting magic?[p/] It was completely—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de5b90",
  "node": "WyattFinished2",
  "text": "Aster: He was probably shooing it away."
}

{
  "id": "line:032b559",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "That cat was at the refinery when Justin died..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dce785",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "That [i]magic[/i] cat was at the scene of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bb096",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey, Tyrion.[p/] I hope the noise wasn't too—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0c744",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Celeste: Whoa...[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006a42b",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Celeste: What did you say to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03066db",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Wyatt: Yo,[p/] I didn't say nothing![p/][s/] He just got like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:096ff88",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Show me this box."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6a754",
  "node": "WyattFinished3",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Sure.[p/] Whatever you say, man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d288f9",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "...It was obvious he was just seeing things.[p/] Commoners mistook natural phenomena for magic all the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05876c7",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "He probably just [i]thought[/i] he saw a magic spell,[p/] and the cat just happened to be there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecee4a",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "I was under a lot of stress.[p/] I almost let myself believe his wild story."
}

{
  "id": "line:08df1f8",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "It was honestly kind of funny when I thought about it,[p/] there was no way this \"magic cat\" created—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0555cc7",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "...It might not be a migraine.[p/] It might just be an aneurysm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee8d17",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Wyatt: Huh...[p/] It's a lot more busted up than I remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fe330",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "I walked up to the metal container and tried to open it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3d0d7",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "The lock was broken,[p/] but the metal was so bent that the chest was stuck closed."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d136c",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "I spotted something lodged in one of the metal crevices of the chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb8a55",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste,[p/] please scan the room for magical traces.[p/] Focus on the metal box."
}

{
  "id": "line:0972bf3",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, wow!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0747447",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Celeste: There's traces of [b]conjuration[b/] all over this metal chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b69c",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Cool.[p/] Cool."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c4685",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "I took a picture of the scene with my Runestone before slumping towards the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e602c4",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "I just lay on the floor, motionless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b483de",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc376d",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "The magic cat cast a spell on the magic box."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb89d4",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "The [i]MAGIC[/i] cat cast a spell on the [i]MAGIC[/i] box."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed8e0",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Wyatt: So...[p/] We cool?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe3a54",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes, Wyatt.[p/] We cool."
}

{
  "id": "line:08582e6",
  "node": "WyattFinished4",
  "text": "Wyatt: Cool..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d065a",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "Wyatt slowly backed out of the house,[p/] puzzled by...[p/] everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ef5d0",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0874a48",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "I responded with something between a groan and a sob."
}

{
  "id": "line:082b0c3",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...[i]Okay[/i],[p/] you need a break."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7d2e",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "Celeste: Let's get you out of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:034f13b",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "She lifted me with one arm and began carrying me out of the house like a sack of grain."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e7878",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "I'd normally object,[p/] but at this point,[p/] my spirit had just surrendered to whatever was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:03707de",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "She brought me to the nearby harbor,[p/] and placed me on a bench overlooking the ocean."
}

{
  "id": "line:078b693",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "Celeste: There you go.[p/] Just breathe in that ocean breeze."
}

{
  "id": "line:04669fe",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "I just muttered something incoherent in response."
}

{
  "id": "line:008eb61",
  "node": "WyattFinished5",
  "text": "...But I admitted that the air was nice here.[p/] It brought me back to happier memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09e2f",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "I closed my eyes and took in a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0c701",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "It was probably nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af5769",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "Celeste: It's [i]so[/i] cute![p/][s/] Hi there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0958",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "See?[p/] She probably just saw a cute animal on the docks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dec1e8",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "Her voice seemed to rise an octave higher."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceda71",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "It was rare.[p/] She was never really one to fawn over animals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2760",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "She really only got like that whenever she saw a cat."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cab24",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "...A cat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcebf5",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "[j]A CAT[/j]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0472f9c",
  "node": "WyattFinished6",
  "text": "Celeste: Hi, Kitty!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4112",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: [i]MROW[/i]! [h=\"Back, you brute!|Away with you!\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc30e9",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my goodness,[p/] look at this tiny little angel!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f6a11",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: [i]Mrow[/i]? [h=\"This one recognizes|royalty when she sees it.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bac480",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: [i]Meow[/i]... [h=\"I'll allow it|this time...\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0742f6d",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Hey, Celeste.[p/] She looks like a stray."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db75b4",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: She might let you pet her if you give her some food."
}

{
  "id": "line:047ce74",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: [i]Mrow[/i]... [h=\"I am not a [i]stray[/i].|I am merely independent.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44ea5",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "It was taking everything I had just to stay calm.[p/] I really needed Celeste to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2f3e1",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know,[p/] they're probably selling some tuna by the fish market nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe7f0",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure she'll appreciate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03efc27",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't even think of that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce127e",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll be right back![p/][s/] Don't scare her off, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bdc53",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16601",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "I slowly watched her as she skipped towards the fish market."
}

{
  "id": "line:07edf9b",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "I waited long enough to make sure that she was out of earshot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c48277",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [j]Alright, you little bastard![/j][p/][s/] [j]What did you do to Justin Waye?![/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee7aa",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: [i]MROW[/i]! [h=\"What's this then?!\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5223e",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: ...That voice.[p/] I've only met one other person who could talk with me like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e4092",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Cat: How are you speaking to me right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3d617",
  "node": "WyattFinished7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's a rare gift."
}

{
  "id": "line:0494529",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "I could see the thoughts of [i]any[/i] creature—[p/]not just a human's."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c443ab",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "And for some reason,[p/] animals were always able to understand me too."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bd69f",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "Maybe understanding their language allowed me to communicate with them properly."
}

{
  "id": "line:003bcdc",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "...Either that,[p/] or I was finally losing my mind.[p/] I honestly wasn't sure at this point."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ce004",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who are you?![p/][s/] Why have you been breaking into my house?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd807b",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "That question definitely drew some looks from the people passing by."
}

{
  "id": "line:08016f7",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "Cat: I have been known by many names,[p/] but [i]you[/i] may call me \"Queen\", peasant."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5fe2",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "Cat: As for \"your house\",[p/] you'll need to be more specific."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb5b86",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "Cat: I break into a lot of people's houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:05209db",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "I was tired and frustrated,[p/] but this had to be a blessing in disguise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0401aac",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus only saw truthful thoughts.[p/] Animals couldn't lie to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c46fb1",
  "node": "WyattFinished8",
  "text": "And despite how articulate they could sound,[p/] they were still simple in comparison to humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a24c45",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Statue"
}

{
  "id": "line:005872a",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: It's a statue of some kind of...[p/] daredevil?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063b3f7",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's Ferdinand Dumont:[p/] a famous stunt performer and physicist."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e791",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard he used to run shows here several decades ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0048726",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: He'd always jump over large obstacles or crevices in some kind of wheeled vehicle."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af44a",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard he even tried creating flying machines near the end of his career."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11ced",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Flying machines?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc4f8a",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah.[p/] I heard he didn't even use magic to make them fly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f81ae9",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Several businesses have opened up since the last time I came here."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b2ffc",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: They all seem to be pretty busy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b482",
  "node": "Square1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: The city is getting pretty crowded.[p/] Everything's packed."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ca356",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Investigation"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe24c",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Rika said that someone attacked her friend in the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03f7c",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They were supposedly a mage too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5a4e9",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Why would anyone do something like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdc379",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know,[p/] but we're going to find out."
}

{
  "id": "line:027c9b6",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't like this...[p/] What is the Grand General planning here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8ef09",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sure it's fine.[p/] Aria doesn't seem too worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6afb",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Aurinax is too important a city to stir up trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:072ebbf",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They'll leave once they locate a stolen package."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2665",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I really hope so."
}

{
  "id": "line:09eede0",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Morrison didn't seem to know about these reports of tensions between him and Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e6370",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: But Aria said that those reports came from multiple sources."
}

{
  "id": "line:0674f69",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's hard to know who to trust,[p/] but I don't think Mr. Morrison is lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:00df538",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Does that mean those reports were all wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b77c",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe they're just the products of some people being spooked by baseless rumors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4eec2",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder if Justin really had a run-in with the Mistweaving Phantom."
}

{
  "id": "line:007985a",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: The Phantom is supposed to be an expert at stealth.[p/] How was [i]Justin[/i] the one that finally saw him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f8cba",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible this isn't the first time the Phantom has silenced a witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf24c",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That just gives us all the more reason to catch them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08df7d2",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Next Lead"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76ca2",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Where should we go next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f19bc",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rika's friend died in the refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0795871",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should head there first and talk to whoever investigated the accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a6084",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a2df4",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind said there were tensions between Dracogen and the workers' unions,[p/] and the union head is supposedly the old harbormaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd23a4",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We might be able to find him near the harbor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7868c",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We've learned a lot,[p/] but it's difficult to make sense of what's going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:044c798",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's time we finally talked to Stefanic Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc28c1",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It's been some time.[p/] Maybe he's finally back at the Refinery."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a6a2",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whatever's happening,[p/] it concerns all of Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:021085a",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Santcus is the ruling lord of the city.[p/] He might be able to tell us something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c964ee",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Will he really talk to us, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090dd25",
  "node": "Square1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll just have to go to his manor and try to get an audience with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b69d",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste, it's my Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:09297bb",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a4024",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You show that thing to me all the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0872ba2",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry.[p/] It's just that I worked for so long to get this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca04b6",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm really proud of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f6085",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Alright, fine.[p/] I guess it's pretty cool."
}

{
  "id": "line:0968420",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes?[p/] Why wouldn't I be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d37bd",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It's just that—[p/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f96571",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]It's nothing.[p/] Just forget I said anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce536",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We've had so many cases together.[p/] I can't believe I've only been practicing law for a month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d88e2e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I just didn't expect so many of your cases to be so boring."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e3db0",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: So many of these \"murders\" just end up being accidents."
}

{
  "id": "line:054bcb0",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: That case with Wallace had some twists in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c0e72",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] that one was pretty memorable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e689db",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I guess Ruby's going to wonder why we haven't arrived back in Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55880",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I sent a letter out,[p/] and I'm sure this blockade will make the news."
}

{
  "id": "line:0160a03",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Assuming that the kingdom doesn't cover this whole thing up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd9bc1",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't expect to meet Aria here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebcb65",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I should bring her to Rika's café when this is all over."
}

{
  "id": "line:012e46e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You two have been spending a lot of time together on your days off."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2427",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] I've been having a lot of fun with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09efda3",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: She teaches me magic,[p/] and I teach her combat."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e473e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure the daughter of a Steelwind could actually give you a run for your money."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d5b16",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] For sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d1813",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm honestly not sure what to make of Dracogen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a782d1",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: He [i]seems[/i] like a sincere person,[p/] but I know better than to trust a member of the upper class."
}

{
  "id": "line:015ce5c",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: He's not a noble, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:031e1bd",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: With his wealth,[p/] he's not exactly a commoner either..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2b227",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] I just realized something."
}

{
  "id": "line:006cc2f",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: When we win this case,[p/] you'll have beaten von Sanctus twice in one week."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd67ec",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "The thought of humiliating him twice in a row [i]did[/i] sound appealing to me,[p/] but it was better not to get too personal when working these cases."
}

{
  "id": "line:0def7ac",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I love that thing that Rika does."
}

{
  "id": "line:00620e5",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What did she call it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04916c5",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's called \"chuunibyou\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d28c6",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's when you act dramatic and exaggerate."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d2ee3",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Chuunibyou\"...[p/] That sounds like a word in the Eastern Kingdoms' language."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3be33",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess so.[p/] Maybe it originates from there."
}

{
  "id": "line:047e261",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I really hope the Grand General pulls his troops out of Aurinax when this is all over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39a93",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It'll be fine.[p/] If something happens,[p/] I'll be here to protect you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f268f2",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm more worried about the others.[p/] Every time Lucio Steelwind gets involved,[p/] innocent people die."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc4ba9",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Player: EttaStrap"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d567b",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wonder what the \"ETTA\" on this strap stands for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063538a",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait,[p/] watch this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9c7e5",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Energy\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfac9a",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"Energy\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff34c6",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay,[p/] what starts with a \"t\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0013c5e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Energy\"...[p/] \"Tyrion\"...[p/] \"Tyrion\"..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67ed8",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Association\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0692909",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Energy Tyrion Tyrion Association\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff4d42",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wow,[p/] you cracked the case, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe6fd",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You damn right I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:021926b",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you have any ideas what this strap might be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0379",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe it's something you hang off a hook."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b9930",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: That might explain the \"VI\".[p/] It could be a label to designate a number?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db8b88",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But why is it so small?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea686",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Why couldn't they have shipped Lotus Juice from Ixia?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04dd064",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ixia?[p/] I thought Lotus Juice came from the Eastern Kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:007922f",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: They used to be called the Empire of Ixia,[p/] but then they united with a bunch of their surrounding kingdoms under one nation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf379a",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I should really take you there someday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccf33d",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe when we're seeing less work.[p/] We've been taking on cases left and right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06cde",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I used to think of becoming a master thief before I became a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:062bea9",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] I was going to be a [i]righteous[/i] thief."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e641c6",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I'd steal from the rich and give to the commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab6310",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess that's noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bde4b",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What changed your mind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0610f6c",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: My...[p/] [i]skill set[/i] isn't all that great for stealth."
}

{
  "id": "line:07093fe",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it because you're really loud?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dd802",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: But, yeah...[p/] I'm better at fighting my way into a fortress than sneaking in."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0676",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Gavin|Wyatt"
}

{
  "id": "line:0723523",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Kids these days.[p/] They have no respect for their elders."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dc038",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] I'm pretty sure those two are only a few years younger than us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0560dc4",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] Well, I'm clearly older than them mentally."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b6bf2",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Player: RikaPast"
}

{
  "id": "line:02647a4",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe Rika had to become a thief."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de7cd8",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I kind of get it.[p/] When there's not enough to go around,[p/] you have to do what you have to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3948b",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] did [i]you[/i]—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fa20c",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I had to.[p/] They shut down families taven,[p/] and winter was coming."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfedbb",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: We wouldn't have survived if I hadn't taken what we needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ddb83",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry you had to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d47e6",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It's okay.[p/] Those days are behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:081db93",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I have the [i]best[/i] job ever, now."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cdee8",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What a way to go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a80162",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I really hope he didn't suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:016dd6a",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It may sound grim,[p/] but sometimes the body goes into shock fast enough that they don't feel any pain."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5b29",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Death must have come quickly for him, at least."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eaff4",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Although I doubt that would give Rika any peace."
}

{
  "id": "line:032189f",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: So [i]that[/i] is Lucio Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea904a",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe that monster is Aria's dad."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2b95c",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I hope this isn't too much for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:008fa97",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: All the more reason for us to solve this mystery as soon as we can."
}

{
  "id": "line:054619e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You've looked like you were on the verge of having an aneurysm since we found that chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:01afa98",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I'm fine.[p/] Let's just keep going."
}

{
  "id": "line:0500010",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "I needed to make sense of what was happening.[p/] I felt like I was losing my mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:09aa08c",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Queen"
}

{
  "id": "line:008199d",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god.[p/] That cat was so cute!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08eb944",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Can we go back?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c62273",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Really?[p/] You don't think she's kind of gross-looking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40a9d",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] [i]all[/i] cats are beautiful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c58bf4",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not [i]her[/i] fault she was born hairless..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0857dc3",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i], Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2848e",
  "node": "Square1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Sorry, Tyrion.[p/] I don't think I can help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f538b",
  "node": "Square2_Examine",
  "text": "She didn't seem keen on talking at the moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0585eab",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You don't have to push yourself so hard."
}

{
  "id": "line:08324f7",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I need to.[p/] I can't afford to fall apart,[p/] especially not now."
}

{
  "id": "line:096319f",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay,[p/] but there's no shame in taking a break."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b443",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should head to that house and see if we can find Justin's friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0044163",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bbf62",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Let's go."
}

{
  "id": "line:071762c",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You look tired.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f7bc7",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You should rest by the harbor a little longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c5a1",
  "node": "Square2_Talk",
  "text": "I questioned her motives,[p/] but she wasn't wrong."
}
